### Kabyle Bible: Matthew

<span id="an_1:1">1:1</span> A ten-an izuṛan n Ɛisa Lmasiḥ yellan si
dderya n Sidna Dawed akk-d Sidna Ibṛahim :

<span id="an_1:2">1:2</span> Sidna Ibṛahim yeǧǧa-d Isḥaq, Isḥaq yeǧǧa-d
Yeɛqub, Yeɛqub yeǧǧa-d Yahuda d watmaten-is.

<span id="an_1:3">1:3</span> Yahuda akk-d Tamaṛ ǧǧan-d Fares, akk-d
Ziraḥ ; Fares yeǧǧa-d Ḥesrun, Ḥesrun yeǧǧa-d Aram.

<span id="an_1:4">1:4</span> Aram yeǧǧa-d Ɛaminadab, Ɛaminadab yeǧǧa-d
Naḥsun, Naḥsun yeǧǧa-d Salmun.

<span id="an_1:5">1:5</span> Salmun d Raḥab ǧǧan-d Buɛaz, Buɛaz akk-d
Rut sɛan-d Ɛubed, Ɛubed yeǧǧa-d Yassa.

<span id="an_1:6">1:6</span> Yassa yeǧǧa-d Sidna Dawed, Sidna Dawed
yuɣal d agellid, yeǧǧa-d ɣer tmeṭṭut n Uryaḥ Sidna Sliman.

<span id="an_1:7">1:7</span> Sidna Sliman yeǧǧa-d Raḥabɛam, Raḥabɛam
yeǧǧa-d Abiya, Abiya yeǧǧa-d Asaf,

<span id="an_1:8">1:8</span> Asaf yeǧǧa-d Yehucafat ; Yehucafat yeǧǧa-d
Yihuram ; Yihuram yeǧǧa-d Ɛuzya ;

<span id="an_1:9">1:9</span> Ɛuzya yeǧǧa-d Yuṭam ; Yuṭam yeǧǧa-d Aḥaz ;
Aḥaz yeǧǧa-d Ḥizeqya ;

<span id="an_1:10">1:10</span> Ḥizeqya yeǧǧa-d Mennac ; Mennac yeǧǧa-d
Ɛamun ; Ɛamun yeǧǧa-d Yuciya ;

<span id="an_1:11">1:11</span> Yuciya yeǧǧa-d Yixunya akk-d watmaten-is,
di lweqt i deg iqaldiyen wwin at Isṛail d imeḥbas ɣer tmurt n Babilun.

<span id="an_1:12">1:12</span> Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurtn Babilun,
Yixunya yeǧǧa-d Calatyel ; Calatyel yeǧǧa-d Zurubabil .

<span id="an_1:13">1:13</span> Zurubabil yeǧǧa-d Abihud. Abihud yeǧǧa-d
Ilyaqim ; Ilyaqim yeǧǧa-d Ɛazuṛ ;

<span id="an_1:14">1:14</span> Ɛazuṛ yeǧǧa-d Saduq ; Saduq yeǧǧa-d Yaxin
; Yaxin yeǧǧa-d Ilihud.

<span id="an_1:15">1:15</span> Ilhud yeǧǧa-d Ilɛazaṛ ; Ilɛazaṛ yeǧǧa-d
Mattan ; Mattan yeǧǧa-d Yeɛqub.

<span id="an_1:16">1:16</span> Yeɛqub yeǧǧa-d Yusef, d Yusef agi i d
argaz n Meryem i d-yeǧǧan Sidna Ɛisa i gețțusemman Lmasiḥ.

<span id="an_1:17">1:17</span> Si lweqt n Sidna Ibṛahim armi d lweqt n
Sidna Dawed, ɛeddan ṛbeɛṭac n leǧyal. Ɛeddan daɣen ṛbeɛṭac n leǧyal si
lweqt n Sidna Dawed armi d lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Babilun. Si
lweqt-agi n usgiǧǧi armi d lweqt n Lmasiḥ ɛeddan daɣen ṛbeɛṭac n leǧyal.

<span id="an_1:18">1:18</span> Atan wamek i d-ilul Sidna Ɛisa : yemma-s
Meryem tella tețwaxḍeb i yiwen wergaz ițțusemman Yusef. S tezmert n Ṛṛuḥ
iqedsen, terfed s tadist uqbel aț-țeddu ț-țislit.

<span id="an_1:19">1:19</span> Yusef axḍib-is, yellan d argaz n ṣṣwab,
ur yebɣi ara a ț-țicemmet, dɣa yeqsed ad imsefṛaq yid-es s tuffra.

<span id="an_1:20">1:20</span> Akken yețxemmim i waya, yers-ed ɣuṛ-es
lmelk n Ṛebbi di targit yenna-yas : A Yusef ! A mmi-s n Dawed ! Ur
țțaggad ara aț-țesɛuḍ Meryem ț-țameṭṭut-ik, axaṭer llufan yellan di
tɛebbuṭ-is, yusa-yas-d s Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen.

<span id="an_1:21">1:21</span> A d-tesɛu aqcic, a s-tsemmiḍ Ɛisa, axaṭer
d nețța ara iselken lumma-s si ddnubat-nsen.

<span id="an_1:22">1:22</span> Ayagi akk yedṛa iwakken ad ițwakemmel
wayen i d-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi seg imi n nnbi Iceɛya :

<span id="an_1:23">1:23</span> Ațan tɛezrit aț-țerfed tadist, a d-tesɛu
aqcic ad ițțusemmi Imanuwil yeɛni :« Ṛebbi yid-nneɣ.»

<span id="an_1:24">1:24</span> Mi i d-yuki Yusef, ixdem ayen i s-d-yenna
lmelk n Sidi Ṛebbi, yeqbel Meryem aț-țili ț-țameṭṭut-is ; yewwi-ț-id ɣer
wexxam-is.

<span id="an_1:25">1:25</span> Meɛna ur ț-innul ara armi i d-tesɛa mmi-s
iwumi isemma Ɛisa.

<span id="an_2:1">2:1</span> Sidna Ɛisa ilul di taddart n Bitelḥem, di
tmurt n Yahuda di lweqt n ugellid Hiṛudus ameqqran, kra n imusnawen
usan-d si cceṛq ɣer temdint n Lquds, iwakken ad steqsin :

<span id="an_2:2">2:2</span> anda ilul llufan-nni ara yilin d agellid n
wat Isṛail ? Axaṭer nwala-d itri-ines si cceṛq, nusa-d a t-neɛbed.

<span id="an_2:3">2:3</span> Agellid Hiṛudus akk-d imezdaɣ n temdint n
Lquds meṛṛa dehcen, yerwi lxaṭer-nsen mi slan s lexbaṛ-agi.

<span id="an_2:4">2:4</span> Hiṛudus yesnejmaɛ-ed akk lmuqedmin d
lɛulama n wegdud, isteqsa-ten ɣef wemkan anda ara d-ilal Lmasiḥ ara
d-yasen.

<span id="an_2:5">2:5</span> Nnan-as : Ahat di tmurt n Yahuda di taddart
n Bitelḥem ! Axaṭer atan wayen i gura nnbi Mixa :

<span id="an_2:6">2:6</span> I kemm a taddart n Bitelḥem, ur telliḍ ara
ț-țaneggarut ger temdinin n Yahuda, axaṭer seg-em ara d-iffeɣ ugellid
ara yeksen at Isṛail agdud-iw.

<span id="an_2:7">2:7</span> Hiṛudus yessawel i imusnawen nni s tuffra,
isteqsa-ten si melmi i walan itri-nni.

<span id="an_2:8">2:8</span> Dɣa iceggeɛ-iten ɣer Bitelḥem, yenna-yasen
: Nadit lexbaṛ n ṣṣeḥ ɣef weqcic-agi, m'ara t-tafem, init-iyi-d iwakken
ad ṛuḥeɣ ula d nekk a t-ɛabdeɣ.

<span id="an_2:9">2:9</span> Mi slan i ugellid, ṛuḥen. AAkken kan i
ffɣen, walan itri-nni i ẓran di cceṛq yezwar, iteddu zdat-sen. MMi
gewweḍ sennig wemkan anda yella weqcic-nni, yeḥbes.

<span id="an_2:10">2:10</span> Feṛḥen aṭas mi walan itri-nni.

<span id="an_2:11">2:11</span> Kecmen ɣer wexxam-nni, walan llufan akk-d
yemma-s Meryem ; tɛeǧben s weqcic-nni dɣa seǧǧden zdat-es. FFsin
tiyemmusin-nsen, fkan-as tirezfin : ddheb, lebxuṛ akk-d leɛṭeṛ ɣlayen.

<span id="an_2:12">2:12</span> Sidi Ṛebbi ixebbeṛ-iten-id di targit ur
țțuɣalen ara ɣer Hiṛudus, dɣa uɣalen ɣer tmurt-nsen seg ubrid nniḍen.

<span id="an_2:13">2:13</span> Mi ṛuḥen, lmelk n Sidi Ṛebbi idheṛ-as-ed
i Yusef di targit, yenna-yas-ed :-- Kker, ddem aqcic akk-d yemma-s,
rewlet ɣer tmurt n Maṣeṛ, qqimet dinna alamma nniɣ-ak-ed a d-tuɣaleḍ,
axaṭer Hiṛudus ad iqelleb ɣef weqcic-agi iwakken a t-ineɣ.

<span id="an_2:14">2:14</span> Yusef ikker yewwi aqcic-nni akk-d yemma-s
deg iḍ, yerwel ɣer tmurt n Maṣeṛ.

<span id="an_2:15">2:15</span> Yeqqim dinna armi yemmut Hiṛudus, iwakken
ad idṛu wayen i d-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi seg imi n nnbi Huceɛ : Ssawleɣ-as i
Mmi a d-iffeɣ si tmurt n Maṣer.

<span id="an_2:16">2:16</span> Mi gwala Hiṛudus belli kelxen-t
imusnawen-nni, ikcem-it zzɛaf d ameqqran, iceggeɛ ɣer taddart n Bitelḥem
akk-d ț-țmura i s-d-izzin, ad nɣen arrac meṛṛa yesɛan si sin iseggasen d
akessar, s wakken yella leḥsab i s-d-fkan imusnawen-nni.

<span id="an_2:17">2:17</span> Dɣa yețwakemmel wayen i d yenna nnbi
Irmiya :

<span id="an_2:18">2:18</span> Yekker leɛyaḍ di taddart n Rama, nesla i
imeṭṭawen d umeǧǧed, d Ṛaḥil i gețrun ɣef warraw-is, tegguma aț-țesbeṛ
fell-asen, axaṭer mmuten.

<span id="an_2:19">2:19</span> Mi gemmut Hiṛudus ameqqran, lmelk n Sidi
Ṛebbi iweḥḥa-d i Yusef di targit mi gella di tmurt n Maṣer,

<span id="an_2:20">2:20</span> yenna-yas : Kker, ddem aqcic d yemma-s
tuɣaleḍ ɣer tmurt n wat Isṛail, axaṭer wid yebɣan ad nɣen aqcic-nni,
mmuten.

<span id="an_2:21">2:21</span> Yusef iddem aqcic-nni d yemma-s, yuɣal
ɣer tmurt n wat Isṛail

<span id="an_2:22">2:22</span> Meɛna mi gesla belli d Aṛxilyus mmi-s n
Hiṛudus, i gellan d agellid ɣef tmurt n Yahuda, yuggad. SSidi Ṛebbi
iɛeggen-as-ed di targit, iṛuḥ ɣer tmurt n Jlili,

<span id="an_2:23">2:23</span> izdeɣ deg yiwet n taddart ițțusemman
Naṣaret, iwakken ad yedṛu wayen i d-nnan lenbiya : Ad ițțusemmi Anaṣari.

<span id="an_3:1">3:1</span> Deg wussan-nni, iban-ed Yeḥya aɣeṭṭas,
yețbecciṛ deg unezṛuf n tmurt n Yahuda,

<span id="an_3:2">3:2</span> iqqaṛ-ed : Tubet, beddlet tikli, axaṭer
tagelda n igenwan tqeṛṛeb-ed.

<span id="an_3:3">3:3</span> Fell-as i d-immeslay nnbi Iceɛya mi d-yenna
: Ț-țaɣect n win ițɛeggiḍen di lxali : Heggit abrid n Sidi Ṛebbi,
ssemsawit iberdan-is.

<span id="an_3:4">3:4</span> Yeḥya yelsa llebsa yețwaxedmen s ccɛeṛ n
welɣem, tabagust n weglim ɣef wammas-is, tamɛict-is d ibẓaẓ akk-d tament
n lexla.

<span id="an_3:5">3:5</span> Imezdaɣ meṛṛa n temdint n Lquds, tamurt n
Yahuda akk-d tmura i d-yezzin i wasif n Urdun, țțasen-d ɣuṛ-es

<span id="an_3:6">3:6</span> iwakken a d-qiṛṛen s ddnubat nsen, nețța
yesseɣḍas-iten deg wasif nni n Urdun.

<span id="an_3:7">3:7</span> Mi gwala aṭas n at ifariziyen d isaduqiyen
i d-ițasen ad țwaɣeḍsen, yenna-yasen : A ccetla n izerman, anwa i kkun
isfaqen belli tzemrem aț-țrewlem i lḥisab i d-iteddun ?

<span id="an_3:8">3:8</span> Sbeggnet-ed s lecɣal-nwen belli tettubem,
tbeddlem tikli.

<span id="an_3:9">3:9</span> Ur qqaṛet ara i yiman-nwen : « Sidna
Ibṛahim d jeddi-tneɣ » ! Axaṭer, a wen-iniɣ : SSidi Ṛebbi yezmer a
d-yefk dderya i Ibṛahim seg idɣaɣen-agi.

<span id="an_3:10">3:10</span> Ațan ihi tcaquṛt thegga ɣer izuṛan n
ttjuṛ, yal ttejṛa ur d-nețțak ara lfakya lɛali, aț-țețwagzem,
aț-țețwaḍeggeṛ ɣer tmes.

<span id="an_3:11">3:11</span> Nekk sseɣḍaseɣ-kkun deg waman iwakken
aț-țetubem, lameɛna a d-yas yiwen yesɛan tazmert akteṛ-iw, ur uklaleɣ
ara a s-fsiɣ ula d arkasen is. Nețța a kkun-yesseɣḍes s Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen
ț-țmes.

<span id="an_3:12">3:12</span> Tazzert deg ufus-is, ad yebrez annar-is,
ad ijmeɛ irden-is ɣer ikuffan, ma d alim a t-yesseṛɣ di tmes ur nxețți.

<span id="an_3:13">3:13</span> Sidna Ɛisa yusa-d si tmurt n Jlili ɣer
wasif n Urdun iwakken a t- yesseɣḍes Yeḥya.

<span id="an_3:14">3:14</span> Yeḥya yugi, yenna-yas : D nekk i geḥwaǧen
ad iyi- tesɣeḍseḍ, kečč tusiḍ-ed ɣuṛ-i iwakken a k-sɣeḍseɣ !

<span id="an_3:15">3:15</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Anef tura ! Akkagi
i glaq a nexdem lebɣi n Sidi Ṛebbi ! DDɣa Yeḥya yunef-as.

<span id="an_3:16">3:16</span> Mi gețwaɣḍes Sidna Ɛisa, yeffeɣ-ed seg
waman ; imiren kan ldin igenwan, yers-ed fell-as Ṛṛuḥ n Sidi Ṛebbi s
ṣṣifa n tetbirt.

<span id="an_3:17">3:17</span> Tekka-d yiwet n taɣect seg igenwan,
tenna-d : «\` Wagi d Mmi ameɛzuz, deg-s i gella lfeṛḥ-iw ! »

<span id="an_4:1">4:1</span> Imiren Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen yewwi Sidna Ɛisa ɣer
unezṛuf iwakken a t-ijeṛṛeb Cciṭan.

<span id="an_4:2">4:2</span> Mi guẓam ṛebɛin wussan d ṛebɛin wuḍan,
yuɣal yelluẓ.

<span id="an_4:3">4:3</span> Iqeṛṛeb ɣuṛ-es Yeblis yenna-yas : Ma d
Mmi-s n Ṛebbi i telliḍ, ini-yasen i yedɣaɣen-agi ad uɣalen d aɣṛum.

<span id="an_4:4">4:4</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Yura di tira iqedsen
: Mačči s weɣṛum kan ara iɛic wemdan, lameɛna s mkul awal i d-ițasen s
ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_4:5">4:5</span> Cciṭan yewwi-t ɣer temdint n Lquds
issers-it ɣef yixef n lǧameɛ iqedsen,

<span id="an_4:6">4:6</span> yenna-yas : Ma d Mmi-s n Ṛebbi i telliḍ,
ḍeggeṛ iman-ik d akessar, anaɣ yura : Sidi Ṛebbi ad yefk lameṛ i
lmalayekkat-is fell-ak, aa k-awint ger ifassen-nsent iwakken ad ḥadrent
aḍar-ik ɣef yedɣaɣe n .

<span id="an_4:7">4:7</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Yura daɣen : Ur
tețjeṛṛibeḍ ara Sidi Ṛebbi IIllu-inek .

<span id="an_4:8">4:8</span> Cciṭan yewwi-t daɣen ɣef wedrar ɛlayen,
isken-as-ed tigeldiwin meṛṛa n ddunit d lɛaḍima-nsent, yenna-yas :

<span id="an_4:9">4:9</span> A k-tent-fkeɣ meṛṛa ma yella tseǧǧdeḍ
zdat-i a yi-tɛebdeḍ.

<span id="an_4:10">4:10</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Beɛɛed akkin
fell-i a Cciṭan, axaṭer yura : Anagar Sidi Ṛebbi-inek ara tɛebdeḍ , i
nețța kan iwumi ara tseǧdeḍ .

<span id="an_4:11">4:11</span> Dɣa Cciṭan iṭṭaxeṛ fell-as. Imiren
usant-ed lmalayekkat ɣuṛ-es, iwakken a s-qedcent.

<span id="an_4:12">4:12</span> Mi gesla s Yeḥya yețwaḥbes, Sidna Ɛisa
yuɣal ɣer tmurt n Jlili.

<span id="an_4:13">4:13</span> Iffeɣ si taddart n Naṣaret, iṛuḥ ad izdeɣ
di Kafernaḥum ; ț-țamdint yyellan rrif n lebḥeṛ di leǧwahi n tmura n
Zabulun d Nefṭali,

<span id="an_4:14">4:14</span> iwakken ad yedṛu wayen yenna nnbi Iceɛya
:

<span id="an_4:15">4:15</span>  A tamurt n Zabulun akk-d Nefṭali, a
timura iqeṛben lebḥeṛ akkin i wasif n Urdun , a tamurt n Jlili i deg
zedɣen leǧnas ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail,

<span id="an_4:16">4:16</span> agdud-nni yezgan di ṭṭlam, iwala tafat
tameqqrant, wid izedɣen di ṭṭlam n lmut, tceṛq-ed fell-asen tafat !

<span id="an_4:17">4:17</span> Seg imiren, Sidna Ɛisa yebda yețbecciṛ
yeqqaṛ : Tubet, uɣalet-ed ɣer webrid, axaṭer tagelda n igenwan
tqeṛṛeb-ed.

<span id="an_4:18">4:18</span> Mi gțeddu Sidna Ɛisa ɣef rrif n lebḥeṛ n
Jlili, iwala sin iḥewwaten : SSemɛun ițțusemman Buṭrus akk-d gma-s
Andriyus. Llan ṭeggiṛen icebbaken-nsen ɣer lebḥeṛ, țṣeggiḍen.

<span id="an_4:19">4:19</span> Yenna-yasen : Ddut-ed yid-i, a kkun-rreɣ
d iṣeggaḍen n yemdanen.

<span id="an_4:20">4:20</span> Dɣa imiren kan, ǧǧan icebbaken nsen, ddan
yid-es.

<span id="an_4:21">4:21</span> Mi gerna yelḥa kra, iwala sin watmaten
nniḍen : Yeɛqub d Yuḥenna yellan d arraw n Zabadi. LLlan akk-d baba-tsen
di teflukt, țxiḍin icebbaken-nsen.

<span id="an_4:22">4:22</span> Yessawel-asen, imiren kan ǧǧan dinna
baba-tsen, taflukt-nni, ṛuḥen ddan yid-es.

<span id="an_4:23">4:23</span> Syenna, Sidna Ɛisa yekka-d tamurt n Jlili
meṛṛa, yesselmad di leǧwameɛ n wat Isṛail, yețbecciṛ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ n
tgeldit n Ṛebbi, isseḥlay yal aṭan d yal leɛyubat n lɣaci.

<span id="an_4:24">4:24</span> Slan yis ula di tmurt n Surya meṛṛa ;
țțawin-as-ed imuḍan i ghelken si mkul aṭan : wid ițwamelken, wid iwumi
yețṛuḥu leɛqel akk-d wukrifen. Sidna Ɛisa isseḥla-ten akk.

<span id="an_4:25">4:25</span> D izumal n lɣaci i t-id-itebɛen si tmurt
n Jlili, si ɛecṛa n temdinin-nni, si temdint n Lquds, si tmurt n Yahuda
akk-d leǧwahi yellan agemmaḍ i wasif n Urdun.

<span id="an_5:1">5:1</span> Mi gwala annect-nni n lɣaci, Sidna Ɛisa
yuli ɣer wedrar iqqim. Inelmaden-is qeṛṛben ɣuṛ-es,

<span id="an_5:2">5:2</span> dɣa ibda isselmad-iten :

<span id="an_5:3">5:3</span> D iseɛdiyen wid ițeddun s neyya, aaxaṭer
tagelda n igenwan d ayla-nsen !

<span id="an_5:4">5:4</span> D iseɛdiyen wid ițrun, axaṭer ad țwaṣebbṛen
!

<span id="an_5:5">5:5</span> D iseɛdiyen wid ḥninen, aaxaṭer ad weṛten
tamurt i sen-iwɛed Sidi Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_5:6">5:6</span> D iseɛdiyen wid illuẓen, iffuden lḥeqq,
axaṭer ad ṛwun !

<span id="an_5:7">5:7</span> D iseɛdiyen wid yesɛan ṛṛeḥma deg
wulawen-nsen, aaxaṭer ad iḥunn fell-asen Sidi Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_5:8">5:8</span> D iseɛdiyen wid iwumi yeṣfa wul, axaṭer ad
walin Sidi Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_5:9">5:9</span> D iseɛdiyen wid i d-isrusun talwit, aad
țțusemmin d arraw n Sidi Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_5:10">5:10</span> D iseɛdiyen wid ițțuqehṛen ɣef lḥeqq,
aaxaṭer ddewla igenwan d ayla-nsen !

<span id="an_5:11">5:11</span> D iseɛdiyen ara tilim, m'ara kkun-regmen,
mm'ara tețwaqehṛem, m'ara xedmen deg-wen lbaṭel ɣef ddemma-w.

<span id="an_5:12">5:12</span> Feṛḥet, ilit di lfeṛḥ, axaṭer ṛṛezq-nwen
d ameqqran deg igenwan, aakka i țwaqehṛen lenbiya i kkun-id izwaren.

<span id="an_5:13">5:13</span> D kunwi i d lmelḥ n ddunit, lameɛna ma
tṛuḥ-as lbenna i lmelḥ, s wacu ara s-ț-id-nerr ? Yelha kan ma nḍeggeṛ-it
ɣer beṛṛa a t-rekkḍen yemdanen.

<span id="an_5:14">5:14</span> D kunwi i ț-țafat n ddunit ; taddart
yellan ɣef wudrar ulamek ara teffer !

<span id="an_5:15">5:15</span> Akken daɣen, ur nceɛɛel ara taftilt
iwakken a ț-nɣumm s kra, meɛna a ț-nessers ɣef lmeṣbeḥ, iwakken
aț-țfeǧǧeǧ i wid akk yellan deg wexxam.

<span id="an_5:16">5:16</span> Akka i glaq aț-țecceɛceɛ tafat-nwen zdat
yemdanen, iwakken ad walin lecɣal-nwen ilhan, yerna ad ḥemden Baba-twen
yellan deg igenwan.

<span id="an_5:17">5:17</span> Ɣuṛ-wat aț-țɣilem usiɣ-ed ad sseɣliɣ ayen
i d-tenna ccariɛa d wayen i d-nnan lenbiya ! Ur d-usiɣ ara ad sseɣliɣ,
lameɛna usiɣ-ed ad snekmaleɣ.

<span id="an_5:18">5:18</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : skud mazal igenwan d
lqaɛa, ula d yiwen wawal neɣ usekkil n ccariɛa ur imeḥḥu, alamma yedṛa
wayen akk yuran deg-s.

<span id="an_5:19">5:19</span> Win ur nqudeṛ ara ula d yiwen n lameṛ
amecṭuḥ n ccariɛa, yerna isselmad i wiyaḍ ad xedmen am nețța, ad
ițwaḥseb d amecṭuḥ akk di tgelda n igenwan. MMa d win ixeddmen ayen i
d-tenna ccariɛa, yerna isselmad i wiyaḍ ad xedmen akken, ad yili d
ameqqran di tgelda n igenwan.

<span id="an_5:20">5:20</span> Axaṭer a wen-iniɣ, ma yella ur tuɣem ara
awal i Sidi Ṛebbi akteṛ n wakken tețțaɣem awal i yimusnawen n ccariɛa d
ifariziyen, ur tkeččmem ara tagelda n igenwan.

<span id="an_5:21">5:21</span> Teslam daɣen s leqwanen i d- ițțunefken i
lejdud-nneɣ : Ur tneqqeḍ ara tamgeṛt, WWin ara yenɣen tamgeṛṭ, ad iɛeddi
di ccṛeɛ, ad ițwaḥkem fell-as.

<span id="an_5:22">5:22</span> Ma d nekk a wen-iniɣ : kra n win ara
izeɛfen ɣef gma-s, ad iɛeddi di ccṛeɛ. Win ara yinin i gma-s : « ay
abuhal, » ad ibedd zdat wesqamu n ccraɛ. Win ara yinin i gma-s : « ay
amehbul, » yuklal ad ikcem ɣer ǧahennama.

<span id="an_5:23">5:23</span> M'ara tțedduḍ aț-țefkeḍ lweɛda i Sidi
Ṛebbi, temmektaḍ-ed zdat n wemkan n iseflawen belli gma-k iṭṭef-ak
cceḥna,

<span id="an_5:24">5:24</span> eǧǧ dinna lweɛda-nni, tṛuḥeḍ uqbel
aț-ḍelbeḍ ssmaḥ i gma-k, d wamek ara tefkeḍ lweɛda-k i Sidi Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_5:25">5:25</span> Ma yella iḍlem-ik yiwen, tedduklem di sin
ɣer wexxam n ccṛeɛ, ɣiwel msefham kečč yid-es deg ubrid, m'ulac axṣim-ik
a k-yawi ɣer lḥakem, lḥakem a k-yefk i wɛessas, aɛessas-nni, a k-yerr
ɣer lḥebs.

<span id="an_5:26">5:26</span> A k-iniɣ tideț : ur d-țeffɣeḍ ara syenna
alamma txellṣeḍ aṣurdi aneggaru n ṭṭlaba-inek.

<span id="an_5:27">5:27</span> Teslam belli qqaṛen-d : ur xeddem ara
asekkak yeɛni zzna.

<span id="an_5:28">5:28</span> Lameɛna, nekkini a wen-d-iniɣ : win ara
imuqlen tameṭṭut, imenna deg ul-is ad iznu yid-es, atan am akken izna
yid-es.

<span id="an_5:29">5:29</span> Daymi ma yella ț-țiṭ-ik tayeffust i
k-ițawin ɣer leḥṛam, qleɛ-iț, ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak. Axaṭer axiṛ-ak a
k-iṛuḥ yiwen si lemfaṣel-ik wala aț-țkecmeḍ s lekmal-ik ɣer ǧahennama.

<span id="an_5:30">5:30</span> Ma yella s ufus-ik ayeffus i txeddmeḍ
leḥṛam, gzem-it, tḍegṛeḍ-t akkin fell-ak, axiṛ-ak a k-ixaṣ ufus wala ma
tkecmeḍ s lekmal-ik ɣer ǧahennama.

<span id="an_5:31">5:31</span> Qqaṛen-d daɣen : Win ara yebrun i
tmeṭṭut-is, a s-yefk lkaɣeḍ n berru .

<span id="an_5:32">5:32</span> Lameɛna nekkini a wen-iniɣ : win ara
yebrun i tmeṭṭut-is, yili ur tezni ara, d nețța i ț-iwelhen ɣer zzna ma
tezweǧ d wayeḍ. Daɣen win yuɣen tameṭṭut innebran, ula d nețța yezna.

<span id="an_5:33">5:33</span> Teslam daɣen s wayen i d-nnan i
lejdud-nneɣ : Ur ḥennet ara, lameɛna ayen i tɛuhdeḍ s limin zdat Sidi
Ṛebbi, ilaq a t-txedmeḍ.

<span id="an_5:34">5:34</span> Meɛna nekk a wen-iniɣ : ur țgallat ara
maḍi ! Ur țgallat s igenni, axaṭer d amkan n lḥekma n Sidi Ṛebbi,

<span id="an_5:35">5:35</span> ur țgallat s lqaɛa axaṭer fell-as i
gesrusu iḍaṛṛen-is, neɣ s Lquds imi ț-țamdint n ugellid ameqqran.

<span id="an_5:36">5:36</span> Ur țgallat ara daɣen : « s yixef n
uqeṛṛuy-nwen » axaṭer ur tezmirem ara aț-țerrem ula d yiwen wenẓad d
aberkan neɣ d amellal.

<span id="an_5:37">5:37</span> Init « ih » ma ilaq aț-ținim ih, neɣ «
xaṭi » ma ilaq aț-ținim xaṭi ; ayen akk ara ternum d zzyada, s ɣuṛ
Cciṭan i d-ițas.

<span id="an_5:38">5:38</span> Teslam s wayen i d-qqaṛen : Tiṭ s tiṭ,
tuɣmest s tuɣmest.

<span id="an_5:39">5:39</span> Meɛna nekk a wen-iniɣ : ma yella win i
wen-ixedmen cceṛ ur țțarat ara țțaṛ. Ma iwwet-ik yiwen ɣer lḥenk
ayeffus, sken-as lḥenk nniḍen.

<span id="an_5:40">5:40</span> Ma yebɣa yiwen a k-isiweḍ ɣer ccṛeɛ
iwakken a k-ikkes aqenduṛ-ik, rnu-yas ula d abeṛnus-ik.

<span id="an_5:41">5:41</span> Ma yella iḥṛes-ik walebɛaḍ a s-tbibbeḍ
taɛkumt azgen webrid-is, kečč awi-yas-ț armi d axxam.

<span id="an_5:42">5:42</span> Efk-as ayen yeḥwaǧ i win i k-d-issutren,
ur reggel ara ɣef win ibɣan ad yerḍel s ɣuṛ-ek.

<span id="an_5:43">5:43</span> Teslam i wayen i d-qqaṛen : Ḥemmel
amdakkel-ik, tkeṛheḍ aɛdaw ik.

<span id="an_5:44">5:44</span> Nekk a wen-iniɣ : ḥemmlet iɛdawen-nwen i
kkun ițqehhiṛen. BBarket wid i kkun-ineɛlen, xedmet lxiṛ i wid i
kkun-ikeṛhen, dɛut s lxiṛ i wid i kkun-iḍelmen, akk-d wid i
kkun-ițqehhiṛen.

<span id="an_5:45">5:45</span> S wakka ara d-tbanem d arraw n Baba-twen
yellan deg igenwan, axaṭer nețța icṛeq-ed iṭij-is ama ɣef wid yelhan ama
ɣef yemcumen, yețțak-ed ageffur ( lehwa ) ama i wid ixeddmen lxiṛ, ama i
wid ixeddmen cceṛ.

<span id="an_5:46">5:46</span> Ma yella tḥemmlem kan wid i
kkun-iḥemmlen, d acu n lfayda ara tesɛum ? Ula d imekkasen n tebzert (
leɣṛama ) xeddmen akenni.

<span id="an_5:47">5:47</span> Ma yella tețțemsalamem d watmaten-nwen
kan, d acu n lxiṛ i txedmem ? Ula d imednuben xeddmen akken.

<span id="an_5:48">5:48</span> Sfut ihi akken yeṣfa Baba-twen n igenwan.

<span id="an_6:1">6:1</span> Ayen txeddmem i Sidi Ṛebbi, ur
t-id-sbegginet ara iwakken a kkun-walin medden, m'ulac ur tseɛɛum ara
lfayda ɣer Baba-twen yellan deg igenwan.

<span id="an_6:2">6:2</span> M'ara tseddqeḍ, ur țberriḥ ara am akken
xeddmen at sin wudmawen di leǧwameɛ neɣ deg iberdan, iwakken ad sɛun
ccan ɣer yemdanen. A wen iniɣ tideț : d ayagi kan i d lfayda-nsen.

<span id="an_6:3">6:3</span> Ma d kečč m'ara tseddqeḍ, ilaq afus-ik
ayeffus ur ițwali ara wayen ixeddem ufus-ik azelmaḍ ;

<span id="an_6:4">6:4</span> iwakken ssadaqa-inek aț-țeqqim di sser,
akka ara tețwaqebleḍ ɣer Baba Ṛebbi yețwalin ayen txeddmeḍ di sser.

<span id="an_6:5">6:5</span> M'ara tețẓallam, ur xeddmet ara am at sin
wudmawen iḥemmlen ad ẓallen s ibeddi di leǧwameɛ neɣ deg iberdan iwakken
a ten-walin medden. AA wen-iniɣ tideț : d ayagi kan i d lfayda-nsen.

<span id="an_6:6">6:6</span> Ma d kečč m'ara tebɣuḍ aț-țẓalleḍ, ṛuḥ
ekcem ɣer texxamt-ik, sekkeṛ tawwurt, tedɛuḍ di sser ɣer Baba Ṛebbi,
nețța yețwalin ayen yellan di sser, a k-id-iqbel.

<span id="an_6:7">6:7</span> M'ara tețẓallam, ur sṭuqqutet ara lehduṛ am
akken xeddmen at ddunit, ɣilen s lketṛa n imeslayen ara d țwaqeblen.

<span id="an_6:8">6:8</span> Ur ten-țɛanadet ara, axaṭer Baba Ṛebbi
yeẓra d acu teḥwaǧem uqbel a s-t-tessutrem.

<span id="an_6:9">6:9</span> Atah wamek ilaq aț-țețẓallam : AA Baba-tneɣ
yellan deg igenwan, iisem-ik ad ițwaqeddes,

<span id="an_6:10">6:10</span> lḥekma n tgeldit-ik a d-tass, llebɣi-k ad
idṛu di lqaɛa aakken yedṛa deg igenwan.

<span id="an_6:11">6:11</span> Efk-aɣ-d mkul ass tamɛict-nneɣ.

<span id="an_6:12">6:12</span> Semmeḥ-aɣ ddnubat-nneɣ aakken i nețsamaḥ
i wid i ɣ-iḍelmen.

<span id="an_6:13">6:13</span> Ssebɛed fell-aɣ ajeṛṛeb, ssellek-aɣ si
tḥila n Cciṭan. AAxaṭer ɣuṛ-ek i tella tgeldit, ttazmert d lɛaḍima i
dayem. Amin !

<span id="an_6:14">6:14</span> Ma yella tețsamaḥem i yemdanen ii
wen-ixeddmen cceṛ, Baba Ṛebbi yyellan deg igenwan a wen-isameḥ uula i
kunwi.

<span id="an_6:15">6:15</span> Lameɛna ma yella kkunwi ur tețsamaḥem ara
i wiyaḍ, aatan Baba Ṛebbi ur a wen-ițsamaḥ aara ula i kunwi
ddnubat-nwen.

<span id="an_6:16">6:16</span> Asmi ara tuẓummem, ur d tesbegginet ara
iman-nwen tḥeznem am at sin wudmawen issexsaṛen udmawen-nsen iwakken a
ten-țwalin yemdanen belli uẓamen. A wen-iniɣ tideț : d ayagi kan i d
lfayda-nsen.

<span id="an_6:17">6:17</span> Ma d kečč, m'ara tuẓumeḍ, ssired udem-ik,
tdehneḍ aqeṛṛuy-ik s rriḥa,

<span id="an_6:18">6:18</span> iwakken yiwen ur k-iɛeqqel belli tuẓameḍ.
Ilaq ayagi ad iqqim gar-ak d Baba Ṛebbi ițwalin ayen yellan di sser,
nețța a k-id-iqbel.

<span id="an_6:19">6:19</span> Ur ssexzanet ara igerrujen di ddunit anda
ara ten-yečč ubeɛɛuc d ṣṣdiḍ, anda ara ten-akren wid ifettken leḥyuḍ.

<span id="an_6:20">6:20</span> Meɛna sxeznet axiṛ igerrujen deg igenwan
anda ur llin ibeɛɛac d ṣṣdiḍ isserkuyen, anda ur zmiren ara imakaren ad
fetken neɣ ad akren.

<span id="an_6:21">6:21</span> Axaṭer anda yella ugerruj-ik, dinna ara
yili wul-ik.

<span id="an_6:22">6:22</span> Allen, ț-țiftilin n lǧețța, ma yella
seḥḥant wallen-ik, aț-țilliḍ s lekmal-ik di tafat.

<span id="an_6:23">6:23</span> Lameɛna, ma yella allen-ik ur seḥḥant
ara, aț-țiliḍ di ṭṭlam. Ma yella dɣa allen-ik ur seḥḥant ara, tafat
yellan deg-k d ṭṭlam, acḥal ihi berrik ṭṭlam i deg telliḍ.

<span id="an_6:24">6:24</span> Ur izmir yiwen ad iqdec ɣef sin imɛellmen
deg yiwet n tikkelt. Ma iḥemmel yiwen, ad ikṛeh wayeḍ ; ma yeṭṭef deg
yiwen, ad iḥqeṛ wayeḍ. Ur tezmirem ara ihi aț-țɛebdem Ṛebbi akk-d
idrimen !

<span id="an_6:25">6:25</span> Daymi i wen-d-qqaṛeɣ : ur țḥebbiṛet ara i
tudert-nwen, ɣef wayen ara teččem d wayen ara teswem akk-d wayen ara
telsem. Acu i gesɛan azal, ț-țudert neɣ d lqut ? D lǧețța neɣ d llebsa ?
Tudert tugar lqut, lǧețța tugar llebsa !

<span id="an_6:26">6:26</span> Walit igṭaṭ ( ifṛax ) deg igenwan : ur
zerrɛen, ur meggren, ur jemmɛen ula d acemma ɣer ikuffan, meɛna
Baba-twen yellan deg igenwan, yețțak-asen-d tamɛict-nsen. Eɛni ur teswim
ara akteṛ n yefṛax ?

<span id="an_6:27">6:27</span> Anwa i gzemren s uḥebbeṛ, ad yernu kra n
wussan i leɛmeṛ-is ?

<span id="an_6:28">6:28</span> Iwacu ara tḥebbṛem ɣef llebsa ? Walit
amek i gemmun ijeǧǧigen n lexla : ur zeṭṭen, ur țellmen,

<span id="an_6:29">6:29</span> lameɛna a wen-iniɣ : ula d agellid Sliman
s yiman-is di ccan-is ameqqran, ur yelsi am yiwen seg-sen.

<span id="an_6:30">6:30</span> Ma yella Ṛebbi islusuy akka leḥcic yellan
di lexla ass-agi, azekka ad ițwadeggeṛ ɣer tmes, amek ur kkun-islusu ara
ula d kunwi ay imdanen ixuṣṣen di liman ?

<span id="an_6:31">6:31</span> Kkset anezgum i yiman-nwen, ur qqaṛet ara
: d acu ara nečč, d acu ara nsew neɣ d acu ara nels ?

<span id="an_6:32">6:32</span> Axaṭer ayagi d imejhal i gețḥebbiṛen
fell-as. Ma d Baba-twen yellan deg igenwan, yeẓra ayen akk teḥwaǧem !

<span id="an_6:33">6:33</span> Nadit uqbel ɣef tgeldit n Sidi Ṛebbi d
wayen yellan d lḥeqq, ayen nniḍen meṛṛa d nețța ara wen-t-id yefken.

<span id="an_6:34">6:34</span> Ur țḥebbiṛet ara ihi i uzekka, axaṭer
azekka s unezgum-is weḥd-es. Yal ass s leɛtab-ines !

<span id="an_7:1">7:1</span> Ur țḥasabet ara wiyaḍ iwakken ur
kkun-ițḥasab ula d yiwen.

<span id="an_7:2">7:2</span> Akken tețḥasabem wiyaḍ ara kkun-iḥaseb Sidi
Ṛebbi. A wen-d-iktil s lkil s wayes tețțektilim i wiyaḍ.

<span id="an_7:3">7:3</span> Acuɣeṛ tețmuqquleḍ axeclaw yellan di tiṭ n
gma-k, kečč ur nețwali ara tigejdit yellan di tiṭ-ik ?

<span id="an_7:4">7:4</span> Amek ara tiniḍ i gma-k : « Eǧǧ-iyi ad kkseɣ
axeclaw-nni yellan di tiṭ-ik, » kečč yesɛan tigejdit di tiṭ-ik ?

<span id="an_7:5">7:5</span> A bu sin wudmawen ! Ekkes uqbel tigejdit
yellan di tiṭ-ik, imiren aț-țwaliḍ amek ara d-tekkseḍ axeclaw yellan di
tiṭ n gma-k.

<span id="an_7:6">7:6</span> Ur țțaket ara ayen yeṣfan i yeqjan, ur
ṭeggiṛet ara tiɛeqcin ɣlayen zdat yilfan, m'ulac a ten ṛekḍen yerna a
d-zzin fell-awen a kkun-gezren.

<span id="an_7:7">7:7</span> Ssutret, a wen-d-ițunefk ! Nadit, aț-țafem
! Sqerbebbet, a wen-d-ldin !

<span id="an_7:8">7:8</span> Axaṭer kra n win ara issutren, a
s-d-ițțunefk ! Win ițnadin, ad yaf ! A s-d-teldi tewwurt i win ara
isṭebṭben.

<span id="an_7:9">7:9</span> Anwa deg-wen ara yefken ablaḍ i mmi-s ma
yessuter-as-d aɣṛum ?

<span id="an_7:10">7:10</span> Neɣ, anwa deg-wen ara yefken azrem i
mmi-s ma yella yessuter-as-d aslem ?

<span id="an_7:11">7:11</span> Ma yella kunwi yellan d imcumen tessnem
aț-țefkem ayen yelhan i warraw-nwen, amek Baba twen yellan deg igenwan
ur d-ițțak ara ayen yelhan i wid ara s-t-issutren ?

<span id="an_7:12">7:12</span> Ihi, xedmet i wiyaḍ ayen i tebɣam a
wen-t-xedmen i kunwi, axaṭer akka i ɣ-d-tweṣṣa ccariɛa n Musa akk-d
lenbiya.

<span id="an_7:13">7:13</span> Kecmet si tewwurt iḍeyqen ! Axaṭer acḥal
tewseɛ tewwurt, acḥal yeshel webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger, yerna aṭas i
gețɛeddayen syenna.

<span id="an_7:14">7:14</span> Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ
webrid yețțawin ɣer tudert yerna drus i gețɛeddayen syenna.

<span id="an_7:15">7:15</span> Ḥadret iman-nwen si lenbiya n lekdeb !
Țțasen-d ɣuṛ-wen am izamaren, nutni ɣer daxel d uccanen.

<span id="an_7:16">7:16</span> A ten-tɛeqlem s lecɣal-nsen. UUr
d-nțekkes ara tiẓurin seg inijel, neɣ lexṛif seg isennanen.

<span id="an_7:17">7:17</span> Ttejṛa yelhan, tețțak-ed lfakya yelhan,
yir ttejṛa tețțak-ed lfakya n diri.

<span id="an_7:18">7:18</span> Ttejṛa yelhan ur tezmir ara a d-tefk yir
lfakya, akken daɣen yir ttejṛa ur tezmir ara a d-tefk lfakya yelhan.

<span id="an_7:19">7:19</span> Yal ttejṛa ur d-nețțak ara lfakya lɛali
aț-țețwagzem, aț-țețwaḍeggeṛ ɣer tmes.

<span id="an_7:20">7:20</span> S wakka, s lecɣal-nsen ara tɛeqlem
lenbiya n lekdeb.

<span id="an_7:21">7:21</span> Mačči d wid kan i yi-d-iqqaṛen : « A
Sidi, a Sidi » ara ikecmen ɣer tgelda n igenwan, meɛna d wid ixeddmen
lebɣi n Baba yellan deg igenwan.

<span id="an_7:22">7:22</span> Aṭas ara yi-d-yinin ass n lḥisab : « a
Sidi a Sidi, s yisem-ik i nbecceṛ imeslayen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, s yisem-ik i
nessufeɣ leǧnun, s yisem-ik i nexdem aṭas n lbeṛhanat ! »

<span id="an_7:23">7:23</span> Dɣa a sen-d-rreɣ : beɛdet akkin fell-i a
wid ixeddmen cceṛ, ur kkun ssineɣ ara !

<span id="an_7:24">7:24</span> Akka, s kra n win yesmeḥsisen i wawal-iw
yerna ixeddem-it, ițemcabi ɣer wemdan aɛeqli yebnan lsas n wexxam-is ɣef
wezṛu.

<span id="an_7:25">7:25</span> Ageffur ( lehwa ) yeɣli-d, isaffen
ḥemlen-d, aḍu ihubb-ed ɣef wexxam-nni, meɛna ur yeɣli ara, axaṭer
lsas-is yers ɣef wezṛu.

<span id="an_7:26">7:26</span> Ma d win ismeḥsisen i wawal iw, ur
nxeddem ara wayen i d-qqaṛeɣ, icuba ɣer wemdan ur nețxemmim ara, i
gebnan axxam-is ɣef ṛṛmel ;

<span id="an_7:27">7:27</span> yeɣli-d ugeffur, ḥemlen-d isaffen,
ihubb-ed waḍu ɣef wexxam-nni, imiren yeɣli. Lexsaṛa-s ț-țameqqrant !

<span id="an_7:28">7:28</span> Mi gfukk Sidna Ɛisa aselmed, lɣaci akk
wehmen deg imeslayen-ines,

<span id="an_7:29">7:29</span> axaṭer isselmad-iten s tissas, mačči am
lecyux-nsen.

<span id="an_8:1">8:1</span> Mi d-yuder Sidna Ɛisa seg udrar, aṭas n
lɣaci i t-id-itebɛen.

<span id="an_8:2">8:2</span> Ataya yiwen wemdan ihelken lbeṛs yusa-d
ɣuṛ-es, iseǧǧed zdat-es, yenna-yas : A Sidi, ma yella tebɣiḍ, tzemreḍ a
yi-tseḥluḍ.

<span id="an_8:3">8:3</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessers afus-is fell-as,
yenna-yas : Bɣiɣ ! Ili-k teḥliḍ ! IImiren kan iḥla wergaz-nni si
lbeṛs-ines, yeṣfa weglim-is.

<span id="an_8:4">8:4</span> Dɣa Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Ḥader aț-țeḥkuḍ
ula i yiwen ɣef wayagi, meɛna ṛuḥ ɣer yiwen si lmuqedmin a k-iẓer, ad
iwali belli teṣfiḍ, tefkeḍ lweɛda-nni n tezdeg s wayes i wen-d-yumeṛ
nnbi Musa, iwakken ayagi a sen-yili d țbut.

<span id="an_8:5">8:5</span> Akken i gekcem Sidna Ɛisa ɣer temdint n
Kafernaḥum, ataya yiwen umeqqran n lɛeskeṛ n Ṛuman iqeṛṛeb ed ɣuṛ-es,
iḥellel-it, yenna yas :

<span id="an_8:6">8:6</span> A Sidi, aqeddac-iw yenṭer, atan iḍleq deg
wexxam, yekref !

<span id="an_8:7">8:7</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Ad ṛuḥeɣ a
t-sseḥluɣ.

<span id="an_8:8">8:8</span> Ameqqran n lɛeskeṛ yerra-yas : A Sidi, ur
uklaleɣ ara aț-țkecmeḍ ɣer wexxam-iw, meɛna ini-d kan yiwen n wawal,
aqeddac-iw ad iḥlu.

<span id="an_8:9">8:9</span> Axaṭer nekk s yiman-iw akken sɛiɣ wid
iḥekmen fell-i, i sɛiɣ wid yellan seddaw n lḥekma-w. Ad iniɣ i yiwen ṛuḥ
ad iṛuḥ, ad iniɣ i wayeḍ aṛwaḥ a d-yas, ad iniɣ daɣen i uqeddac-iw :
xdem aya, a t-ixdem.

<span id="an_8:10">8:10</span> Mi gesla Sidna Ɛisa imeslayen-agi
itɛeǧǧeb, yenna i wid yellan dinna : A wen-iniɣ tideț, ger wat Isṛail
meṛṛa ur ufiɣ ara liman am wagi.

<span id="an_8:11">8:11</span> A wen-iniɣ daɣen : aṭas ara d-yasen si
cceṛq d lɣeṛb, ad ṭṭfen imukan ɣer tama n Ibṛahim, n Isḥaq akk-d Yeɛqub
di tgelda n igenwan.

<span id="an_8:12">8:12</span> Meɛna aṭas seg wid i gɣilen ad weṛten
tagelda ara yețwaḍeggṛen ɣer beṛṛa, ɣer ṭṭlam anda ara ilin imeṭṭawen,
nndama tameqqrant akk-d weqṛac n tuɣmas.

<span id="an_8:13">8:13</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna i umeqqran-nni n lɛeskeṛ
: Ṛuḥ, imi tumneḍ atan wayen i tḍelbeḍ a k-id-yaweḍ ! DDi teswiɛt-nni,
yeḥla uqeddac-is.

<span id="an_8:14">8:14</span> Sidna Ɛisa iṛuḥ ɣer wexxam n Buṭrus, yufa
taḍeggalt n Buṭrus deg usu tuɣ-iț tawla.

<span id="an_8:15">8:15</span> Innul afus-is, dɣa teffeɣ-iț tawla-nni.
Imiren kan tekker-ed, tebda tqeddec-asen.

<span id="an_8:16">8:16</span> Mi geɣli yiṭij, wwin-d i Sidna Ɛisa aṭas
n yemdanen ițwamelken. S wawal-is, issufeɣ seg-sen leǧnun yerna yesseḥla
imuḍan meṛṛa.

<span id="an_8:17">8:17</span> Ixdem ayagi iwakken ad ițwakemmel wawal i
d-yenna nnbi Iceɛya : Yewwi leɛyub-nneɣ , iɛebba lehlakat-nneɣ .

<span id="an_8:18">8:18</span> Sidna Ɛisa mi gwala annect-nni n lɣaci
yezzi-yas-d, yumeṛ i inelmaden-is ad zegren ɣer ugemmaḍ n lebḥeṛ.

<span id="an_8:19">8:19</span> Yiwen lɛalem n ccariɛa iqeṛṛeb ɣer Sidna
Ɛisa, yenna-yas : A Sidi, anda teddiḍ ad dduɣ.

<span id="an_8:20">8:20</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Uccanen sɛan
lɣiṛan, ifṛax n igenni sɛan leɛcuc, ma d Mmi-s n bunadem ur yesɛi ara
anda ara yessers aqeṛṛuy-is.

<span id="an_8:21">8:21</span> Yiwen seg inelmaden-is, yenna-yas : A
Sidi, semmeḥ-iyi ad ṛuḥeɣ ad meḍleɣ baba.

<span id="an_8:22">8:22</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Ddu yid-i eǧǧ wid
yemmuten ad meḍlen lmegtin-nsen.

<span id="an_8:23">8:23</span> Sidna Ɛisa yuli ɣer teflukt, ddan yid-es
inelmaden-is.

<span id="an_8:24">8:24</span> Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, tekker-ed tbuciḍant
di lebḥeṛ armi tɣumm teflukt-nni s lemwaji. Sidna Ɛisa yella iṭṭes.

<span id="an_8:25">8:25</span> Qeṛṛben-d ɣuṛ-es inelmaden-is,
ssakin-t-id, nnan-as : A Sidi, sellek-aɣ m'ulac a nemmet !

<span id="an_8:26">8:26</span> Yenna-yasen : Acimi tuggadem, a wid iwumi
ixuṣṣ liman ! IImiren ikker, yumeṛ i waḍu d lebḥeṛ ad rsen dɣa ters-ed
talwit ț-țameqqrant.

<span id="an_8:27">8:27</span> Wid iḥedṛen, tɛeǧǧben qqaṛen : Anwa-t
wagi ? Ula d aḍu d lebḥeṛ țțaɣen-as awal !

<span id="an_8:28">8:28</span> Mi gewweḍ Sidna Ɛisa agemmaḍ i lebḥeṛ,
ɣer tmurt n at Gadaṛa, a ten-aya sin yergazen yețwazedɣen, ffɣen-d si
tmeqbeṛt, mmugren-t-id. Yiwen ur izmir ad iɛeddi seg webrid-nni axaṭer
weɛṛen aṭas.

<span id="an_8:29">8:29</span> Bdan țɛeggiḍen : D acu i tebɣiḍ ɣuṛ-nneɣ
a Mmi-s n Ṛebbi ? Tusiḍ-ed iwakken a ɣ-tɛețbeḍ uqbel lweqt ?

<span id="an_8:30">8:30</span> Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit
tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna.

<span id="an_8:31">8:31</span> Leǧnun-nni țḥellilen Sidna Ɛisa,
qqaṛen-as : Ma tessufɣeḍ-aɣ, ceggeɛ-aɣ ɣer tqeḍɛit-ihina n yilfan.

<span id="an_8:32">8:32</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Ṛuḥet ! FFfɣen-d
si sin-nni n yemdanen, kecmen deg yilfan-nni. IImiren kan, grarben ɣer
daxel n lebḥeṛ, ɣeṛqen, mmuten akk.

<span id="an_8:33">8:33</span> Imeksawen-nni rewlen, ṛuḥen ɣer temdint
ad ḥkun ayen akk yedṛan d yergazen-nni yețwamelken.

<span id="an_8:34">8:34</span> Imezdaɣ akk n temdint ffɣen-d ɣer Sidna
Ɛisa ; mi d-wwḍen ɣuṛ-es, ḥellelen-t ad iffeɣ si tmurt-nsen.

<span id="an_9:1">9:1</span> Sidna Ɛisa yuli ɣer teflukt, yezger lebḥeṛ
yuɣal ɣer temdint n Kafernaḥum.

<span id="an_9:2">9:2</span> Wwin-as-d yiwen wukrif iḍleq ɣef wusu. MMi
gwala liman n yemdanen-agi, yenna i wukrif-nni : Ur țțaggad ara a mmi,
țwaɛeffan ak ddnubat-ik.

<span id="an_9:3">9:3</span> Llan dinna kra si lɛulama țxemmimen deg
wulawen-nsen qqaṛen : Argaz-agi yekfeṛ !

<span id="an_9:4">9:4</span> Dɣa Sidna Ɛisa yeẓran ayen țxemmimen,
yenna-yasen : Acuɣeṛ yir axemmem-agi deg ulawen-nwen ?

<span id="an_9:5">9:5</span> D acu i gsehlen a t-id-iniɣ : « Țwaɛfan-ak
ddnubat-ik neɣ kker telḥuḍ » ?

<span id="an_9:6">9:6</span> Meɛna iwakken aț-țeẓrem belli Mmi-s n
bunadem yesɛa tazmert di ddunit-agi ad yeɛfu ddnubat... YYenna i
wukrif-nni : Ekker, ddem usu-inek tṛuḥeḍ ɣer wexxam-ik !

<span id="an_9:7">9:7</span> Imiren, argaz-nni yekker, iṛuḥ ɣer
wexxam-is.

<span id="an_9:8">9:8</span> Mi walan ayagi, lɣaci akk ikcem-iten lxuf,
țḥemmiden Sidi Ṛebbi, imi i d-ifka tazmert am tagi i yemdanen.

<span id="an_9:9">9:9</span> Mi gɛedda zdat wexxam anda țxelliṣen
tabzert, ( leɣṛama ) Sidna Ɛisa iwala yiwen umekkas isem-is Matta,
yenna-yas : Ddu-d yid-i ! IImiren kan ikker Matta, yedda yid-es.

<span id="an_9:10">9:10</span> Mi llan tețțen deg wexxam n Matta, aṭas n
imekkasen akk-d yir imdanen i d-yusan, qqimen akk-d Sidna Ɛisa d
inelmaden-is, tețțen yid-sen.

<span id="an_9:11">9:11</span> Ifariziyen mi walan ayagi nnan i
inelmaden-is : Acuɣeṛ Ssid-nwen iteț akk-d imekkasen d yir imdanen ?

<span id="an_9:12">9:12</span> Sidna Ɛisa yesla i wayen i d nnan,
yerra-yasen : Mačči d wid iseḥḥan i geḥwaǧen ṭṭbib, meɛna d wid ihelken.

<span id="an_9:13">9:13</span> Meyzet ɣef lmeɛna n wawal-agi yellan di
tira iqedsen : D ulawen yeṣfan i bɣiɣ mačči d iseflawen n lmal. AAxaṭer
ur d-usiɣ ara ad ssiwleɣ i iḥeqqiyen iwakken a d uɣalen ɣer webrid,
meɛna i imednuben.

<span id="an_9:14">9:14</span> Inelmaden n Yeḥya aɣeṭṭas usan-d ɣer
Sidna Ɛisa nnan-as : Acuɣeṛ nukkni akk-d ifariziyen nețțuẓum ma d
inelmaden-ik ur țțuẓumen ara ?

<span id="an_9:15">9:15</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Eɛni inebgawen n
tmeɣṛa zemren ad ilin di leḥzen skud yella yesli yid-sen ? A d-yas wass
i deg ara sen-ițwakkes yesli, imiren ad uẓummen.

<span id="an_9:16">9:16</span> Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i
uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, axaṭer tafaweț-nni tajḍiṭ aț-țejbed aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim,
acerrig-nni ad innerni.

<span id="an_9:17">9:17</span> Ur nețɛemmiṛ ara daɣen iyeddiden iqdimen
s ccṛab ajdid, neɣ m'ulac ad fellqen, ccṛab ad inɣel, iyeddiden ad
xesṛen ; meɛna a nerr ccṛab ajdid deg yeddiden ijdiden, s wakkenni ccṛab
d uyeddid ad țwaḥerzen.

<span id="an_9:18">9:18</span> Mazal Sidna Ɛisa ițmeslay, yusa-d yiwen n
ccix n lǧameɛ iseǧǧed zdat-es, yenna-yas : Tura kan i temmut yelli, di
leɛnaya-k as-ed aț-țserseḍ afus-ik fell-as, a d-teḥyu !

<span id="an_9:19">9:19</span> Sidna Ɛisa ikker yedda yid-es nețța d
inelmaden-is.

<span id="an_9:20">9:20</span> Ațaya yiwet n tmeṭṭut yuḍnen ssiq tnac
iseggasen aya, tekka-yas-d si deffir, tennul tacḍaṭ n ubeṛnus-is,

<span id="an_9:21">9:21</span> axaṭer teqqaṛ deg ul-is : « lemmer zemreɣ
ad nnaleɣ ɣas ula ț-țacḍaṭ n ubeṛnus-is, ad ḥluɣ. »

<span id="an_9:22">9:22</span> Sidna Ɛisa yezzi ɣer deffir, mi ț-iwala
yenna-yas : Ur țțaggad a yell-i, liman-im isseḥla-kkem. SSeg imiren
tameṭṭut-nni teḥla.

<span id="an_9:23">9:23</span> Mi gewweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer wexxam n
ccix-nni, yufa lɣaci țmeǧǧiden, yerna nhewwalen meṛṛa. Yenna-yasen :

<span id="an_9:24">9:24</span> Ffɣet syagi, taqcict ur temmut ara, d
iḍes kan i teṭṭes. DDɣa țmesxiṛen fell-as.

<span id="an_9:25">9:25</span> Mi ssufɣen lɣaci, ikcem, yeṭṭef-ed
taqcict-nni seg ufus, dɣa tekker-ed.

<span id="an_9:26">9:26</span> Yeffeɣ lexbaṛ-agi di tmurt meṛṛa.

<span id="an_9:27">9:27</span> Mi gṛuḥ Sidna Ɛisa syenna, tebɛen-t sin
iderɣalen, țɛeggiḍen : A mmi-s n Sidna Dawed, ḥunn fell-aɣ !

<span id="an_9:28">9:28</span> Mi gewweḍ ɣer wexxam, iderɣalen-nni
kecmen ɣuṛ-es, dɣa Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Tumnem belli zemreɣ a wen
xedmeɣ ayen i yi-d-tessutrem ? RRran-as : Ih a Sidi numen !

<span id="an_9:29">9:29</span> Innul allen-nsen, yenna : A wen-ițwaxdem
s wakken yella liman-nwen !

<span id="an_9:30">9:30</span> Dɣa yuɣal-asen-d yeẓri. Sidna Ɛisa yeggul
deg-sen : Ɣuṛ-wat ad iffeɣ lexbaṛ ɣef wayagi !

<span id="an_9:31">9:31</span> Meɛna akken kan ffɣen, bdan aberreḥ,
lexbaṛ-nni yekka-d meṛṛa tamurt.

<span id="an_9:32">9:32</span> Mi ṛuḥen sin-nni, a ten-aya wiyaḍ
wwin-as-d yiwen wergaz i gesgugem uṛuḥani.

<span id="an_9:33">9:33</span> Akken issufeɣ Sidna Ɛisa aṛuḥani-nni,
agugam-nni yebda ițmeslay. Lɣaci akk tɛeǧben, qqaṛen : Leɛmeṛ neẓri
ayagi di tmurt n wat Isṛail !

<span id="an_9:34">9:34</span> Lameɛna ifariziyen qqaṛen : S tezmert n
ugellid n leǧnun i ten-issufuɣ.

<span id="an_9:35">9:35</span> Sidna Ɛisa yekka-d ɣef temdinin ț-țudrin
meṛṛa, yesselmad di leǧwameɛ nsen, yețbecciṛ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ n tgeldit n
Sidi Ṛebbi, isseḥlay mkul aṭan d mkul lɛib.

<span id="an_9:36">9:36</span> Sidna Ɛisa tegzem tasa-s mi gwala
annect-nni n lɣaci ɛyan, feclen, ḥeznen am ulli ur nesɛi ameksa .

<span id="an_9:37">9:37</span> Dɣa yenna i inelmaden-is : Tamegra
meqqṛet, meɛna drus ifellaḥen i gellan.

<span id="an_9:38">9:38</span> Ḥellelet ihi bab n tmegra a d iceggeɛ
ixeddamen ɣer tmegra-s.

<span id="an_10:1">10:1</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessawel i tnac inelmaden-is,
yefka-yasen tazmert s wayes ara ssufuɣen leǧnun, ara seḥluyen mkul aṭan
d mkul lɛib.

<span id="an_10:2">10:2</span> Atnan yismawen n tnac-nni inelmaden n
Sidna Ɛisa :Amezwaru d Semɛun ițțusemman Buṭrus akk-d gma-s Andriyus,
Yeɛqub mmi-s n Zabadi akk-d gma-s Yuḥenna,

<span id="an_10:3">10:3</span> Filibus d Bartelmay, Suma akk-d Matta
amekkas n tebzert, Yeɛqub mmi-s n Ḥalfi akk-d Taddi ;

<span id="an_10:4">10:4</span> Semɛun awaṭani, Yudas n Qeṛyut, win akken
ixedɛen Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_10:5">10:5</span> Sidna Ɛisa iceggeɛ tnac inelmaden-is,
iweṣṣa-ten : Ur țṛuḥut ara ɣer tmura tibeṛṛaniyin, ur keččmet ara ɣer
temdinin n at Samarya ;

<span id="an_10:6">10:6</span> ṛuḥet axiṛ ɣer wat Isṛail yellan am ulli
iḍaɛen.

<span id="an_10:7">10:7</span> M'ara tețțeddum, țbecciṛet qqaṛet : «
Ațaya tgeldit n igenwan tqeṛṛeb-ed » !

<span id="an_10:8">10:8</span> Sseḥlut imuḍan, sseḥyut-ed lmegtin,
ssizdeget wid ihelken lbeṛs, ssufɣet leǧnun. Akken i wen-d-ițțunefk mbla
idrimen, fket ula d kunwi mbla idrimen.

<span id="an_10:9">10:9</span> Ur țțawit yid-wen ama d ddheb, ama d
lfeṭṭa, ama d idrimen ;

<span id="an_10:10">10:10</span> ur țțawit yid-wen agrab neɣ sin
iqendyaṛ, ur țțawit irkasen neɣ aɛekkaz, axaṭer axeddam yuklal lqut-is.

<span id="an_10:11">10:11</span> Di yal tamdint neɣ taddart anda ara
tkecmem, steqsit ma yella win ara yesṭerḥben yis-wen, qqimet ɣuṛ-es
alamma tekkrem aț-țṛuḥem.

<span id="an_10:12">10:12</span> M'ara tkecmem ɣer yiwen wexxam, sellmet
fell-asen,

<span id="an_10:13">10:13</span> ma sṭerḥben yis-wen, lehna-nwen aț-țers
fell-asen ; ma yella ur sṭerḥben ara yis-wen, lehna-nwen aț-țeqqim
ɣuṛ-wen.

<span id="an_10:14">10:14</span> M'ur qbilen ara ad sṭreḥben yis-wen neɣ
ad semḥessen i wawal, ffɣet seg wexxam-nni neɣ si temdint nni, zwit ula
d aɣebbaṛ seg iḍaṛṛen nwen.

<span id="an_10:15">10:15</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : ass n lḥisab,
imezdaɣ n temdint-agi ad țțuɛaqben akteṛ n temdinin n Sudum akk-d Gumuṛ.

<span id="an_10:16">10:16</span> Atan, a kkun-ceggɛeɣ am ulli ger
wuccanen, ḥeṛcet ihi am izerman, sɛut neyya am yetbiren.

<span id="an_10:17">10:17</span> Ḥadret ɣef yiman-nwen, axaṭer kra n
yemdanen a kkun-sbedden ɣer ccṛeɛ; yerna a kkun-wten s ujelkaḍ di
leǧwameɛ-nsen.

<span id="an_10:18">10:18</span> Ɣef ddemma n yisem-iw, a kkun-sbedden
zdat lḥekkam akk-d igelliden, iwakken am nutni am at leǧnas nniḍen, ad
slen s yisem-iw.

<span id="an_10:19">10:19</span> M'ara kkun-ṭṭfen, ur țḥebbiṛet ara ɣef
wamek ara temmeslayem, neɣ ɣef wayen ara d-tinim, imeslayen ara d-tinim,
a wen-d-țțunefken di teswiɛt nni kan.

<span id="an_10:20">10:20</span> Axaṭer mačči d kunwi ara imeslayen,
meɛna d Ṛṛuḥ n Baba Ṛebbi ara d-imeslayen seg-wen.

<span id="an_10:21">10:21</span> Amdan ad yefk gma-s ɣer lmut, ababat ad
yefk mmi-s, dderya a d kkren ɣer imawlan-nsen, a ten ssiwḍen ɣer lmut.

<span id="an_10:22">10:22</span> A kkun-keṛhen irkul ɣef ddemma n
yisem-iw, meɛna win ara yeṭṭfen alamma ț-țaggara, ad ițțusellek.

<span id="an_10:23">10:23</span> M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n temdint,
rewlet ɣer tayeḍ. A wen-iniɣ tideț : Mmi-s n bunadem a d-yuɣal uqbel a
d-tekkem tudrin meṛṛa n tmurt n wat Isṛail.

<span id="an_10:24">10:24</span> Ulac anelmad yugaren ccix-is neɣ
aqeddac yellan sennig umɛellem is.

<span id="an_10:25">10:25</span> Akken ițwaḥseb ccix ara yețwaḥseb
unelmad-is. Daɣen akken yella wemɛellem ara yili uqeddac-is. MMa semman
i bab n wexxam Balzabul iḥekkmen ɣef leǧnun, amek ur țsemmin ara akkenni
i wat wexxam-is !

<span id="an_10:26">10:26</span> Ur ten-țaggadet ara ihi ! Axaṭer kra n
wayen yeffren a d-iḍheṛ, kra n lbaḍna yellan a d-tban.

<span id="an_10:27">10:27</span> Ayen i wen-qqaṛeɣ deg iḍ, init-eț
ɛinani deg wass, ayen slan imeẓẓuɣen-nwen di sser, berrḥet-eț deg
iberdan.

<span id="an_10:28">10:28</span> Ur țțaggadet ara wid ineqqen lǧețța
lameɛna ur zmiren ara ad nnɣen ṛṛuḥ, aggadet win izemren ad iḍeggeṛ ṛṛuḥ
akk-d lǧețța ɣer ǧahennama.

<span id="an_10:29">10:29</span> Eɛni ur znuzun ara sin iẓiwcen s uṣuṛdi
? Meɛna ula d yiwen deg-sen ur d-iɣelli ɣer lqaɛa mbla lebɣi n Baba
Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_10:30">10:30</span> Ula d anẓaden uqeṛṛuy-nwen țwaḥesben
irkulli.

<span id="an_10:31">10:31</span> Ihi ur țțaggadet ara : tesɛam azal
akteṛ n waṭas n iẓiwcen !

<span id="an_10:32">10:32</span> Kra win ara yessetḥin s yisem-iw zdat
yemdanen, ula d nekk, ad ssetḥiɣ yis zdat Baba yellan deg igenwan.

<span id="an_10:33">10:33</span> Kra win ara yi-nekṛen zdat yemdanen, a
t-nekkṛeɣ ula d nekk zdat Baba yellan deg igenwan.

<span id="an_10:34">10:34</span> Ɣuṛ-wat aț-țɣilem d lehna i d wwiɣ ɣer
ddunit ; mačči d lehna i d-wwiɣ, meɛna d ccwal i d-wwiɣ.

<span id="an_10:35">10:35</span> Axaṭer wwiɣ-d lfiṛaq ger weqcic d
baba-s, ger teqcict d yemma-s, ger teslit ț-țemɣaṛt-is,

<span id="an_10:36">10:36</span> a d-kkren yeɛdawen seg at wexxam.

<span id="an_10:37">10:37</span> Win iḥemmlen baba-s d yemma-s neɣ mmi-s
d yelli-s akteṛ iw ur yuklal ara ad yili d anelmad-iw.

<span id="an_10:38">10:38</span> Kra win ur neqbil ara ad inɛețțab ɣef
ddemma n yisem-iw iwakken ad iyi-itbeɛ, ur yuklal ara ad yili d
anelmad-iw.

<span id="an_10:39">10:39</span> Win iḥerzen taṛwiḥt-is, a s-tṛuḥ, ma d
win ara isebblen taṛwiḥt-is ɣef ddemma-w ad yuɣal a ț-yaf.

<span id="an_10:40">10:40</span> Win isṭerḥben yis-wen, yis-i i
gesṭerḥeb, win isṭerḥben yis-i, isṭerḥeb s win i yi-d-iceggɛen.

<span id="an_10:41">10:41</span> Win isṭerḥben s nnbi imi s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i
d-yusa a s-d-ițțunefk wayen yuklal nnbi, win isṭerḥben s uḥeqqi imi d
aḥeqqi i gella, a s-d-ițunefk wayen yuklal uḥeqqi.

<span id="an_10:42">10:42</span> Kra win ara yefken lkas n waman
isemmaḍen i yiwen seg imecṭuḥen-agi imi d anelmad-iw i gella, a wen-iniɣ
tideț : ur a s-ițṛuḥ ara lḥeqq yuklal.

<span id="an_11:1">11:1</span> Mi gweṣṣa tnac-nni inelmaden is, Sidna
Ɛisa iṛuḥ syenna ad ibecceṛ di tudrin n leǧwahi-nni.

<span id="an_11:2">11:2</span> Yeḥya yellan di lḥebs, yesla s lecɣal n
Lmasiḥ, iceggeɛ ɣuṛ-es inelmaden is iwakken a s-inin :

<span id="an_11:3">11:3</span> D kečč i d win akken ara d yasen neɣ
ilaq-aɣ a nerǧu wayeḍ ?

<span id="an_11:4">11:4</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen-d : Ṛuḥet
ssiwḍet-as lexbaṛ i Yeḥya ɣef wayen twalam d wayen teslam :

<span id="an_11:5">11:5</span> Iderɣalen țwalin, iquḍaren leḥḥun,
ibeṛsiyen ṣeffun, iɛeẓẓugen sellen, lmegtin ḥeggun-d, lexbaṛ n lxiṛ
ițțubecceṛ i yimeɣban.

<span id="an_11:6">11:6</span> D aseɛdi win iwumi ur țțiliɣ ara d sebba
n tuccḍa ( ugur ) !

<span id="an_11:7">11:7</span> Mi ṛuḥen inelmaden-is, Sidna Ɛisa yebda
iheddeṛ i lɣaci ɣef Yeḥya : D acu i tṛuḥem a t-id-teẓrem deg unezṛuf ? D
aɣanim yețhuzzu waḍu ?

<span id="an_11:8">11:8</span> Ɣer wacu i tṛuḥem aț-țfeṛǧem ? ƔƔer yiwen
wergaz yelsan llebsa ifazen ? Wid yețlusun llebsa ifazen, deg ixxamen n
igelliden i țțilin.

<span id="an_11:9">11:9</span> Anwa i ɣer tṛuḥem a t-id-teẓrem ihi ? D
yiwen n nnbi ? Țideț ih, d nnbi ! A wen-iniɣ : yugar nnbi.

<span id="an_11:10">11:10</span> Axaṭer d nețța i ɣef yura : Atan
zewwreɣ zdat-ek amceggeɛ-inu, iwakken ad iheggi abrid zdat-ek.

<span id="an_11:11">11:11</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : ulac mmi-s n tmeṭṭut
yugaren Yeḥya aɣeṭṭas. Lameɛna, amecṭuḥ maḍi di tgelda n igenwan, meqqeṛ
akteṛ-is.

<span id="an_11:12">11:12</span> Seg wussan-nni i deg ițbecciṛ Yeḥya
aɣeṭṭas armi ț-țura, imdanen țnaɣen ɣef tgelda n igenwan, bɣan a
ț-țkecmen s ddreɛ.

<span id="an_11:13">11:13</span> Axaṭer ccariɛa n Musa d lenbiya
hedṛen-d ɣef tgelda n igenwan armi d lweqt n Yeḥya aɣeṭṭas.

<span id="an_11:14">11:14</span> Ma tebɣam aț-țfehmem, d nețța i d
Ilyas-nni ilaqen a d-yas.

<span id="an_11:15">11:15</span> Win yesɛan imeẓẓuɣen, isel-ed !

<span id="an_11:16">11:16</span> Ɣer wuɣuṛ ara metleɣ lǧil-agi ? Icuba
ɣer warrac yeqqimen deg uzniq, ssawalen i warrac nniḍen, qqaṛen asen :

<span id="an_11:17">11:17</span> Newwet ajewwaq uur tecḍiḥem ara, nnecna
cnawi n leḥzen uur tmeǧdem ara.

<span id="an_11:18">11:18</span> Axaṭer Yeḥya yusa-d, ur iteț ur itess,
tennam : « izdeɣ-it uṛuḥani. »

<span id="an_11:19">11:19</span> Mmi-s n bunadem yusa-d, iteț, itess am
wiyaḍ, teqqaṛem : «\` Ițxemmim kan ɣef wučči ț-țissit, d amdakkul n
imekkasen ixeddaɛen akk-d yir imdanen » lameɛna tideț tban-ed s
lecɣal-is.

<span id="an_11:20">11:20</span> Sidna Ɛisa ibda ițlumu timdinin nni i
deg ixdem aṭas n lbeṛhanat, axaṭer imezdaɣ-is ur d-uɣalen ara ɣer webrid
n Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_11:21">11:21</span> A nnger-im a tamdint n Kurazim ! A
nnger-im a tamdint n Bitsayda ! Axaṭer lemmer lbeṛhanat yedṛan deg-kkunt
dṛan di temdinin n Sur akk-d Sidun, tili imezdaɣ-nsent aṭas aya i
sburren tacekkaṛt n leḥzen, qqimen ɣef yiɣiɣden iwakken a d sbegnen
belli ndemmen uɣalen-d ɣer ubrid n Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_11:22">11:22</span> Daymi, imezdaɣ n temdinin-agi ad
țuɛaqben akteṛ n wid n temdinin n Sur akk-d Sidun.

<span id="an_11:23">11:23</span> Ula d kemm a tamdint n Kafernaḥum,
tɣileḍ aț-țaliḍ ɣer igenni ? Xaṭi ! Aț-țețwaḍeggreḍ ɣer laxeṛt ; axaṭer
lemmer di temdint n Sudum i dṛan lbeṛhanat i gedṛan ɣuṛ-em, tili
mazal-iț ar ass-a !

<span id="an_11:24">11:24</span> Daymi, ass n lḥisab anegaru
aț-țețțuɛaqbeḍ akteṛ n tmurt n Sudum.

<span id="an_11:25">11:25</span> Di lweqt-nni, Sidna Ɛisa inṭeq yenna :
Ḥemmdeɣ-k a Baba Ṛebbi, a Bab igenwan d lqaɛa, imi i d tessekneḍ i
imecṭaḥ ayen i teffreḍ i imusnawen d lɛuqal.

<span id="an_11:26">11:26</span> Ih a Baba Ṛebbi ! Ḥemmdeɣ-k imi d wagi
i d lebɣi-k.

<span id="an_11:27">11:27</span> Baba Ṛebbi yerra-d kullec ger
ifassen-iw. YYiwen ur yessin Mmi-s n Ṛebbi anagar Baba Ṛebbi ! Yiwen ur
issin daɣen Baba Ṛebbi anagar Mmi-s akk-d win iwumi yebɣa Mmi-s a
s-t-id-isken.

<span id="an_11:28">11:28</span> Aset-ed ɣuṛ-i a wid akk yeɛyan, iɛebban
taɛekkumt ẓẓayen, a wen-fkeɣ talwit d westeɛfu.

<span id="an_11:29">11:29</span> Refdet ɣef tuyat-nwen azaglu inu
tlemdem s ɣuṛ-i, axaṭer ul-iw yeččuṛ d ṛṛeḥma yerna d aḥnin, aț-țafem
talwit i teṛwiḥin-nwen.

<span id="an_11:30">11:30</span> Azaglu-inu yeshel, taɛekkumt-iw fsuset.

<span id="an_12:1">12:1</span> Yiwet n tikkelt, deg wass n ssebt yellan
d ass n westeɛfu, Sidna Ɛisa izger igran n yirden. Inelmaden-is lluẓen,
bdan țekksen-d tigedrin, tețțen-tent.

<span id="an_12:2">12:2</span> Ifariziyen mi ten-walan, nnan i Sidna
Ɛisa : Acuɣeṛ inelmaden-ik xeddmen ayen iḥeṛmen deg wass n westeɛfu ?

<span id="an_12:3">12:3</span> Meɛna Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Eɛni ur
teɣṛim ara wayen yexdem ugellid Dawed, mi gelluẓ nețța d wid yellan
yid-es ?

<span id="an_12:4">12:4</span> Mi gekcem ɣer wexxam iqedsen, yečča seg
weɣṛum-nni yețțunefken d lweɛda i lmuqedmin yerna yefka seg-s i
imdukkal-is !

<span id="an_12:5">12:5</span> Eɛni ur teɣṛim ara di tektabt n ccariɛa n
Musa belli lmuqedmin xeddmen ɣas akken d ass n westeɛfu yerna mačči d
leḥṛam fell-asen ?

<span id="an_12:6">12:6</span> Ihi a wen-d-iniɣ : yella dagi win yugaren
axxam iqedsen.

<span id="an_12:7">12:7</span> Lemmer tfehmem d acu i d lmeɛna n
wawal-agi : D ulawen yesɛan ṛṛeḥma i bɣiɣ mačči d isflawen n lmal ttili
ur tḥekkmem ara s lmut ɣef wid ur neḍlim ara !

<span id="an_12:8">12:8</span> Axaṭer Mmi-s n bunadem, d nețța i gḥekmen
ɣef wass n westeɛfu.

<span id="an_12:9">12:9</span> Syenna, yerra ɣer yiwen n lǧameɛ,

<span id="an_12:10">12:10</span> yella dinna yiwen wergaz iwumi yekref
ufus. Ifariziyen steqsan-t nnan-as : Eɛni iḥlel useḥlu deg wass n
westeɛfu ? SSteqsan-t akka, iwakken a s-d-afen sebba s wayes ara
t-sḍelmen.

<span id="an_12:11">12:11</span> Yerra-yasen : Anwa deg-wen yesɛan yiwet
n tixsi kan, ma yella teɣli ɣer tesraft deg wass n westeɛfu ur
ț-id-issalay ara ?

<span id="an_12:12">12:12</span> Eɛni tixsi teswa akteṛ n wemdan ? Ihi,
yeḥlel a nexdem lxiṛ deg wass n westeɛfu !

<span id="an_12:13">12:13</span> Imiren Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas i
wergaz-nni : Sleq-ed afus-ik ! YYeḍleq afus-is, dɣa yuɣal iṣeḥḥa am ufus
nniḍen.

<span id="an_12:14">12:14</span> Ifariziyen ffɣen, ṛuḥen mcawaṛen wway
gar-asen amek ara a s-d-afen sebba s wayes ara t-nɣen.

<span id="an_12:15">12:15</span> Mi gesla bɣan a t-nɣen, Sidna Ɛisa iṛuḥ
syenna. Aṭas i geddan yid-es, yesseḥlay imuḍan meṛṛa,

<span id="an_12:16">12:16</span> iqqaṛ-asen : Ɣuṛ-wat aț-țessufɣem
lexbaṛ !

<span id="an_12:17">12:17</span> Iwakken ad idṛu wayen yenna nnbi Iceɛya
:

<span id="an_12:18">12:18</span> Ataya uqeddac-iw i xtaṛeɣ, win eɛzizen
fell-i, deg-s i gella lfeṛḥ-iw. A d-yers Ṛṛuḥ-iw fell-as, ad ibecceṛ
lḥeqq i leǧnas.

<span id="an_12:19">12:19</span> Ur iskkaray ara ccwal, ur ițɛeggiḍ ara,
ur ițḥettim ara iman-is ɣef wiyaḍ.

<span id="an_12:20">12:20</span> Ur ițkemmil ara i uɣanim iceqqeqen, ur
isnusuy ara taftilt yețmețțaten, alamma yesbedd lḥeqq.

<span id="an_12:21">12:21</span> Imiren leǧnas meṛṛa ad ssirmen ɣuṛ-es,
fell-as ara țeklen.

<span id="an_12:22">12:22</span> Wwin-d i Sidna Ɛisa yiwen wergaz i
gesgugem, i gesderɣel uṛuḥani. Yesseḥla-t, yuɣal wergaz-nni iheddeṛ,
yețwali.

<span id="an_12:23">12:23</span> Lɣaci meṛṛa wehmen di Sidna Ɛisa qqaṛen
: Mačči d wagi i d mmi-s n Sidna Dawed, win akken ara d-yasen ?

<span id="an_12:24">12:24</span> Mi sen-slan ifariziyen nnan : Argaz-agi
yessufuɣ leǧnun s tezmert n Balzabul iḥekkmen ɣef leǧnun.

<span id="an_12:25">12:25</span> Sidna Ɛisa yeẓran ayen i țxemmimen,
yenna-yasen : Yal tagelda anda țnaɣen lɣaci wway gar-asen, aț-țuɣal
aț-țenger. YYal taddart neɣ yal axxam i deg țnaɣen imezdaɣ wway
gar-asen, ur d-yețɣimi ara.

<span id="an_12:26">12:26</span> Ma yella Cciṭan issufuɣ Cciṭan, atan
yebḍa d yiman-is ! Amek ihi ara d-tdum ddewla-s ?

<span id="an_12:27">12:27</span> Ma yella nekkini ssufuɣeɣ leǧnun s
tezmert n Balzabul, i warraw nwen s wacu i ten ssufuɣen ? Daymi, d
arraw-nwen ara kkun-iḥasben !

<span id="an_12:28">12:28</span> Meɛna ma yella nekkini s Ṛṛuḥ n Ṛebbi i
ssufuɣeɣ leǧnun, ihi tagelda n Ṛebbi ațan tewweḍ-ed armi d ɣuṛ-wen.

<span id="an_12:29">12:29</span> Yiwen ur yezmir ad ikcem ɣer wexxam n
wergaz iǧehden iwakken a s-iddem ayla-as ma yella ur t-yuriz ara uqbel,
meɛna m'ara t-yarez, imiren ad yizmir ad iddem ayen akk yellan deg
wexxam-is.

<span id="an_12:30">12:30</span> Win ur nelli ara yid-i, ixulef-iyi ;
win ur d-njemmeɛ ara yid-i ițḍeggiɛ !

<span id="an_12:31">12:31</span> Daymi i wen-qqaṛeɣ : Mkul ddnub d mkul
rregmat zemren ad țwasemmḥen i yemdanen, ma d rregmat ɣef Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen
ur țwasemmaḥent ara !

<span id="an_12:32">12:32</span> Yal win ara iregmen di Mmi-s n bunadem,
a s-ițwasameḥ, ma d win ara iregmen Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen, ur s-ițwasamaḥ ara ama
di lweqt-agi, ama di lweqt i d-iteddun.

<span id="an_12:33">12:33</span> Ɛeqlet ttejṛa ɣer lfakya-s : ma telha
ttejṛa, a d-tefk lfakya yelhan, ma yella diri-ț, a d-tefk lfakya n diri
!

<span id="an_12:34">12:34</span> A ccetla n izerman, amek ara d-tinim
ayen yelhan ma yella kunwi diri-kkun ? Axaṭer d ayen yellan deg ul i
d-ițeffɣen seg imi !

<span id="an_12:35">12:35</span> Argaz lɛali yessufuɣ-ed ayen yelhan seg
ugerruj yellan deg ul-is ma d amcum yessufuɣ-ed ayen n diri si lexzin n
diri yellan deg ul-is !

<span id="an_12:36">12:36</span> Aql-i nniɣ-awen-t : ass n lḥisab, ad
țțuḥasben yemdanen ɣef yal awal ur nesɛi lmeɛna i d-iffɣen seg yimi-nsen
;

