<span id="an_14:23">14:23</span> Mi ṛuḥen akk lɣaci-nni, yuli weḥd-es
ɣer wedrar iwakken ad iẓẓall, dɣa yeɣli-d yiḍ.

<span id="an_14:24">14:24</span> Taflukt-nni tella di tlemmast n lebḥeṛ,
lemwaji kkatent-eț axaṭer aḍu iqubel-iten-id.

<span id="an_14:25">14:25</span> Mi qṛib ad yali wass, ataya Sidna Ɛisa
iteddu-d ɣef wuḍar s ufella n waman.

<span id="an_14:26">14:26</span> Akken i t-walan ileḥḥu ɣef waman,
inelmaden-is xelɛen qqaṛen : D lexyal ! BBdan țɛeggiḍen s lxuf.

<span id="an_14:27">14:27</span> Meɛna imiren kan Sidna Ɛisa
yenna-yasen-d : Ur xellɛet ara, d nekk ! Ur țțaggadet ara !

<span id="an_14:28">14:28</span> Dɣa Buṭrus yenna-yas : A Sidi, ma yella
d keččini, efk-ed lameṛ a n-aseɣ ɣuṛ-ek ɣef wuḍar s ufella n waman.

<span id="an_14:29">14:29</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : As-ed ! BBuṭrus
yers-ed si teflukt, ileḥḥu ɣef waman, iteddu ɣer Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_14:30">14:30</span> Meɛna mi gwala yekker-ed waḍu, ikcem-it
lxuf, yebda izedder, dɣa iɛeggeḍ : A Sidi, sellek-iyi !

<span id="an_14:31">14:31</span> Imiren kan, Sidna Ɛisa yeḍleq afus-is,
ijbed-it-id yenna-yas : A win iwumi ixuṣṣ liman ! Acuɣeṛ i k-ikcem ccekk
?

<span id="an_14:32">14:32</span> Ulin ɣer teflukt di sin, dɣa yers
waḍu-nni.

<span id="an_14:33">14:33</span> Inelmaden-nni yellan di teflukt seǧǧden
zdat Sidna Ɛisa nnan-as : Ț-țideț, d kečč i d Mmi-s n Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_14:34">14:34</span> Zegren lebḥeṛ-nni, armi wwḍen ɣer tmurt
n Jiniṣaret.

<span id="an_14:35">14:35</span> Imezdaɣ n lǧiha nni ɛeqlen Sidna Ɛisa,
dɣa ceggɛen ɣer yal lǧiha n tmurt, wwin-as-d imuḍan nsen meṛṛa.

<span id="an_14:36">14:36</span> Ḥellelen-t iwakken a ten-yeǧǧ ad nalen
ɣas ula ț-țacḍaṭ uqenduṛ-is. Wid akk i t-innulen, ḥlan.

<span id="an_15:2">15:2</span> Acuɣeṛ inelmaden-ik țṛuẓun lɛadda i
d-ǧǧan lejdud-nneɣ ? M'ara qeṛṛben ɣer lqut, ur ssiriden ara
ifassen-nsen.

<span id="an_15:3">15:3</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : I kunwi, acimi
tețṛuẓum lumuṛat n Ṛebbi iwakken aț-țxedmem ṛṛay nwen ?

<span id="an_15:4">15:4</span> Yak d ṣṣeḥ, Ṛebbi yenna-d : Qadeṛ baba-k
d yemma-k, yyenna daɣen : Kra win ara ineɛlen baba-s d yemma-s, ad
yețwaḥkem fell-as s lmut.

<span id="an_15:5">15:5</span> Meɛna kunwi teqqaṛem : win yefkan d
lweɛda i Ṛebbi ayen s wacu i glaq ad iɛiwen imawlan-is,

<span id="an_15:6">15:6</span> am akken d imawlan-is i gɛawen. SS wakka,
tbeddlem awal n Ṛebbi, iwakken aț-țesɛeddim lɛaddat-nwen.

<span id="an_15:7">15:7</span> Ay at sin wudmawen ! Ț-țideț i d-yenna
nnbi Iceɛya mi d-icar fell awen :

<span id="an_15:8">15:8</span> Y enna-d Ṛebbi : agdud-agi, ițɛuzzu-yi s
wawal kan, ma d ul-is yebɛed fell-i.

<span id="an_15:9">15:9</span> L eɛbada-nsen ur tesɛi ara azal axaṭer
sselmaden ayen i d-yekkan seg imdanen.

<span id="an_15:10">15:10</span> Dɣa Sidna Ɛisa yessawel i lɣaci
yenna-yasen : Semḥesset-d tfehmem ayagi :

<span id="an_15:11">15:11</span> mačči d ayen i gkeččmen seg imi n
wemdan i t-yessamasen, meɛna d ayen i d-ițeffɣen seg-s.

<span id="an_15:12">15:12</span> Inelmaden qeṛṛben-d ɣer Sidna Ɛisa
nnan-as : Ifariziyen iɣaḍ-iten lḥal ɣef yimeslayen-nni i d-tenniḍ !

<span id="an_15:13">15:13</span> Yerra-yasen : Yal imɣi ur yeẓẓi ara
Baba yellan deg igenwan, ad yețwaqleɛ.

<span id="an_15:14">15:14</span> Anfet-asen, d iderɣalen iteṭṭfen afus i
iderɣalen nniḍen ; ma yella aderɣal yeṭṭef afus i wayeḍ, ad ɣlin i sin
ɣer tesraft.

<span id="an_15:15">15:15</span> Buṭrus yenṭeq-ed yenna-yas :
Ssefhem-aɣ-d lemtel-agi.

<span id="an_15:16">15:16</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna i inelmaden-is : Eɛni
ula d kunwi txuṣṣ-ikkun lefhama ?

<span id="an_15:17">15:17</span> Ur tefhimem ara belli ayen ikeččmen seg
imi n wemdan yețțara ɣer uɛebbuḍ-is, mbeɛd ad ițwadeggeṛ ɣer beṛṛa.

<span id="an_15:18">15:18</span> Lameɛna ayen i d-iteffɣen seg imi
itekk-ed seg wul, d annect-agi i gessenǧasen amdan.

<span id="an_15:19">15:19</span> Axaṭer seg wul i d-tekken : yir
ixemmimen, timegṛaḍ, zzna ( lɛaṛ ), yir tikli, tukerḍa, cchada n ẓẓuṛ
akk-d rregmat.

<span id="an_15:20">15:20</span> Atan wayen yessenǧasen amdan, mačči d
učči mbla tarda n ifassen i t-yessenǧasen.

<span id="an_15:21">15:21</span> Sidna Ɛisa iṛuḥ syenna, iteddu ɣer
tmura n Sur akk-d Sidun.

<span id="an_15:22">15:22</span> Yiwet n tmeṭṭut n at Kenɛan i gzedɣen
dinna tusa-d ɣuṛ-es tețɛeggiḍ : A Sidi, a mmi-s n Sidna Dawed, ḥunn
fell-i ! Ațan yelli izdeɣ-iț uṛuḥani, iɛețțeb-iț aṭas.

<span id="an_15:23">15:23</span> Sidna Ɛisa ur as-d-yerri ula d yiwen
wawal. Inelmaden-is qeṛṛben ɣuṛ-es nnan-as : Err-as awal, axaṭer tugi
aț-țeḥbes leɛyaḍ deffir-nneɣ.

<span id="an_15:24">15:24</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Țțuceggɛeɣ-ed
anagar ɣer wulli iḍaɛen n wat Isṛail !

<span id="an_15:25">15:25</span> Lameɛna tameṭṭut-nni teɣli ɣer iḍaṛṛen
n Sidna Ɛisa tenna-yas : A Sidi ɛiwen-iyi di leɛnaya-k !

<span id="an_15:26">15:26</span> Yenna-yas : Ur ilaq ara ad ițwakkes
weɣṛum i warrac, ad ițwadeggeṛ i yeqjan.

<span id="an_15:27">15:27</span> Tenna-yas : Ț-țideț a Sidi, lameɛna ula
d iqjan tețțen tifețțitin i d-iɣellin si ṭṭabla n imawlan-nsen.

<span id="an_15:28">15:28</span> Imiren Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas :
Liman-inem d ameqqran a tameṭṭut ! A m-yețwaxdem wayen tebɣiḍ ! IImiren
kan yelli-s teḥla.

<span id="an_15:29">15:29</span> Sidna Ɛisa iṛuḥ syenna, yerra ɣer
leǧwahi n lebḥeṛ n Jlili, yuli ɣer wedrar yeqqim.

<span id="an_15:30">15:30</span> Usan-d ɣuṛ-es lɣaci d izumal, wwin-as-d
iquḍaren, iderɣalen, ineɛyuba, igugamen d waṭas imuḍan nniḍen.
Ssersen-ten ɣer zdat iḍaṛṛen-is dɣa isseḥla-ten.

<span id="an_15:31">15:31</span> Imdanen meṛṛa tɛeǧben mi walan igugamen
heddṛen, ineɛyuba ḥlan, iquḍaren leḥḥun, iderɣalen țwalin, dɣa bdan
țḥemmiden Sidi Ṛebbi Illu n wat Isṛail.

<span id="an_15:32">15:32</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessawel-asen i inelmaden-is
yenna-yasen : Ɣaḍen-iyi lɣaci-agi axaṭer tlata wussan aya segmi llan
yid-i, yerna ur sɛin d acu ara ččen. Ur bɣiɣ ara a ten-rreɣ akka lluẓen
neɣ m'ulac ad feclen deg webrid.

<span id="an_15:33">15:33</span> Inelmaden nnan-as : Ansi ara ɣ-d-yekk
deg umkan-agi yexlan, weɣṛum ara isseṛwun annect agi n lɣaci ?

<span id="an_15:34">15:34</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Acḥal n
teḥbulin n weɣṛum i tesɛam ɣuṛ-wen ? RRran-as : Sebɛa n teḥbulin akk-d
kra n iselman ( iḥutiwen ).

<span id="an_15:35">15:35</span> Imiren yenna i lɣaci ad qqimen ɣer
lqaɛa.

<span id="an_15:36">15:36</span> Yeddem-ed tiḥbulin-nni n weɣṛum d
iselman-nni, iḥmed Ṛebbi, yebḍa-ten, yefka-ten i inelmaden-is iwakken a
ten-feṛqen i lɣaci.

<span id="an_15:37">15:37</span> Sčan akk armi ṛwan, yerna ččuṛen sebɛa
n tqecwalin n wayen i d-yegran.

<span id="an_15:38">15:38</span> Ger wid yeččan, llan azal n ṛebɛa alaf
n yergazen mbla tilawin d warrac.

<span id="an_15:39">15:39</span> Mi gerra lɣaci, Sidna Ɛisa yerkeb di
teflukt, iṛuḥ ɣer tmurt n Magadan.

<span id="an_16:1">16:1</span> Ifariziyen d isaduqiyen qeṛṛben ɣer Sidna
Ɛisa, ssutren-as lbeṛhan iwakken a t-jeṛben.

<span id="an_16:2">16:2</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : M'ara yeɣli
yiṭij, twalam igenni d azeggaɣ, teqqaṛem ad yelhu lḥal.

<span id="an_16:3">16:3</span> Akken daɣen taṣebḥit, teqqaṛem a d-iwwet
ugeffur ( lehwa ) axaṭer yella usigna. AAmek ! Tesnem aț-țfehmem lḥala n
igenni, ur tezmirem ara aț-țfehmem licaṛat yeɛnan lweqt-agi !

<span id="an_16:4">16:4</span> Lǧil am agi ijehlen ixedɛen Ṛebbi,
yessutur lbeṛhan ! Meɛna ur as-d-ițțunefkay ara lbeṛhan nniḍen anagar
win n nnbi Yunes ! DDɣa iṛuḥ, yeǧǧa-ten.

<span id="an_16:5">16:5</span> Mi zegren agummaḍ i lebḥeṛ, inelmaden-is
țțun ur wwin ara yid-sen aɣṛum.

<span id="an_16:6">16:6</span> Dɣa Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Ḥadret
iman-nwen seg iɣes n temtunt n ifariziyen d isaduqiyen !

<span id="an_16:7">16:7</span> Inelmaden xemmemen deg yiman-nsen, nnan :
Ahat imi ur d-newwi ara yid-nneɣ aɣṛum i ɣ-d-yenna akka !

<span id="an_16:8">16:8</span> Sidna Ɛisa iẓra ɣef wacu i țxemmimen
yenna-yasen : A wid i gxuṣṣen di liman ! Tɣilem imi ur d-tewwim ara
aɣṛum i wen-d-nniɣ akka ?

<span id="an_16:9">16:9</span> Mazal ur tefhimem ara ? Eɛni tețțum yakan
xemsa teḥbulin-nni n weɣṛum i bḍiɣ i xemsa alaf n yergazen ? D wacḥal n
tqecwalin i d-yegran ?

<span id="an_16:10">16:10</span> Ur tecfim ara daɣen ɣef sebɛa
teḥbulin-nni n weɣṛum i bḍiɣ i ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen, d wacḥal n
tqecwalin i d-yegran ?

<span id="an_16:11">16:11</span> Amek akka ur tefhimem ara belli mačči
ɣef weɣṛum i wen-d-țmeslayeɣ ? ḤḤadret iman-nwen seg iɣes n temtunt n
ifariziyen d isaduqiyen !

<span id="an_16:12">16:12</span> Imiren inelmaden-is fehmen belli mačči
ɣef yiɣes n temtunt i sen-d-immeslay, lameɛna ad ḥadren iman-nsen ɣef
wuselmed n ifariziyen d isaduqiyen.

<span id="an_16:13">16:13</span> Mi gewweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer tmurt n
Qiṣarya n Filibus, isteqsa inelmaden is, yenna-yasen : D acu i-d-qqaṛen
medden ɣef Mmi-s n bunadem ?

<span id="an_16:14">16:14</span> Rran-as : Kra qqaṛen d Yeḥya aɣeṭṭas,
wiyaḍ qqaṛen d nnbi Ilyas, wiyaḍ daɣen d nnbi Irmiya neɣ d yiwen ger
lenbiya.

<span id="an_16:15">16:15</span> I kunwi, d acu-yi ɣuṛ-wen ?

<span id="an_16:16">16:16</span> Buṭrus yerra-yas : Kečč d Lmasiḥ, Mmi-s
n Sidi Ṛebbi yeddren !

<span id="an_16:17">16:17</span> Yenṭeq ɣuṛ-es yenna-yas : Amarezg-ik, a
Buṭrus a mmi-s n Yunes, axaṭer mačči s tmusni-inek i tfehmeḍ ayagi,
meɛna d Baba Ṛebbi yellan deg igenwan i k-t-id-isbegnen.

<span id="an_16:18">16:18</span> Ihi nekk a k-iniɣ : kečč a Buṭrus d
azṛu, yerna ɣef wezṛu-agi ara bnuɣ tajmaɛt-iw, ula ț-ținezmarin n lmut
ur țțaṭṭafent ara zdat-es !

<span id="an_16:19">16:19</span> Ad a k-fkeɣ tisura n tgelda n igenwan,
ayen ara teqneḍ neɣ ayen iwumi ara tserrḥeḍ di ddunit, ad yețwaqbel deg
igenwan.

<span id="an_16:20">16:20</span> Imiren yumeṛ i yinelmaden-is ur qqaṛen
ula i yiwen belli d nețța i d Lmasiḥ.

<span id="an_16:21">16:21</span> Seg imiren, Sidna Ɛisa yebda issefham i
inelmaden-is belli ilaq ad yali ɣer temdint n Lquds, anda ara yenneɛtab
aṭas ger ifassen n lmuqedmin akk-d lɛulama n ccariɛa ad ḥekmen fell-as s
lmut, ass wis tlata a d-iḥyu si ger lmegtin.

<span id="an_16:22">16:22</span> Buṭrus ijbed-it weḥd-es, yenna yas : A
k-imneɛ Ṛebbi a Sidi, a wer d-yedṛu wayagi yid-ek !

<span id="an_16:23">16:23</span> Sidna Ɛisa idewweṛ ɣuṛ-es, yenna-yas :
Beɛɛed akkin fell-i a Cciṭan ! Tebɣiḍ aț-țiliḍ d ugur deg webrid-iw !
Ixemmimen-ik ur d-kkan ara s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, lameɛna d ixemmimen n yemdanen.

<span id="an_16:24">16:24</span> Imiren Sidna Ɛisa yenna i inelmaden-is
: Kra win yebɣan ad iddu yid-i, ilaq-as ur yețḥebbiṛ ara ɣef yiman-is,
ad iqbel ad inɛețțab ɣef ddemma n yisem-iw, a yi-d-itbeɛ.

<span id="an_16:25">16:25</span> Kra win yebɣan ad isellek taṛwiḥt-is, a
s-tṛuḥ ; ma d win iseblen taṛwiḥt-is ɣef ddemma-w ad yuɣal a ț-yaf.

<span id="an_16:26">16:26</span> D acu n lfayda ara yesɛu wemdan di
rrbeḥ n ddunit meṛṛa, ma yella yesṛuḥ taṛwiḥt-is ? Neɣ d acu i gezmer a
t-yefk wemdan iwakken a d-ifdu taṛwiḥt-is ?

<span id="an_16:27">16:27</span> Axaṭer Mmi-s n bunadem a d-yas nețța d
lmalayekkat-is di lɛaḍima n Baba-s, ad yefk i yal yiwen ayen yuklal, yal
yiwen ɣef leḥsab n lefɛayel-is.

<span id="an_16:28">16:28</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : llan kra seg wid
yellan dagi, ur țmețțaten ara alamma ẓran Mmi-s n bunadem yusa-d am
ugellid.

<span id="an_17:1">17:1</span> Mi ɛeddan sețța wussan, Sidna Ɛisa yewwi
yid-es Buṭrus, Yeɛqub akk-d gma-s Yuḥenna, ulin ɣer wedrar eɛlayen, anda
qqimen ḍeṛfen iman-nsen.

<span id="an_17:2">17:2</span> Taswiɛt kan ibeddel ṣṣifa zdat sen, walan
udem-is yețfeǧǧiǧ am yiṭij, llebsa-s tuɣal ț-țamellalt, tecceɛceɛ am
tafat.

<span id="an_17:3">17:3</span> A ten-aya dehṛen-asen-d Sidna Musa akk-d
Sidna Ilyas țmeslayen d Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_17:4">17:4</span> Buṭrus inṭeq yenna i Sidna Ɛisa : A Sidi,
yelha ma neqqim dagi, ma tebɣiḍ ad sbeddeɣ tlata iqiḍunen : yiwen i
kečč, yiwen i Sidna Musa, wayeḍ i Sidna Ilyas.

<span id="an_17:5">17:5</span> Mazal-it ițmeslay mi d-ters yiwet n tagut
ițfeǧǧiǧen tɣumm-iten. Si tagut-nni tenṭeq-ed yiwet n taɣect, tenna-d :
Wagi d Mmi eɛzizen deg-s i gella lfeṛḥ-iw, smeḥsiset-as !

<span id="an_17:6">17:6</span> Mi slan i taɣect-nni, inelmaden
ikcem-iten lxuf, ɣlin ɣef wudem.

<span id="an_17:7">17:7</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessers afus-is fell-asen,
yenna-yasen : Ur țțaggadet ara, kkret !

<span id="an_17:8">17:8</span> Mi refden allen-nsen, ur walan ula d
yiwen nniḍen anagar Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_17:9">17:9</span> Akken i d-țadren seg wedrar, Sidna Ɛisa
yumeṛ-iten yenna-yasen : Ur qqaṛet i yiwen wayen akka twalam alamma
yeḥya-d Mmi-s n bunadem si ger lmegtin.

<span id="an_17:10">17:10</span> Inelmaden steqsan Sidna Ɛisa nnan-as :
Iwacu imusnawen n ccariɛa qqaṛen-d : « Ilaq a d-yas nnbi Ilyas d
amezwaru ? »

<span id="an_17:11">17:11</span> Yerra-yasen : Ț-țideț ilaq a d-yas nnbi
Ilyas d amezwaru, iwakken ad iseggem kullec.

<span id="an_17:12">17:12</span> Ma d nekk aql-i nniɣ awen-d : nnbi
Ilyas yusa-d yakan, lameɛna imdanen ur t-ɛqilen ara yerna xedmen deg-s
akken i sen ihwa. Akka daɣen ara inɛețțab Mmi-s n bunadem ger
ifassen-nsen !

<span id="an_17:13">17:13</span> Inelmaden fehmen imiren belli
ițmeslay-asen-d ɣef Yeḥya aɣeṭṭas.

<span id="an_17:14">17:14</span> Mi wwḍen ɣer wanda llan lɣaci, yiwen
wergaz iqeṛṛeb-ed ɣer Sidna Ɛisa, yeɣli ɣef tgecrar zdat-es yenna yas :

<span id="an_17:15">17:15</span> A Sidi, ḥunn ɣef mmi ! Atan kkaten-t
imsigman, yenneɛtab aṭas ! Acḥal d abrid i geɣli ɣer tmes neɣ ɣer waman,

<span id="an_17:16">17:16</span> wwiɣ-t-id i inelmaden-ik, meɛna ur
zmiren ara a t-sseḥlun.

<span id="an_17:17">17:17</span> Inṭeq Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : A lǧil
ijehlen, iɛewjen ! Ar melmi ara yiliɣ yid-wen ? Ar melmi ara wen-sebṛeɣ
? Awit-iyi-d aqcic-agi ɣer dagi !

<span id="an_17:18">17:18</span> Sidna Ɛisa iɛeggeḍ ɣef lǧen-nni,
yumeṛ-as ad iffeɣ seg weqcic-nni. Imiren kan, aqcic-nni yeḥla.

<span id="an_17:19">17:19</span> Mi llan inelmaden iman-nsen, qeṛṛben
ɣer Sidna Ɛisa nnan-as : Acuɣeṛ nukkni ur nezmir ara a t-nessufeɣ ?

<span id="an_17:20">17:20</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Axaṭer txuṣṣem
di liman ! Aql-i nniɣ-awen, lemmer tesɛim liman annect n uɛeqqa n
uxerḍel, tili a s tinim i wedrar-agi, qleɛ iman-ik sya ɣer dihin ad
iqleɛ. Ulac wayen iwumi ur tețțizmirem ara.

<span id="an_17:21">17:21</span> Sṣenf-agi n leǧnun țeffɣen anagar s
tẓallit d uẓummu.

<span id="an_17:22">17:22</span> Mi llan di tmurt n Jlili, Sidna Ɛisa
yenna-yasen : Mmi-s n bunadem ad ițțusellem ger ifassen n yemdanen ;

<span id="an_17:23">17:23</span> a t-nɣen, meɛna ass wis tlata a d-iḥyu
si ger lmegtin. DDɣa inelmaden ikcem-iten leḥzen d ameqqran.

<span id="an_17:24">17:24</span> Mi gewweḍ Sidna Ɛisa akk-d inelmaden-is
ɣer Kafernaḥum, imekkasen n lǧameɛ qeṛṛben-d ɣer Buṭrus nnan-as : Eɛni
Ssid-nwen ur ițxelliṣ ara tabzert n lǧameɛ ?

<span id="an_17:25">17:25</span> Yerra-yasen Buṭrus : Ih, ad ixelleṣ !
Imiren kan mi gekcem Buṭrus ɣer wexxam, Sidna Ɛisa iluɛa-t, yenna-yas :
D acu twalaḍ a Buṭrus ? Anwa i glaqen ad ixelleṣ tabzert i igelliden n
ddunit-a , d arraw-nsen neɣ d ibeṛṛaniyen ?

<span id="an_17:26">17:26</span> Buṭrus yerra-yas : D ibeṛṛaniyen ! DDɣa
Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas-d : Ihi arraw n tmurt ur țxelliṣen ara !

<span id="an_17:27">17:27</span> Lameɛna iwakken ur ten-yețɣaḍ ara lḥal,
ṛuḥ, ḍeggeṛ tasennaṛt ɣer lebḥeṛ, aslem ( aḥewtiw ) amezwaru ara
d-teṭṭfeḍ, ldi-yas imi, aț-țafeḍ deg-s aṣurdi n lfeṭṭa, efk-asen-t d
lexlaṣ n tebzert-nneɣ nekk yid-ek.

<span id="an_18:1">18:1</span> Di lweqt-nni, inelmaden n Sidna Ɛisa
qeṛṛben ɣuṛ-es nnan-as : -- Anwa i d ameqqran di tgelda n igenwan ?

<span id="an_18:2">18:2</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessawel i yiwen weqcic
isbedd-it di tlemmast-nsen, yenna :

<span id="an_18:3">18:3</span> A wen-d-iniɣ tideț ; ma yella ur
d-tuɣalem ara ɣer webrid, m'ur teqbilem ara aț-țilim .am arrac
imecṭuḥen, ur tkeččmem ara ɣer tgelda n igenwan !

<span id="an_18:4">18:4</span> Daymi, win ara yeṣṣemẓin iman-is am
weqcic-agi amecṭuḥ, d nețța ara yilin d ameqqran di tgelda n igenwan.

<span id="an_18:5">18:5</span> Kra win ara yestṛeḥben s weqcic am-agi
ɣef ddemma n yisem-iw, yis-i i gesṭerḥeb.

<span id="an_18:6">18:6</span> Win ara yesseɣlin di ddnub ula d yiwen
seg imecṭuḥen-agi yumnen yis-i, axiṛ-as a s-cudden aɣaṛef n tsirt ɣer
temgeṛṭ-is, a t-ḍeggṛen ɣer lebḥeṛ ad iɣṛeq.

<span id="an_18:7">18:7</span> A tawaɣit n ddunit-a, imi qwant tsebbiwin
n tuccḍa ! Axaṭer tisebbiwin n tuccḍa ulamek ur d-țilint ara. Meɛna a
nnger n win ara yilin d sebba-nsent.

<span id="an_18:8">18:8</span> Ma yella d afus-ik neɣ d aḍaṛ-ik ara
k-yesseɣlin di ddnub, gzem-iten, ḍeggeṛ-iten akkin fell-ak, axiṛ-ak
aț-țiliḍ di ddunit d aɛiban wala aț-țesɛuḍ sin iḍaṛṛen neɣ sin ifassen,
aț-țwaḍeggṛeḍ ɣer tmes ur nxețți.

<span id="an_18:9">18:9</span> Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer
ddnub, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit s
yiwet n tiṭ wala aț-țesɛuḍ snat wallen, aț- țwaḍeggṛeḍ ɣer tmes n
ǧahennama.

<span id="an_18:10">18:10</span> Ɣuṛ-wat aț-țḥeqṛem yiwen seg
imecṭuḥen-agi axaṭer aql-i nniɣ awen-t : lmalayekkat-nsen deg igenwan,
zgant daymen zdat Baba Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_18:11">18:11</span> \[ Axaṭer Mmi-s n bunadem yusa-d ad
isellek wid i gḍaɛen ! \]

<span id="an_18:12">18:12</span> D acu twalam ? Ma yella win yesɛan
meyya wulli dɣa teɛṛeq-as yiwet deg-sent, ur ițțaǧa ara țesɛa
uțesɛin-nni nniḍen di lexla iwakken a d-inadi ɣef tin i s-iɛeṛqen ?

<span id="an_18:13">18:13</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : ma yufa-ț, ad ifṛeḥ
yis akteṛ n țesɛa uțesɛin-nni nniḍen ur neɛṛiq ara.

<span id="an_18:14">18:14</span> Akken daɣen Baba-twen Ṛebbi yellan deg
igenwan, ur yebɣi ara a s-iṛuḥ ula d yiwen seg imecṭuḥen-agi.

<span id="an_18:15">18:15</span> Ma yella twalaḍ gma-k idneb, ṛuḥ
ṭṭef-it weḥd-es, nhu-t. Ma yuɣ-ak awal, atan trebḥeḍ-ed gma-k !

<span id="an_18:16">18:16</span> Meɛna ma igumma a k-d-isel, awi yiwen
neɣ sin yemdanen yid-ek, iwakken ad ilin d inigan m'ara tefru temsalt ,
akken i d-tenna ccariɛa.

<span id="an_18:17">18:17</span> Ma yugi a sen-isel, ssiweḍ tamsalt ɣer
tejmaɛt n watmaten, m'ur iḥess ara ula i tejmaɛt-nni, ḥseb-it am akken d
akafriw neɣ d amekkas axabit !

<span id="an_18:18">18:18</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : ayen akk ara teqnem
neɣ iwumi ara tserrḥem di ddunit, ad yețwaqbel deg igenwan.

<span id="an_18:19">18:19</span> A wen-iniɣ daɣen s tideț : ma yella sin
seg-wen ddukklen iwakken ad ssutren kra di tẓallit, Baba Ṛebbi yellan
deg igenwan, a sen-t-id-yefk.

<span id="an_18:20">18:20</span> Axaṭer anda ara dduklen sin neɣ tlata s
yisem-iw, ad ḥedṛeɣ gar-asen !

<span id="an_18:21">18:21</span> Imiren Buṭrus iqeṛṛeb ɣuṛ-es yenna-yas
: A Sidi, acḥal n tikkal ilaq ad semḥeɣ i gma ma yeḍlem-iyi, armi d
sebɛa n tikkal ? SSidna Ɛisa yerra yas :

<span id="an_18:22">18:22</span> Xaṭi ! Ur k-d-nniɣ ara alamma d sebɛa
tikkal, meɛna alamma d sebɛin iberdan sebɛa tikkal !

<span id="an_18:23">18:23</span> Daymi, tagelda n igenwan tețțemcabi ɣer
yiwen ugellid yebɣan ad imḥasab nețța d iqeddacen-is.

<span id="an_18:24">18:24</span> Akken yebda leḥsab, wwin-as-d yiwen
uqeddac iwumi yețțalas imelyunen.

<span id="an_18:25">18:25</span> Imi ur yesɛi ara s wacu ara ixelleṣ,
agellid-nni ifka lameṛ a ten-zzenzen d aklan, s nețța s tmeṭṭut-is, s
warraw-is d wayen akk yesɛa, iwakken ad ixelleṣ ṭṭlaba-ines.

<span id="an_18:26">18:26</span> Aqeddac-nni yeɣli ɣer iḍaṛṛen n
ugellid, iḥellel-it yenna-yas : «\` A Sidi, ṣṣbeṛ kra wussan, ad uɣaleɣ
a k-xellṣeɣ ayen akk i yi tețțalaseḍ. »

<span id="an_18:27">18:27</span> Imi i t-iɣaḍ aṭas, agellid-nni
isumeḥ-as ṭṭlaba-ines iserreḥ-as ad iṛuḥ.

<span id="an_18:28">18:28</span> Akken kan i d-iffeɣ uqeddac-nni
immuger-ed yiwen seg imdukkal-is ixeddmen yid-es, iwumi yețțalas kra n
iṣurdiyen. IIkker ɣuṛ-es yeṭṭef-it si temgeṛṭ yeqqaṛ-as : « Err-iyi-d
ayen i k țțalaseɣ ! »

<span id="an_18:29">18:29</span> Amdakkel-is yeɣli ɣer iḍaṛṛen-is
iḥellel-it, yenna-yas : « Sṣbeṛ kra n wussan, ad uɣaleɣ a k-xellṣeɣ ! »

<span id="an_18:30">18:30</span> Lameɛna ur yeqbil ara ad isbeṛ, yerra-t
ɣer lḥebs, alamma tețwaxelleṣ ṭṭlaba-ines.

<span id="an_18:31">18:31</span> Iqeddacen nniḍen mi walan ayen yedṛan,
iɣaḍ-iten lḥal, dɣa ṛuḥen ṣṣawḍen lexbaṛ i ugellid.

<span id="an_18:32">18:32</span> Agellid iceggeɛ ɣer uqeddac-nni akken a
d-yas, dɣa yenna-yas : « A yir amdan ! Mi tețḥellileḍ deg-i, eɛni ur
k-sumḥeɣ ara akk ṭṭlaba-inek ?

<span id="an_18:33">18:33</span> Acuɣeṛ ihi ur as-tsumḥeḍ ara i
wemdakkel-ik akken i k-sumḥeɣ nekkini ? »

<span id="an_18:34">18:34</span> Agellid-nni yezɛef aṭas, yerra
aqeddac-nni ɣer lḥebs, iwakken ad inɛețțab alamma tețwaxelleṣ ṭṭlaba
ines.

<span id="an_18:35">18:35</span> Akken daɣen ara wen-yexdem Baba Ṛebbi
yellan deg igenwan ma ur tețsamaḥem ara i watmaten-nwen seg ul.

<span id="an_19:1">19:1</span> Mi gekfa lewṣayat-agi, Sidna Ɛisa iṛuḥ si
tmurt n Jlili ɣer tmurt n Yahuda ɣer leǧwahi n wasif n Urdun.

<span id="an_19:2">19:2</span> Aṭas n lɣaci i t-iḍefṛen ɣer dinna, dɣa
yesseḥla wid akk ihelken.

<span id="an_19:3">19:3</span> Kra ifariziyen qeṛṛben-d ɣuṛ-es iwakken a
t-jeṛben, nnan-as : Eɛni ccariɛa-nneɣ tsumeḥ-as i wergaz ad yebru i
tmeṭṭut-is ɣef yal sebba yellan ?

<span id="an_19:4">19:4</span> Yerra-yasen : Ur teɣṛim ara ayen i
d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa : di tazwara Sidi Ṛebbi ixleq-ed argaz ț-țmeṭṭut,

<span id="an_19:5">19:5</span> yenna-d : AArgaz ad yeǧǧ baba-s d
yemma-s, iiwakken ad iɛic nețța ț-țmeṭṭut-is, ddɣa di sin yid-sen, ad
uɣalen d yiwen.

<span id="an_19:6">19:6</span> S wakka ur llin ara d sin, meɛna uɣalen d
yiwen. Ur as-ilaq ara ihi i wemdan ad ifṛeq ayen yesdukkel Sidi Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_19:7">19:7</span> Nnan-as : Acuɣeṛ ihi Sidna Musa yeǧǧa
yaɣ-d lqanun belli m'ara yebru wergaz i tmeṭṭut-is, a s-yefk lkaɣeḍ n
berru ?

<span id="an_19:8">19:8</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Ɣef ddemma n
wulawen-nwen yeqquṛen i wen-iserreḥ nnbi Musa aț-țebrum i tilawin-nwen.
Meɛna di tazwara mačči akka i gella lḥal.

<span id="an_19:9">19:9</span> Ma d nekk a wen-d-iniɣ : kra n win ara
yebrun i tmeṭṭut-is yili ur tezni ara, iwakken ad yaɣ tayeḍ, d nețța i
geznan !

<span id="an_19:10">19:10</span> Inelmaden nnan-as : Ma yella akka i d
lḥala n wergaz ɣer tmeṭṭut, ulac lfayda di zzwaǧ !

<span id="an_19:11">19:11</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Mačči d
imdanen meṛṛa i gzemren ad qeblen aselmed agi lameɛna anagar wid iwumi i
d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi lefhama i gzemren ad qeblen annect-agi.

<span id="an_19:12">19:12</span> Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan.
Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d
imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen. LLlan daɣen wid iḥeṛmen iman-nsen ɣef zwaǧ, ɣef
ddemma n tgelda n igenwan. Win i gzemren ad ifhem aselmed agi a t-yefhem
!

<span id="an_19:13">19:13</span> Kra yemdanen țawin-d i Sidna Ɛisa arrac
imecṭuḥen iwakken ad issers afus-is fell-asen a ten-ibarek, meɛna
inelmaden-is țțaran-ten.

<span id="an_19:14">19:14</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Anfet-asen i
warrac a d-asen ɣuṛ-i, ur sen-qeṭṭɛet ara abrid, axaṭer tagelda n
igenwan thegga i nutni akk-d wid yellan am nutni !

<span id="an_19:15">19:15</span> Yessers afus-is fell-asen, iburek iten,
dɣa iṛuḥ syenna.

<span id="an_19:16">19:16</span> Imiren yiwen wergaz iqeṛṛeb-ed ɣer
Sidna Ɛisa, yenna-yas : A Sidi, d acu i yi-ilaqen a t xedmeɣ n wayen
yelhan iwakken ad sɛuɣ tudert n dayem ?

<span id="an_19:17">19:17</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Acuɣeṛ i
yi-testeqsayeḍ ɣef wayen yelhan ? AAnagar yiwen i gelhan ! Ma tebɣiḍ
aț-țesɛuḍ tudert-agi, xdem lumuṛat yellan di ccariɛa. YYerra-yas-ed
weqcic-nni : Anwi i d lumuṛat ara tebɛeɣ ?

<span id="an_19:18">19:18</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Ur tneqqeḍ ara
tamgeṛṭ, ur tzennuḍ ara, ur tețțcehhideḍ ara s ẓẓur, ur tețțakkṛreḍ ara,

<span id="an_19:19">19:19</span> qadeṛ baba-k d yemma-k, tḥemmleḍ
lɣiṛ-ik am yiman-ik !

<span id="an_19:20">19:20</span> Aqcic-nni yerra-yas-ed : Ayagi akk
xedmeɣ-t, d acu i yi-ixuṣṣen ?

<span id="an_19:21">19:21</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Ma tebɣiḍ ihi
aț-țkemleḍ deg webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi , ṛuḥ, zzenz akk ayen i tesɛiḍ,
tefkeḍ idrimen-nni i yimeɣban, s wakka aț-țesɛuḍ agerruj deg igenwan !
Imiren as-ed, aț-țedduḍ yid-i.

<span id="an_19:22">19:22</span> Mi gesla i yimeslayen-agi, ilemẓi-nni
yeḥzen aṭas dɣa iṛuḥ, axaṭer d ameṛkanti ameqqran i gella.

<span id="an_19:23">19:23</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna i inelmaden-is : A
wen-iniɣ s tideț : iwɛeṛ aṭas i umeṛkanti ad ikcem ɣer tgelda n igenwan
!

<span id="an_19:24">19:24</span> A wen-iniɣ daɣen : ma yella iwɛeṛ i
welɣem ad iɛeddi di tiṭ n tissegnit, iwɛeṛ akteṛ i umeṛkanti ad ikcem
ɣer tgelda n igenwan !

<span id="an_19:25">19:25</span> Mi slan i imeslayen-agi, inelmaden-is
dehcen aṭas, nnan-as : Anwa i gzemren ad ițțusellek ihi ?

<span id="an_19:26">19:26</span> Dɣa Sidna Ɛisa imuqel-iten, yenna :
Imdanen s yiman-nsen ur zmiren ara, meɛna Sidi Ṛebbi yezmer i kullec.

<span id="an_19:27">19:27</span> Buṭrus inṭeq, yenna-yas : Aql-aɣ nukkni
neǧǧa kullec iwakken a k-netbeɛ, d acu ara yedṛun yid-nneɣ ?

<span id="an_19:28">19:28</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : A wen-iniɣ s
tideț, asm'ara d-ḥyun lmegtin ɣer ddunit tajḍiṭ, asm'ara yeqqim Mmi-s n
bunadem ɣef wukersi n lḥekma di lɛaḍima-s, ula d kunwi yeddan yid-i,
aț-țeqqimem di tnac yid-wen ɣef yikersiyen n lḥekma iwakken aț-țḥasbem
tnac n leɛṛac n wat Isṛail.

<span id="an_19:29">19:29</span> Yerna, kra win ara yeǧǧen ɣef ddemma n
yisem-iw axxam-is neɣ atmaten-is, yessetma-s neɣ baba-s, yemma-s,
arraw-is neɣ tiferkiwin-is, ad as-d-yețțunefk akteṛ n wayen yeǧǧa, yerna
a t-id-tṣaḥ tudert n dayem.

<span id="an_19:30">19:30</span> Aṭas seg wid yellan d imezwura ad
uɣalen d ineggura, aṭas daɣen seg wid yellan d ineggura ad uɣalen d
imezwura.

<span id="an_20:2">20:2</span> Imsefham yid-sen a ten-ixelleṣ s twizeț n
lfeṭṭa i wass, dɣa iceggeɛ-iten ɣer tfeṛṛant-is.

<span id="an_20:3">20:3</span> Iffeɣ daɣen ɣef țesɛa n ṣṣbeḥ, iwala
wiyaḍ qqimen di beṛṛa mbla lxedma.

<span id="an_20:4">20:4</span> yenna-yasen : Ṛuḥet ula d kunwi
aț-țxedmem di tfeṛṛant-iw, a wen-fkeɣ ayen tuklalem.

<span id="an_20:5">20:5</span> Dɣa ṛuḥen. Bab n tfeṛṛant-nni yexdem
akken daɣen ɣef tnac n wass akk-d ț-țlata n tmeddit.

<span id="an_20:6">20:6</span> Iffeɣ daɣen ɣef lxemsa n tmeddit, yufa
wiyaḍ qqimen di beṛṛa yenna-yasen : Acuɣeṛ i tețɣimim ass kamel mbla
lxedma ?

<span id="an_20:7">20:7</span> Nnan-as-ed : Ulac win i ɣ-d-ifkan lxedma
! YYenna-yasen : Ṛuḥet ula d kunwi aț-țxedmem di tfeṛṛant-iw !

<span id="an_20:8">20:8</span> Mi i d-tewweḍ tmeddit, bab n tfeṛṛant
yenna i lewkil-is : Ssiwel i ixeddamen txellseḍ-ten yiwen yiwen. Zwir
seg ineggura tessegriḍ imezwura.

<span id="an_20:9">20:9</span> Usan-d wid yebdan lxedma ɣef lxemsa n
tmeddit, ixelleṣ-iten s ssuma n yiwen wass,

<span id="an_20:10">20:10</span> mi i d-tewweḍ nnuba n wid ibdan lxedma
ɣef țesɛa n ṣṣbeḥ, ɣilen ad țwaxelṣen akteṛ n wiyaḍ, meɛna ula d nutni
țwaxellṣen s ssuma n yiwen wass.

<span id="an_20:11">20:11</span> Mi ṭṭfen lexlaṣ-nsen, iɣaḍ-iten lḥal,
nnan i bab n tfeṛṛant-nni :

<span id="an_20:12">20:12</span> Ixeddamen-agi ineggura xedmen yiwet n
ssaɛa kan, txellṣeḍ ten am nukkni yenɛețțaben ass kamel i wezɣal ?

<span id="an_20:13">20:13</span> Meɛna yerra-yas i yiwen seg sen : Ay
amdakkel, acuɣeṛ i k-iɣaḍ lḥal ? Eɛni ur nemsefham ara ɣef lexlaṣ-nwen
ad yili tawizeț n lfeṭṭa d ssuma n yiwen wass ?

<span id="an_20:14">20:14</span> Awi lḥeqq-ik tṛuḥeḍ. I ma yella bɣiɣ ad
fkeɣ i uneggaru annect i k-fkiɣ i kečč ?

<span id="an_20:15">20:15</span> Eɛni ur zmireɣ ara ad xedmeɣ akken bɣiɣ
s idrimen-iw ? Neɣ iɣaḍ-ik lḥal imi ur lliɣ ara d amecḥaḥ ?

<span id="an_20:16">20:16</span> S wakka aṭas ineggura ara yuɣalen d
imezwura, aṭas n imezwura ara yuɣalen d ineggura.

<span id="an_20:17">20:17</span> Mi țeddun ad alin ɣer temdint n Lquds,
Sidna Ɛisa iṭṭef tnac-nni inelmaden-is weḥḥed-sen, yenna yasen :

<span id="an_20:18">20:18</span> Ḥesset-ed : atan a nali ɣer temdint n
Lquds, anda ara ițțusellem Mmi-s n bunadem ger ifassen n lmuqedmin
imeqqranen akk-d lɛulama n ccariɛa. Ad ḥekmen fell-as s lmut,

<span id="an_20:19">20:19</span> yerna a t-sellmen ger ifassen nn
ikafriwen iwakken ad stehzin fell-as, a t-jelkḍen ( a t-cellṭen ), a
t-semmṛen ɣef wumidag, ass wis tlata a d-iḥyu si ger lmegtin.

<span id="an_20:20">20:20</span> Imiren yemma-s n Yeɛqub d Yuḥenna,
arraw n Zabadi, tqeṛṛeb-ed ɣer Sidna Ɛisa nețțat d warraw-is, tseǧǧed
ɣer iḍaṛṛen-is.

<span id="an_20:21">20:21</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : D acu i tebɣiḍ ?
Tenna-yas : Di leɛnaya-k a Sidi, efk-asen imukan i sin-agi n warraw-iw
di tgelda-inek, iwakken ad qqimen wa ɣer uyeffus-ik, wa ɣer uzelmaḍ-ik.

<span id="an_20:22">20:22</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Ur teẓrim ara
ayen akka i d tessutrem ! Eɛni tzemrem aț-țeswem si tbuqalt-agi n lemṛaṛ
ara sweɣ ? NNnan-as : Ih a Sidi, nezmer !

<span id="an_20:23">20:23</span> Yerra-yasen : Ț-țideț, aț-țeswem si
tbuqalt-agi, meɛna ɣef wayen yeɛnan imukan ɣer tama-w tayeffust neɣ
tazelmaṭ, mačči d nekk ara ten-ifken, ad țțunefken i wid iwumi i
ten-ihegga Baba Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_20:24">20:24</span> Ɛecṛa n inelmaden-nni mi slan ayagi,
ikcem-iten zzɛaf ɣef ddemma n sin-nni watmaten.

<span id="an_20:25">20:25</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessawel-asen, yenna-yasen :
Walit igelliden n yegduden nniḍen akk-d imeqqranen-nsen amek ḥeṛsen
yerna ḥeqṛen lɣaci-nsen !

<span id="an_20:26">20:26</span> Ur ilaq ara ad yili wannect-agi
gar-awen. Ma yella yiwen seg-wen yebɣa ad yuɣal d ameqqran, ilaq ad yili
d aqeddac-nwen.

<span id="an_20:27">20:27</span> Akken daɣen, win yebɣan ad yili d
amezwaru, ilaq ad yuɣal d akli-nwen.

<span id="an_20:28">20:28</span> Daymi Mmi-s n bunadem ur d-yusi ara
iwakken ad qedcen fell-as, meɛna yusa-d iwakken ad yili d aqeddac, yerna
ad isebbel tudert-is iwakken ad isellek aṭas n yemdanen.

<span id="an_20:29">20:29</span> Mi d-ffɣen si temdint n Yiriku, aṭas n
lɣaci i d-iḍefṛen Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_20:30">20:30</span> Llan sin iderɣalen qqimen rrif n
webrid, mi slan belli d Sidna Ɛisa i d-iɛeddan bdan țɛeggiḍen : A Sidi !
A mmi-s n Sidna Dawed ! Ḥunn fell-aɣ !

<span id="an_20:31">20:31</span> Lɣaci-nni țlumun-ten, qqaṛen asen ad
ssusmen, ma d nutni țkemmilen leɛyaḍ : Ḥunn fell-aɣ a Sidi, a mmi-s n
Sidna Dawed !

<span id="an_20:32">20:32</span> Sidna Ɛisa iḥbes, issawel-asen,
yenna-yasen : D acu i tebɣam a wen-t- xedmeɣ ?

<span id="an_20:33">20:33</span> Rran-as : Nebɣa a ɣ-d-yuɣal yeẓri a
Sidi !

<span id="an_20:34">20:34</span> Ɣaḍen aṭas Sidna Ɛisa, yennul
allen-nsen, imiren kan yuɣal-iten-id yeẓri, dɣa ddan yid-es.

<span id="an_21:1">21:1</span> Mi qṛib ad kecmen ɣer temdint n Lquds,
wwḍen ɣer yiɣil n uzemmur yellan tama n taddart n Bitfaji, Sidna Ɛisa
iceggeɛ sin inelmaden-is,

<span id="an_21:2">21:2</span> yenna-yasen : Ṛuḥet ɣer taddart yellan
ɣer zdat, dinna aț-țafem taɣyult akk-d mmi-s, brut-asen-d,
tawim-iyi-ten-id.

<span id="an_21:3">21:3</span> Ma yella win i wen-d-yennan kra, init-as
: d Ssid-nneɣ i ten-iḥwaǧen, imiren a sen-d-iserreḥ.

<span id="an_21:4">21:4</span> Ayagi yedṛa-d am akken i t-id yenna nnbi
Zakarya di tira iqedsen :

<span id="an_21:5">21:5</span> Init i wat wedrar n Siyun : AA taya
ugellid-nwen iteddu-d ɣuṛ-wen s wannuz, irkeb-ed ɣef weɣyul amecṭuḥ
mmi-s n teɣyult.

<span id="an_21:6">21:6</span> Inelmaden-nni ṛuḥen, xedmen ayen i
sen-d-yenna Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_21:7">21:7</span> Wwin-d taɣyult-nni d mmi-s, sburren-asen
llebsa-nsen, dɣa srekben Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_21:8">21:8</span> Aṭas n lɣaci ssan iceṭṭiḍen-nsen deg
ubrid, wiyaḍ țṛuẓun-d tiseḍwa si ttjuṛ, țessun-tent ula d nutni deg
ubrid.

<span id="an_21:9">21:9</span> Lɣaci yezwaren zdat Sidna Ɛisa d wid i
t-id-iḍefṛen, țɛeggiḍen s lfeṛḥ qqaṛen : Ḥusana i mmi-s n Sidna Dawed !
Ițțubarek win i d-yusan s yisem n Sidi Ṛebbi ! Ḥusana deg imukan
eɛlayen.

<span id="an_21:10">21:10</span> Mi gekcem Sidna Ɛisa ɣer temdint n
Lquds, imezdaɣ meṛṛa nhewwalen, qqaṛen : Anwa-t wagi ?

<span id="an_21:11">21:11</span> Lɣaci-nni țțaran-asen : D Sidna Ɛisa,
nnbi-nni n taddart n Naṣaret i d-yusan si tmurt n Jlili !

<span id="an_21:12">21:12</span> Sidna Ɛisa yekcem ɣer lǧameɛ iqedsen,
iqecceɛ meṛṛa wid yețțaɣen znuzun dinna deg ufrag n lǧameɛ. Iqleb-asen
ṭṭwabel i wid yețbeddilen idrimen akk-d wid yeznuzun itbiren.

<span id="an_21:13">21:13</span> dɣa yenna-yasen : Yura : Axxam-iw ad
ițțusemmi d axxam n tẓallit, ma d kunwi terram-t d lɣaṛ n imakaren.

<span id="an_21:14">21:14</span> Di lǧameɛ-nni, qeṛṛben-d ɣuṛ-es
iderɣalen d iquḍaren, dɣa yesseḥla ten.

<span id="an_21:15">21:15</span> Lmuqedmin imeqqranen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa rfan mi walan leɛǧayeb i gxeddem akk-d warrac ițɛeggiḍen di
lǧameɛ : Ḥusana i mmi-s n Sidna Dawed !

<span id="an_21:16">21:16</span> Imiren nnan i Sidna Ɛisa : Tesliḍ d acu
i d-qqaṛen ? SSidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Sliɣ ih ! Eɛni ur teɣṛim ara
imeslayen-agi yuran di tira iqedsen : Tessufɣeḍ-ed leḥmadi seg imawen n
warrac akk-d wid n llufanat iteṭṭḍen .

<span id="an_21:17">21:17</span> Imiren yeǧǧa-ten dinna, yeffeɣ si
temdint, iṛuḥ ɣer taddart n Bitanya, dinna i gensa.

<span id="an_21:18">21:18</span> Azekka-nni taṣebḥit mi d-yuɣal ɣer
temdint, Sidna Ɛisa yelluẓ ;

<span id="an_21:19">21:19</span> iwala yiwet n tneqleț rrif n webrid,
iqeṛṛeb ɣuṛ-es, ur yufi deg-s acemma anagar afriwen ; dɣa yenna-yas :
Seg wass-a, ur tețțuɣaleḍ ara a d-tefkeḍ lfakya ! IImiren kan,
taneqleț-nni teqquṛ.

<span id="an_21:20">21:20</span> Inelmaden-is mi walan ayagi tɛeǧben,
nnan : Amek akka teqquṛ tneqleț-agi deg yiwet n teswiɛt ?

<span id="an_21:21">21:21</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : A wen-iniɣ
tideț, ma yella tesɛam liman ur tețcukkum ara, aț-țizmirem aț-țxedmem
akteṛ n wayen xedmeɣ i tneqleț-agi ! AAț-ținim i wedrar-agi qleɛ iman-ik
syagi tḍeggṛeḍ iman-ik ɣer lebḥeṛ, ayagi a d-yedṛu !

<span id="an_21:22">21:22</span> Ayen akk ara tessutrem s liman di
tẓallit, a wen-d-ițunefk !

<span id="an_21:23">21:23</span> Sidna Ɛisa yekcem ɣer lǧameɛ ibda
yesselmad. Lmuqedmin akk-d imeqqranen n wegdud qeṛṛben ɣuṛ-es nnan-as :
Ansi i k-d-tekka tezmert s wayes i txeddmeḍ ayagi ? Anwa i k-d-yefkan
tazmert-agi ?

<span id="an_21:24">21:24</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : A wen-fkeɣ
asteqsi ula d nekk, yiwen kan ; ma tǧawbem-iyi-d, ula d nekk a wen-iniɣ
ansi i yi-d-tekka tezmert-agi.

<span id="an_21:25">21:25</span> Aɣḍas n Yeḥya, s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i d-ikka neɣ
s ɣuṛ yemdanen ? DDɣa bdan qqaṛen wway gar-asen : Ma nenna-yas seg
igenwan, a ɣ-d-yini acuɣeṛ ihi ur tuminem ara yis,

<span id="an_21:26">21:26</span> ma nenna-yas daɣen seg imdanen, nuggad
lɣaci-agi, axaṭer ḥesben akk Yeḥya d nnbi.

<span id="an_21:27">21:27</span> Dɣa nnan-as i Sidna Ɛisa : Ur neẓri ara
! YYerra-yasen : Ihi ula d nekk ur wen-d-qqaṛeɣ ara ansi i yi-d-tekka
tezmert s wayes i xeddmeɣ ayagi !

<span id="an_21:28">21:28</span> D acu twalam ? Yiwen wergaz yesɛa sin
warraw-is, yenṭeq ɣer umezwaru, yenna-yas : A mmi, ṛuḥ aț-țxedmeḍ
ass-agi di tfeṛṛant-iw.

<span id="an_21:29">21:29</span> Yerra-yas : Ur țṛuḥuɣ ara ! MMeɛna
yuɣal yendem, iṛuḥ ad ixdem di tfeṛṛant.

<span id="an_21:30">21:30</span> Yenna-yas daɣen i mmi-s wi sin ad iṛuḥ
ad ixdem, yerra-yas-d : Ih a baba ad ṛuḥeɣ ! MMeɛna ur iṛuḥ ara.

<span id="an_21:31">21:31</span> Anwa deg sen i gxedmen lebɣi n baba-s ?
RRran-as-ed : D amezwaru a Sidi ! SSidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : A wen-d-iniɣ
tideț, imekkasen imakaren akk-d yir tilawin a kkun zwiren ɣer tgelda n
igenwan !

<span id="an_21:32">21:32</span> Axaṭer Yeḥya yusa-d ɣuṛ-wen
yesken-awen-d abrid n tideț, meɛna ur t-tuminem ara ; ma d imekkasen d
yir tilawin umnen yis. Yerna ɣas akken twalam ayagi, ur d-tuɣalem ara
ɣer webrid teggumam aț-țamnem yis.

<span id="an_21:33">21:33</span> A wen-d-rnuɣ daɣen lemtel nniḍen :
yella yiwen umɛellem, yeẓẓa tafeṛṛant, izzi-yas-ed s zzeṛb, yeɣza amkan
i tɛeṣṣart n tẓurin, yebna taɛrict i tɛessast, issekra tafeṛṛant-is i
ixemmasen, imiren iṛuḥ ɣer lɣeṛba.

<span id="an_21:34">21:34</span> Mi d-yewweḍ lweqt n tẓurin, iceggeɛ
iqeddacen-is ɣer ixemmasen nni iwakken a s-d-fken amur-is n lɣella.

<span id="an_21:35">21:35</span> Meɛna ixemmasen-nni ṭṭfen
iqeddacen-nni, wa wten-t, wa nɣan-t, wayeḍ ṛejmen-t.

<span id="an_21:36">21:36</span> Iceggeɛ-asen daɣen tarbaɛt nniḍen n
iqeddacen yugaren tamezwarut. Meɛna tedṛa yid-sen am imezwura-nni.

<span id="an_21:37">21:37</span> Taggara, iceggeɛ-asen mmi-s, yenna :
Ahat imi d mmi a t-qadṛen !

<span id="an_21:38">21:38</span> Lameɛna mi walan mmi-s, ixemmasen-nni
nnan wway gar-asen : Ataya win ara iweṛten, kkret a t-nenneɣ iwakken a
nawi lweṛt-is.

<span id="an_21:39">21:39</span> Sṭfen-t, ḍeggṛen-t ɣer beṛṛa n
tfeṛṛant, dɣa nɣan-t.

<span id="an_21:40">21:40</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna i lɣaci : Ihi tura,
m'ara d-yas bab n tfeṛṛant-nni, d acu ara sen-yexdem i ixemmasen-agi ?

<span id="an_21:41">21:41</span> Rran-as-ed : Ad ineɣ ixemmasen imcumen,
ma ț-țafeṛṛant a ț-issekru i ixemmasen nniḍen ara s-d-ifken amur-is di
lweqt n lɣella.

<span id="an_21:42">21:42</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Leɛmeṛ teɣṛim
imeslayen-agi i d-nnant tira iqedsen : Adɣaɣ-nni i ḍeggṛen wid ibennun,
d nețța i guɣalen d azṛu alemmas , WWin yeṭṭfen lebni. AA yagi yekka-d s
ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, d ayen i ɣ-istɛeǧben .

<span id="an_21:43">21:43</span> Daymi i wen-qqaṛeɣ : Tagelda n igenwan
a wen tețwakkes, aț-țețțunefk i leǧnas nniḍen ara d-ifken lɣella.

<span id="an_21:44">21:44</span> Win ara yeɣlin ɣef wusalas-agi ad
yerreẓ, daɣen win i ɣef ara d-yeɣli usalas-agi ad yețwamḥeq.

<span id="an_21:45">21:45</span> Mi slan i imeslayen-agi, ifariziyen d
lmuqedmin imeqqranen fehmen belli fell-asen i d-iheddeṛ Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_21:46">21:46</span> Meɛna ɣas akken bɣan a t-ṭṭfen, ur
zmiren ara axaṭer uggaden lɣaci-nni i t-iḥesben d nnbi.

<span id="an_22:1">22:1</span> Sidna Ɛisa imeslay-asen-d daɣen s lemtel,
yenna-yasen : --

<span id="an_22:2">22:2</span> Tagelda n igenwan tcuba ɣer yiwen ugellid
i gxedmen tameɣṛa i mmi-s.

<span id="an_22:3">22:3</span> Iceggeɛ iqeddacen-is ad ssiwlen i wid
yețwaɛeṛden, meɛna ugin a d-asen.

<span id="an_22:4">22:4</span> Yerna iceggeɛ-asen iqeddacen nniḍen a
sen-inin : Heggaɣ imensi, zliɣ izgaren-iw d wakraren-iw, kullec ihegga,
aset-ed ɣer tmeɣṛa !

<span id="an_22:5">22:5</span> Meɛna widak-nni ițwaɛeṛḍen ur s-fkin ara
azal, yal yiwen yelha d ccɣel-is, wa iṛuḥ ɣer yiger-is, wa ɣer ssuq-is.

<span id="an_22:6">22:6</span> Wiyaḍ ṭṭfen iqeddacen-nni, regmen-ten,
nɣan-ten.

<span id="an_22:7">22:7</span> Agellid-nni ikcem-it zzɛaf d ameqqran,
dɣa iceggeɛ lɛeskeṛ-is nɣan iqettalen-nni, sseṛɣen tamdint-nsen.

<span id="an_22:8">22:8</span> Imiren yenna i iqeddacen-is : Imensi n
tmeɣṛa ihegga, meɛna widak-nni ițwaɛeṛḍen ur t-uklalen ara ;

<span id="an_22:9">22:9</span> ṛuḥet ɣer izenqan, tɛeṛḍem-d ɣer tmeɣṛa
wid akk ara tafem deg iberdan.

<span id="an_22:10">22:10</span> Iqeddacen-nni ṛuḥen ɣer izenqan
jemɛen-d wid akk ufan, ama d amcum ama d win yelhan, s wakka axxam n
tmeɣṛa yeččuṛ-ed d lɣaci.

<span id="an_22:11">22:11</span> Mi d-ikcem ugellid ad iwali inebgawen,
iwala yiwen wergaz ur yelsi ara llebsa n tmeɣṛa.

<span id="an_22:12">22:12</span> yenna-yas : Ay amdakkel, amek i
d-tkecmeḍ ɣer dagi mbla llebsa n tmeɣṛa yețwaheggan i yinebgawen ?
AArgaz-nni yessusem, ur yufi d acu ara s-yini.

<span id="an_22:13">22:13</span> Agellid-nni yefka lameṛ i iqeddacen-is
yenna-yasen : Cuddet-as ifassen d iḍaṛṛen, tḍeggṛem-t ɣer ṭṭlam n beṛṛa,
anda llan imeṭṭawen d nndama tameqqrant.

<span id="an_22:14">22:14</span> Axaṭer aṭas i gețwaɛerḍen, meɛna drus
ara yețwaqeblen.

<span id="an_22:15">22:15</span> Imiren ṛuḥen ifariziyen ad mcawaṛen
amek ara d-sseɣlin Sidna Ɛisa deg wawal.

<span id="an_22:16">22:16</span> Ceggɛen-as kra seg inelmaden-nsen akk-d
kra si terbaɛt n Hiṛudus, nnan-as : A Sidi, neẓra-k d bab n lḥeqq i
telliḍ, tesselmadeḍ iberdan n Ṛebbi s tideț, ur tuggadeḍ ula d yiwen, ur
txeddmeḍ ara lxilaf ger yemdanen.

<span id="an_22:17">22:17</span> Ini-yaɣ-d ihi d acu twalaḍ : d leḥlal
neɣ d leḥṛam a nxelleṣ tabzert ( leɣṛama ) i ugellid Qayṣar (yestɛemṛen
tamurt-nneɣ) ?

<span id="an_22:18">22:18</span> Meɛna Sidna Ɛisa yeẓran ayen i
țxemmimen, yenna-yasen : Ay at sin wudmawen ! Acuɣeṛ tebɣam a yi-tjeṛbem
?

<span id="an_22:19">22:19</span> Seknet-iyi-d aṣurdi s wacu țxelliṣen
tabzert ! FFkan-as-d aṣurdi n lfeṭṭa.

<span id="an_22:20">22:20</span> Dɣa isteqsa-ten : Udem akk-d tira
yellan deg uṣuṛdi-agi, wi ten-ilan ?

<span id="an_22:21">22:21</span> Rran-as : N Qayṣer ! IImiren
yenna-yasen : Erret ihi i Qayṣer ayen yellan n Qayṣer, terrem i Ṛebbi
ayen yellan n Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_22:22">22:22</span> Mi slan i imeslayen-agi, wehmen, dɣa
ṛuḥen ǧǧan-t.

<span id="an_22:23">22:23</span> Ass-nni, isaduqiyen i gellan d imdanen
ur nețțamen ara s ḥeggu n lmegtin, usan-d ɣer Sidna Ɛisa, steqsan-t,
nnan-as :

<span id="an_22:24">22:24</span> A Sidi, Sidna Musa yenna-d : ma yella
yemmut wergaz d amengur, ilaq gma-s ad yaɣ taǧǧalt-nni iwakken a d-isɛu
yid-es dderya ara iweṛten gma-s-nni yemmuten.

<span id="an_22:25">22:25</span> Yuɣ lḥal llan ɣuṛ-nneɣ sebɛa watmaten,
amezwaru izewǧen yemmut ur d-yeǧǧi dderya, dɣa gma-s yerra ( yuɣa )
tameṭṭut-nni.

<span id="an_22:26">22:26</span> Akkenni i tedṛa d wis sin, d wis tlata,
armi d wis sebɛa.

<span id="an_22:27">22:27</span> Mi mmuten irkulli, temmut ula
ț-țameṭṭut-nni ;

<span id="an_22:28">22:28</span> ass n ḥeggu n lmegtin anwa deg-sen ara
ț-yesɛun ț-țameṭṭut-is imi i ț-uɣen di sebɛa yid-sen ?

<span id="an_22:29">22:29</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yasen : Tɣelṭem !
Axaṭer ur tefhimem tira iqedsen, ur tessinem tazmert n Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_22:30">22:30</span> Ass n ḥeggu n lmegtin, irgazen
ț-țilawin ur zeggjen ara, meɛna ad uɣalen am lmalayekkat deg igenni.

<span id="an_22:31">22:31</span> Ɣef wayen yeɛnan ḥeggu n lmegtin, ur
teɣṛim ara acu i d-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi ? :

<span id="an_22:32">22:32</span> D nekk i d Illu n Ibṛahim, n Isḥaq, n
Yeɛqub. Sidi Ṛebbi mačči d Ṛebbi n lmegtin, meɛna d Ṛebbi n wid yeddren.

<span id="an_22:33">22:33</span> Mi s-slan, lɣaci qqimen țweḥḥiden deg
imeslayen-is !

<span id="an_22:34">22:34</span> Mi slan ifariziyen belli Sidna Ɛisa
yeɣleb isaduqiyen deg wawal, nnejmaɛen wway gar-asen.

<span id="an_22:35">22:35</span> Yiwen seg-sen d lɛalem n ccariɛa,
isteqsa-t iwakken a t-ijeṛṛeb :

<span id="an_22:36">22:36</span> A Sidi, anwa i d lameṛ ameqqran meṛṛa
di ccariɛa ?

<span id="an_22:37">22:37</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : -- Aț-țḥemleḍ
Illu Sidi Ṛebbi-inek seg wul-ik, s teṛwiḥt-ik, s wayen yellan di
tezmert-ik.

<span id="an_22:38">22:38</span> D wagi i d lameṛ yellan d amezwaru
yerna d ameqqran akk di ccariɛa.

<span id="an_22:39">22:39</span> Atan wayeḍ yesɛan azal annect
umezwaru-agi : Aț-țḥemleḍ lɣiṛ-ik am yiman-ik.

<span id="an_22:40">22:40</span> D sin lumuṛat-agi i d lsas n ccariɛa
akk-d lenbiya.

<span id="an_22:41">22:41</span> Mi llan ifariziyen nnejmaɛen, Sidna
Ɛisa isteqsa-ten yenna :

<span id="an_22:42">22:42</span> D acu ara d-tinim ɣef Lmasiḥ ? Ansi ara
d-yekk, yeɛni anwi i d lejdud-is ? NNnan-as : D mmi-s n Sidna Dawed.

<span id="an_22:43">22:43</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Amek ihi i
s-isemma Dawed s tezmert n Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen « Sidi » mi genna :

<span id="an_22:44">22:44</span> Sidi Ṛebbi yenna i Ssid-iw : ṭṭef amkan
ɣer tama-w tayeffust, alamma rriɣ iɛdawen-ik seddaw iḍaṛṛen-ik.

<span id="an_22:45">22:45</span> Ma yella ihi Dawed yessawel-as « Sidi »
amek ara yili ihi d mmi-s ?

<span id="an_22:46">22:46</span> Yiwen deg-sen ur izmir a s-d yerr awal,
seg wass-nni țțaggaden a t-steqsin.

<span id="an_23:1">23:1</span> Imiren Sidna Ɛisa yenṭeq ɣer lɣaci d
inelmaden-is yenna yasen :

<span id="an_23:2">23:2</span> Lɛulama d ifariziyen sselmaden ccariɛa n
Musa.

<span id="an_23:3">23:3</span> Xedmet ayen akk ara wen-d-inin, meɛna ur
xeddmet ara wayen xeddmen nutni, axaṭer ayen i d-qqaṛen ur t-xeddmen
ara.

<span id="an_23:4">23:4</span> Țcuddun tiɛekkmin ẓẓayen țɛebbin-tent ɣef
tuyat n yemdanen, ma d nutni țțagin a ten-ɛiwnen ula s yixef n
iḍuḍan-nsen.

<span id="an_23:5">23:5</span> Ayen akk i xeddmen, xeddmen-t iwakken a
ten-walin yemdanen, țɛelliqen tiḥerztin ț-țeɣṛisin ɣef yiman-nsen.

<span id="an_23:6">23:6</span> Ḥemmlen ad ṭṭfen imukan imezwura ama di
tmeɣṛiwin ama di leǧwameɛ, ḥemmlen m'ara țsellimen fell-asen yemdanen di
tejmuyaɛ akk-d leswaq ;

<span id="an_23:7">23:7</span> ḥemmlen daɣen m'ara sen-qqaṛen yemdanen :
« a Sidi ».

<span id="an_23:8">23:8</span> Ma d kunwi ɣuṛ-wat a wen qqaṛen : « a
Sidi » axaṭer d atmaten i tellam yerna yiwen kan i d Ssid-nwen.

<span id="an_23:9">23:9</span> Ur qqaṛet ula i yiwen di ddunit : « Baba
» axaṭer anagar yiwen i d baba-wen, d Baba Ṛebbi yellan deg igenwan.

<span id="an_23:10">23:10</span> Ur qebblet ara aț-țețțusemmim : «
imeqqranen » axaṭer anagar yiwen i d ameqqran : d Lmasiḥ !

<span id="an_23:11">23:11</span> Ameqqran deg-wen, d win iqeddcen
fell-awen.

<span id="an_23:12">23:12</span> Kra n win issimɣuṛen iman-is a d-yers,
ma d win issimẓiyen iman is ad ițwarfed !

<span id="an_23:13">23:13</span> A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa, ay at sin wudmawen ! AAxaṭer tmeddlem tiwwura n igenwan i
yemdanen, ur tkeččmem kunwi, ur tețțaǧǧam ad kecmen wid yebɣan !

<span id="an_23:14">23:14</span> A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa, ay at sin wudmawen ! Axaṭer tettețțem ayla n tuǧǧal,
tesṭuqqutem awal di tẓallit-nwen iwakken a d-tesbegnem iman-nwen telham.
Ɣef wayagi, lɛiqab i kkun-ițṛaǧun d ameqqran !

<span id="an_23:15">23:15</span> A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa, ay at sin udmawen ! Tețnadim timura, tzeggrem lebḥuṛ iwakken a
d-rebḥem ɣas ula d yiwen ɣer ddin i tettabaɛem; mi t-id-rnam ɣuṛ-wen,
tețțaram-t d win yuklalen ǧahennama akteṛ-nwen !

<span id="an_23:16">23:16</span> A nnger-nwen ay iderɣalen iteṭṭfen afus
i wiyaḍ ! Teqqaṛem : « Ma yella yeggul bunadem s lǧameɛ iqedsen, ɣas
yeḥnet ulac fell-as ; ma d win ara yegallen s ddheb yellan di lǧameɛ, ur
s-ilaq ara ad iḥnet, ilaq ad iṭṭef di limin-ines ! »

<span id="an_23:17">23:17</span> Ay imehbal, ay iderɣalen ! D acu i
gesɛan azal, d ddheb neɣ d lǧameɛ i gețțarran ddheb-nni d imqeddes ?

<span id="an_23:18">23:18</span> Teqqaṛem daɣen : « Win ara yegallen s
udekkan n iseflawen, ɣas iḥnet ulac fell-as, ma d win ara yegallen s
iseflawen nni, ur s-ilaq ara ad iḥnet, ilaq ad iṭṭef di limin-ines.»

<span id="an_23:19">23:19</span> Ay iderɣalen ! Anwa i gesɛan azal, d
iseflawen neɣ d udekkan-nni i gerran iseflawen d imqedsen ?

<span id="an_23:20">23:20</span> Win ara yegallen s udekkan n iseflawen,
yeggul s udekkan-nni d wayen akk yersen fell-as.

<span id="an_23:21">23:21</span> Win ara yegallen daɣen s lǧameɛ, yeggul
s lǧameɛ akk-d Win i gellan deg-s.

<span id="an_23:22">23:22</span> Win ara yegallen s igenwan, yeggul
daɣen s igenwan akk-d Sidi Ṛebbi iḥekkmen deg-sen.

<span id="an_23:23">23:23</span> A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa, ay at sin udmawen ! tețțakem leɛcuṛ ɣef nneɛneɛ, abesbas d
lkemmun, lameɛna tețțaǧǧam ɣer deffir lḥeqq, ṛṛeḥma d laman. DD
annect-agi i gețṛaǧu deg-wen Sidi Ṛebbi aț-țezwirem deg-sen a
ten-txedmem, mbla ma terram deg idis ayen nniḍen.

<span id="an_23:24">23:24</span> Ay iderɣalen iteṭṭfen afus i wiyaḍ !
Tețṣeffim tissit-nwen ɣef yizi, tesseblaɛem alɣem.

<span id="an_23:25">23:25</span> A nnger-wen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa, ay at sin wudmawen ! Axaṭer tessizdigem taqbuct d uḍebsi s
ufella kan, meɛna ɣer daxel-nsen ččuṛen ț-țukeṛdiwin d ṭṭmeɛ.

<span id="an_23:26">23:26</span> Ay afarizi aderɣal ! Ssizdeg uqbel
daxel n teqbuct d uḍebsi, iwakken ula s ufella-nsen ad izdigen !

<span id="an_23:27">23:27</span> A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa, ay at sin udmawen ! TTețțemcabim ɣer iẓekwan isebɣen s lǧir ; s
ufella cebḥen, ɣer daxel ččuṛen d iɣsan n lmegtin d rekku.

<span id="an_23:28">23:28</span> Akka ula d kunwi, tețbegginem-d
iman-nwen telham ɣer yemdanen, lameɛna zdaxel teččuṛem d leɣruṛ d cceṛ.

<span id="an_23:29">23:29</span> A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n
ccariɛa, ay at sin wudmawen ! Tbennum iẓekwan n lenbiya, tețcebbiḥem
iẓekwan n wid iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi,

<span id="an_23:30">23:30</span> teqqaṛem lemmer i nɛac di zzman n
lejdud-nneɣ, tili ur neqbil ara a nțekki yid-sen deg ussizel n idammen n
lenbiya.

<span id="an_23:31">23:31</span> S wakka tețcehhidem belli kunwi ț-țarwa
n wid ineqqen lenbiya

<span id="an_23:32">23:32</span> yerna kunwi tețkemmilem ayen xedmen
lejdud-nwen !

<span id="an_23:33">23:33</span> A ccetla n izerman ! Amek ara tmenɛem
si lɛiqab n ǧahennama ?

<span id="an_23:34">23:34</span> Daymi ara wen-d-ceggɛeɣ lenbiya,
imusnawen akk-d lɛulama. KKra seg-sen a ten-tenɣem, kra a ten-tsemmṛem
ɣef wumidag, kra nniḍen a ten-tejlekḍem di leǧwameɛ nwen yerna a
ten-tețqehhiṛem si temdint ɣer tayeḍ.

<span id="an_23:35">23:35</span> Ihi, idammen n iḥeqqiyen yuzzlen di
lqaɛa, si Habil aḥeqqi mmi-s n Adem armi d Zakarya mmi-s n Birikya, i
tenɣam ger lǧameɛ iqedsen d udekkan iseflawen, a d-uɣalen ɣer yiri-nwen.

<span id="an_23:36">23:36</span> A wen-d-iniɣ tideț : ayagi meṛṛa a
d-yeɣli ɣef lǧil-agi !

<span id="an_23:37">23:37</span> A tamdint n Lquds ! A tamdint n Lquds
ineqqen lenbiya, ireǧǧmen wid i m-d-ițuceggɛen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, acḥal n
tikkal i bɣiɣ a d-jemɛeɣ arraw-im akken tjemmeɛ tyaziṭ ifṛax-is ddaw
wafriwen-is, meɛna tegummaḍ !

<span id="an_23:38">23:38</span> Ihi atan wexxam-im ad yexlu !

<span id="an_23:39">23:39</span> Axaṭer aql-i a wen-iniɣ : ur tețțuɣalem
ara a yi-twalim, alamma d ass i deg ara d-tinim : Yețțubarek win i
d-yusan s yisem n Sidi Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_24:1">24:1</span> Mi d-iffeɣ si lǧameɛ iqedsen, Sidna Ɛisa
iteddu ad iṛuḥ. Inelmaden-is qeṛṛben-d ɣuṛ-es, țwehhin-as iwakken ad
yerr ddehn-is ɣer cbaḥa akk-d lebni n lǧameɛ iqedsen.

<span id="an_24:2">24:2</span> Meɛna Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Twalam
annect-agi meṛṛa ? A wen-iniɣ tideț : ur d-yețɣimi wezṛu ɣef wayeḍ,
kullec ad ihudd.

<span id="an_24:3">24:3</span> Yuli ɣer yiɣil n uzemmur iqqim weḥd-es,
inelmaden-is usan-d a t-steqsin nnan-as : Melmi ara d-idṛu wayen i d
tenniḍ, amek ara neɛqel ass ameqqran n tuɣalin-ik akk-d taggara n ddunit
?

<span id="an_24:4">24:4</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Ɣuṛ-wat win ara
wen-ikellxen !

<span id="an_24:5">24:5</span> Axaṭer aṭas n yemdanen ara d-yasen s
yisem-iw, a d-inin : «\` D nekk i d Lmasiḥ ! » Yerna ad kellxen aṭas n
lɣaci.

<span id="an_24:6">24:6</span> Aț-țeslem s ṭradat ț-țegrawliwin, meɛna
ɣuṛ-wat a kkun-iffeɣ leɛqel. Ur țțaggadet ara, axaṭer ilaq a d-yedṛu
wannect-a, meɛna mazal mačči d nnger n ddunit.

<span id="an_24:7">24:7</span> Agdud ad yennaɣ d wayeḍ, tagelda
aț-țeẓdem ɣef tayeḍ, a d-yili laẓ d zzelzlat deg waṭas n imukan.

<span id="an_24:8">24:8</span> Ayagi akk ara yedṛun, ad yili am lqeṛḥ
amezwaru n tmeṭṭut iṭṭfen addud.

<span id="an_24:9">24:9</span> Imiren a kkun-fken iwakken
aț-țețțuɛetbem, a kkun-nɣen, leǧnas meṛṛa a kkun-keṛhen ɣef ddemma n
yisem-iw.

<span id="an_24:10">24:10</span> Aṭas ara yeǧǧen liman-nsen, ad
msekṛahen, ad țemyexdaɛen wway gar-asen.

<span id="an_24:11">24:11</span> A d-nnulfun lenbiya n lekdeb, ad ɣuṛṛen
aṭas n lɣaci,

<span id="an_24:12">24:12</span> simmal ad yețzad lbaṭel, simmal
lmaḥibba n waṭas n yemdanen aț-țenqes.

<span id="an_24:13">24:13</span> Ma d win ara yeṭṭfen di liman-is alamma
ț-țaggara, ad ițțusellek.

<span id="an_24:14">24:14</span> Lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ ɣef tgelda n Sidi
Ṛebbi, ad ițțubecceṛ di ddunit meṛṛa iwakken leǧnas ad slen yis. Imiren
ara d-taweḍ taggara n ddunit.

<span id="an_24:15">24:15</span> M'ara twalim deg wemkan iqedsen win
iwumi semman lmuṣiba issengaren i ɣef d-ihḍeṛ nnbi Danyel ; ( win ara
yeɣṛen taktabt-agi n nnbi Danyel ad ifhem !)

<span id="an_24:16">24:16</span> Imiren, wid ara yilin di tmurt n Yahuda
ilaq ad rewlen ɣer idurar,

<span id="an_24:17">24:17</span> win ara yilin s ufella n ssqef, ur ilaq
ara ad ikcem ɣer wexxam iwakken a d-iddem lqecc-is,

<span id="an_24:18">24:18</span> win daɣen ara yilin di lexla, ur ilaq
ara ad yuɣal ɣer deffir iwakken a d-iddem abeṛnus-is !

<span id="an_24:19">24:19</span> A tawaɣit n tilawin ara yilin s tadist
akk-d țid ara yessuṭuḍen deg ussan-nni !

<span id="an_24:20">24:20</span> Dɛut ɣer Ṛebbi iwakken tarewla agi-nwen
ur d-tdeṛṛu ara di ccetwa neɣ deg wass n westeɛfu.

<span id="an_24:21">24:21</span> Axaṭer « ad yili yiwen n leɛtab ur
d-nelli seg wasmi d-tebda ddunit ar ass-a yerna ur ițțuɣal ara a d-yili
! »

<span id="an_24:22">24:22</span> Lemmer ur issenqes ara Sidi Ṛebbi deg
wussan-nni, tili yiwen ur imenneɛ, meɛna ɣef ddemma n wid yextaṛ ara
yeṣṣenqes i wussan-agi.

<span id="an_24:23">24:23</span> Imiren ma yenna-yawen-d yiwen : Lmasiḥ
atan dagi neɣ atan, dihin, ur țțamnet ara !

<span id="an_24:24">24:24</span> Axaṭer a d-asen wid ara yerren
iman-nsen d Lmasiḥ neɣ d lenbiya, ad xedmen lbeṛhanat d leɛǧayeb akk-d
licaṛat iwakken ad kelxen ma zemren ula d wid yextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_24:25">24:25</span> Atan nniɣ-awen-t-id ihi :

<span id="an_24:26">24:26</span> ma nnan-awen Lmasiḥ atan deg unezṛuf,
ur țṛuḥut ara, neɣ ma nnan-awen walit, atan deg umkan-ihin yeffren, ur
țțamnet ara.

<span id="an_24:27">24:27</span> Axaṭer asm'ara d-yas Mmi-s n bunadem,
ad yili am tafat n lbeṛeq m'ara d-tfeǧǧeǧ si cceṛq alamma d lɣeṛb.

<span id="an_24:28">24:28</span> Anda yella umuṛḍus ( lǧifa ), dinna ara
nnejmaɛen igudar.

<span id="an_24:29">24:29</span> M'ara ɛeddin wussan-nni n leɛtab, iṭij
ad inqes, aggur ur d-ițțak ara tiziri-ines, itran a d-ɣlin seg igenni,
tizmar n igenwan ad rgagint.

<span id="an_24:30">24:30</span> Imiren a d-iban Mmi-s n bunadem deg
igenni, leɛṛac meṛṛa n ddunit ad meǧden, a d wwten deg idmaren-nsen
m'ara walin Mmi-s n bunadem deg igenwan, yusa-d ɣef wusigna s tezmert
akk-d lɛaḍima tameqqrant.

<span id="an_24:31">24:31</span> A d-iceggeɛ lmalayekkat-is ad berrḥent
s ṣṣut n lbuq, a d snejmaɛent wid akk yextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, si yal amkan,
seg ixef n ddunit ɣer wayeḍ.

<span id="an_24:32">24:32</span> Meyzet ɣef lemtel n tneqleț : mi lqaqit
isegman-is, fsan wafriwen-is, teḥsam yewweḍ-d unebdu !

<span id="an_24:33">24:33</span> Ula d kunwi, m'ara twalim yewweḍ-ed
wannect-agi meṛṛa, ḥṣut belli Mmi-s n bunadem ițeddu-d, atan ɣer
tewwurt.

<span id="an_24:34">24:34</span> A wen-d-iniɣ tideț : lǧil-agi ur
ițɛedday ara alamma ideṛṛu-d wannect agi meṛṛa.

<span id="an_24:35">24:35</span> Igenni d lqaɛa ad fnun, ma d
imeslayen-iw ur fennun ara !

<span id="an_24:36">24:36</span> Meɛna ɣef wayen yeɛnan ass neɣ ssaɛa n
wannect-agi meṛṛa, yiwen ur ten-issin, ama d lmalayekkat n igenwan, ama
d Mmi-s n Ṛebbi, anagar Baba Ṛebbi i geẓran.

<span id="an_24:37">24:37</span> Am akken i tedṛa di zzman n nnbi Nuḥ,
akken daɣen ara tedṛu di lweqt n Mmi-s n bunadem.

<span id="an_24:38">24:38</span> Axaṭer deg ussan-nni uqbel a d-neflen
waman ɣef ddunit, imdanen llan tețțen, tessen, țemyezwaǧen, zeggjen i
warraw-nsen, armi d ass i deg yekcem nnbi Nuḥ ɣer lbabuṛ.

<span id="an_24:39">24:39</span> Yiwen ur ifaq s wacemma armi d-ḥemlen
waman i ten-yewwin, snegren-ten akk. AAkken ara tedṛu di lweqt n tuɣalin
n Mmi-s n bunadem !

<span id="an_24:40">24:40</span> Imiren, ger sin yergazen ara yilin deg
iger, yiwen ad ițwarfed wayeḍ a d-iqqim.

<span id="an_24:41">24:41</span> Ger snat n tilawin yeẓẓaden s tsirt,
yiwet aț-țețwarfed tayeḍ a d-teqqim !

<span id="an_24:42">24:42</span> Ɛasset ihi ur ɣefflet ara ! Axaṭer ur
teẓrim ara lweqt i deg ara d-yas Ssid-nwen !

<span id="an_24:43">24:43</span> Rret ddehn-nwen ɣer wayagi : lemmer
yeẓri bab n wexxam lweqt i deg ara d-yas umakar, tili ad iɛiwez ur iggan
ara, iwakken ur t-țțakren ara.

<span id="an_24:44">24:44</span> Daymi ula d kunwi heggit iman-nwen
axaṭer di lweqt i ɣef ur tebnim ara, ara d-yas Mmi-s n bunadem.

<span id="an_24:45">24:45</span> Anwa i d aqeddac aɛeqli i ɣef ara
yețkel bab n wexxam ? D win ara iwekkel ɣef wat wexxam-is meṛṛa, iwakken
a sen-yefk lqut-nsen di lawan.

<span id="an_24:46">24:46</span> Amarezg n uqeddac-agi ara d-yaf bab n
wexxam m'ara d-yaweḍ, yelha d ccɣel-nni.

<span id="an_24:47">24:47</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : a t-yerr d lewkil
ɣef wayla-s meṛṛa !

<span id="an_24:48">24:48</span> Meɛna ma yella axeddam-agi diri-t, ad
yini deg ul-is : bab n wexxam iɛeṭṭel, mazal ur d-ițas ara ;

<span id="an_24:49">24:49</span> dɣa ad ibdu ad ikkat iqeddacen n
wexxam-nni, ad iteț, ad itess nețța d isekṛanen.

<span id="an_24:50">24:50</span> Bab n wexxam a d-yas deg wass i ɣef ur
ibni ara uqeddac-nni, di lawan ur yeẓri.

<span id="an_24:51">24:51</span> A t-iqecceɛ, a t-iɛaqeb akken țwaɛaqben
at sin udmawen : imiren ara yilin imeṭṭawen d nndama tameqqrant.

<span id="an_25:1">25:1</span> Daymi deg wussan-nni, tagelda n igenwan
aț-țecbu ɣer ɛecṛa telmeẓyin i geddmen tiftilin-nsent iwakken ad ṛuḥent
ad mmagrent isli.

<span id="an_25:2">25:2</span> Xemsa seg-sent ț-țuḥṛicin, xemsa nniḍen
ț-țungifin.

<span id="an_25:3">25:3</span> Mi d-ddment tungifin-nni tiftilin nsent,
ur d-wwint ara zzit yid-sent.

<span id="an_25:4">25:4</span> Ma ț-țuḥṛicin-nni, wwint-ed yid-sent
tiqbucin n zzit.

<span id="an_25:5">25:5</span> Imi i gɛeṭṭel yesli, tilmeẓyin-nni
nuddment dɣa ṭsent.

<span id="an_25:6">25:6</span> Di tlemmast n yiḍ, yiwet n taɣect
tɛeggeḍ-ed : Ataya yesli iteddu-d, ffɣemt a t-temmagremt !

<span id="an_25:7">25:7</span> Imiren kan ukint-ed akk telmeẓyin-nni,
heggant tiftilin-nsent.

<span id="an_25:8">25:8</span> Tungifin-nni nnant i tuḥṛicin :
Fkemt-aɣ-d kra si zzit-nkunt, tiftilin-nneɣ qṛib ad xsint.

<span id="an_25:9">25:9</span> Tuḥṛicin rrant-asent : Ulamek, ur
aɣ-d-tkeffu ara i nekkunti d kunemti, ṛuḥemt a d taɣemt i yiman-nkunt
ɣer wid yeznuzun.

<span id="an_25:10">25:10</span> Mi ṛuḥent a d-aɣent, isli yewweḍ-ed,
tuḥṛicin-nni iheggan iman-nsent kecment yid-es ɣer wexxam n tmeɣṛa, dɣa
rran-d tawwurt.

<span id="an_25:11">25:11</span> Mi i d-wwḍent tungifin-nni, bdant
țɛeggiḍent : A Sidi, a Sidi ldi-yaɣ-d tawwurt.

<span id="an_25:12">25:12</span> Meɛna nețța yerra-yasent-ed : A
kunt-iniɣ tideț : ur kkunt ssineɣ ara !

<span id="an_25:13">25:13</span> Daymi a wen-iniɣ : Ɛasset, imi ur
teẓrim ass, ur teẓrim lweqt.

<span id="an_25:14">25:14</span> Ass n tuɣalin n Mmi-s n bunadem ad yili
daɣen am yiwen wergaz i gțeddun ad iṛuḥ ɣer lɣeṛba, yesnejmaɛ-ed
iqeddacen-is, iwekkel iten ɣef wayen akk yesɛa.

<span id="an_25:15">25:15</span> Ifka i umezwaru xemsmeyya twiztin n
ddheb, wi sin yefka-yas mitin, wis tlata yefka-yas meyya ; yefka i yal
yiwen s wakken tella tezmert-is, dɣa iṛuḥ.

<span id="an_25:16">25:16</span> Imiren kan, aqeddac-nni iwumi yefka
xemsmeyya twiztin, iṛuḥ yetjeṛ yis-sent, irbeḥ-ed xemsmeyya nniḍen.

<span id="an_25:17">25:17</span> Ula d win iwumi yefka mitin, ixdem
akken, irbeḥ-ed mitin nniḍen.

<span id="an_25:18">25:18</span> Ma d win iwumi yefka meyya, iṛuḥ yeɣza
di lqaɛa, yeffer tiwiztin-nni i s-d-ifka umɛellem-is.

<span id="an_25:19">25:19</span> Mi gɛedda lweqt, yuɣal-ed umɛellem-nni,
isnejmaɛ-iten-id iwakken ad imḥasab yid-sen.

<span id="an_25:20">25:20</span> Win akken iwumi yefka xemsmeyya
twiztin, yusa-d yewwi-d yid-es xemsmeyya twiztin nniḍen, yenna-yas : A
Sidi tefkiḍ-iyi-d xemsmeyya twiztin n ddheb, a tent-ih xemsmeyya nniḍen
i d-rebḥeɣ yis-sent.

<span id="an_25:21">25:21</span> Amɛellem-is yenna-yas : D ayen yelhan i
txedmeḍ ay aqeddac unṣiḥ, imi deg-ek laman ɣef tɣawsiwin timecṭuḥin, sya
d asawen a k-wekkleɣ ɣef timeqqranin ! Ili-k di lfeṛḥ yid-i !

<span id="an_25:22">25:22</span> Aqeddac-nni iwumi yefka mitin twiztin n
ddheb, iqeṛṛeb-ed ula d nețța, yenna-yas : A Sidi tefkiḍ-iyi mitin
twiztin n ddheb, a tent-ih mitin nniḍen i d-rebḥeɣ yis-sent.

<span id="an_25:23">25:23</span> Amɛellem-is yenna-yas : D ayen yelhan i
txedmeḍ, ay aqeddac unṣiḥimi deg-k laman ɣef tɣawsiwin timecṭuḥin, sya d
asawen a k-wekkleɣ ɣef timeqqranin ! Ili-k di lfeṛḥ yid-i !

<span id="an_25:24">25:24</span> Iwweḍ-ed win akken iwumi yefka meyya
twiztin, yenna yas : A Sidi ẓriɣ-k d argaz iweɛṛen, tmeggreḍ anda ur
tezriɛeḍ, tjemmɛeḍ seg wennar ayen ur tesrewteḍ ,

<span id="an_25:25">25:25</span> dɣa uggadeɣ-k, daymi i ṛuḥeɣ ffreɣ deg
wakal tiwiztin-nni i yi-tefkiḍ. Atan wayla-k, ddem-it !

<span id="an_25:26">25:26</span> Amɛellem-is yenna-yas : Ay aqeddac
amcum, ameɛdaz ! Imi iyi-teẓriḍ meggreɣ-d anda ur zriɛeɣ, jemmɛeɣ-ed
daɣen anda ur srewteɣ,

<span id="an_25:27">25:27</span> acuɣeṛ ihi ur tessekraḍ ara idrimin-iw
iwakken m'ara d-uɣaleɣ a ten-id-erreɣ s lfayda.

<span id="an_25:28">25:28</span> Imiren amɛellem-nni yumeṛ i
iqeddacen-is yenna-yasen : Kkset-as meyya-nni twiztin ternum-tent i win
yesɛan ɛecṛa alef n twiztin !

<span id="an_25:29">25:29</span> Axaṭer kra win yesɛan, a s-nernu ad
yili di tawant, ma d win ur nesɛi ara, a s-nekkes ula d ayen yesɛa.

<span id="an_25:30">25:30</span> Ma d aqeddac-agi ur nemɛin, ḍeggṛet-eț
ɣer ṭṭlam n beṛṛa anda ara yilin imeṭṭawen d nndama tameqqrant.

<span id="an_25:31">25:31</span> Asm'ara d-yas Mmi-s n bunadem di
tmanegt-is nețța d lmalayekkat meṛṛa, ad iḥkem di lɛaḍima-s ;

<span id="an_25:32">25:32</span> leǧnas meṛṛa a d-nnejmaɛen zdat-es, a
ten-ifṛeq am umeksa iɛeSlen ulli ɣef tɣeṭṭen.

<span id="an_25:33">25:33</span> Ad yerr ulli ɣer uyeffus-is, tiɣeṭṭen
ɣer uzelmaḍ-is.

<span id="an_25:34">25:34</span> Imiren agellid ad yini i wid yellan ɣer
uyeffus-is : Aset-ed a kunwi iburek Baba, aț-țweṛtem tagelda i
wen-ițțuheggan seg wasmi i tebda ddunit.

<span id="an_25:35">25:35</span> Axaṭer lliɣ lluẓeɣ tefkam-iyi ččiɣ,
ffudeɣ tefkam-iyi swiɣ, usiɣ-ed d abeṛṛani testeṛḥbem yis-i,

<span id="an_25:36">25:36</span> lliɣ d aɛeryan tesselsem-iyi, d amuḍin
telham-d yid-i, lliɣ daɣen d ameḥbus tusam-d teẓram-iyi.

<span id="an_25:37">25:37</span> Imiren iḥeqqiyen a s-d-rren : A Sidi
melmi i k-neẓra telluẓeḍ, nefka-yak teččiḍ ? Neɣ neẓra-k teffuḍeḍ
nefka-yak teswiḍ ?

<span id="an_25:38">25:38</span> Melmi daɣen i d-tusiḍ d abeṛṛani
nesṭeṛḥeb yis-ek, neɣ melmi i k-nwala d aɛeryan, nessels-ik ?

<span id="an_25:39">25:39</span> Melmi i k-neẓra d amuḍin neɣ di lḥebs
nusa-d ɣuṛ-ek ?

<span id="an_25:40">25:40</span> Agellid a sen-d-yerr : A wen-iniɣ
tideț, yal tikkelt i deg txedmem ayagi i yiwen seg imecṭuḥen-agi yellan
d atmaten-iw, i nekk iwumi t-txedmem.

<span id="an_25:41">25:41</span> Imiren ad yini i wid yellan ɣer
uẓelmaḍ-is : Beɛdet akkin fell-i a kunwi yețwaneɛlen, ṛuḥet ɣer tmes n
dayem yețwaheggan i Cciṭan d wid i t- tebɛen.

<span id="an_25:42">25:42</span> Axaṭer lliɣ lluẓeɣ ur iyi tesseččem
ara, ffudeɣ ur iyi-tefkim ara ad sweɣ,

<span id="an_25:43">25:43</span> usiɣ-ed d abeṛṛani ur tesṭerḥbem ara
yis-i, lliɣ d aɛeryan ur iyi tesselsem ara, lliɣ daɣen d amuḍin, d
ameḥbus, ur d-tusim ara aț-țesteqsim fell-i.

<span id="an_25:44">25:44</span> Imiren ula d nutni a s-d-rren : A Sidi,
melmi i k-neẓra telluẓeḍ neɣ teffudeḍ d abeṛṛani neɣ d aɛeryan, d amuḍin
neɣ d ameḥbus, ur d-nelhi ara yid-ek ?

<span id="an_25:45">25:45</span> Nețța a sen-d-yerr : A wen-iniɣ tideț :
yal tikkelt i deg ur texdimem ara ayagi i yiwen seg imecṭuḥen-agi, i
nekk iwumi ur t-texdimem ara.

<span id="an_25:46">25:46</span> Imiren widak-agi ad kecmen ɣer lɛiqab
ur nfennu, ma d iḥeqqiyen ad kecmen ɣer tudert n dayem !

<span id="an_26:1">26:1</span> Mi gfukk Sidna Ɛisa imeslayen-agi, yenna
i inelmaden-is : --

<span id="an_26:2">26:2</span> Mazal sin wussan i lɛid n Tuffɣa, Mmi-s n
bunadem ad ițțuzenz iwakken ad ițuṣemmer ɣef wumidag.

<span id="an_26:3">26:3</span> Dɣa lmuqedmin imeqqranen akk-d imeqqranen
n wegdud nnejmaɛen deg ufrag n Kayef, i gellan d lmuqeddem ameqqran.

<span id="an_26:4">26:4</span> Msefhamen ad ṭṭfen Sidna Ɛisa s tḥila
iwakken a t-nɣen.

<span id="an_26:5">26:5</span> Meɛna nnan : « mačči deg ussan-agi n lɛid
n Tuffɣa ara t-neḥbes, neɣ m'ulac ad yekker ccwal ger lɣaci .»

<span id="an_26:6">26:6</span> Mi gella Sidna Ɛisa di taddart n Bitanya,
deg wexxam n Semɛun abeṛsi,

<span id="an_26:7">26:7</span> ațaya yiwet n tmeṭṭut tewwi-d tabuqalt
yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ amellal, teččuṛ d leɛṭeṛ ɣlayen. Mi geqqim Sidna
Ɛisa ɣer ṭṭabla, tameṭṭut-nni tusa-d tesmar leɛṭeṛ-nni ɣef wuqeṛṛuy-is.

<span id="an_26:8">26:8</span> Mi walan ayagi, inelmaden iɣaḍ-iten lḥal,
nnan : Iwumi lexsaṛa-yagi ?

<span id="an_26:9">26:9</span> Lemmer nezzenz leɛṭeṛ-nni, tili yewwi-d
ssuma tameqqrant ara nefṛeq i igellilen !

<span id="an_26:10">26:10</span> Sidna Ɛisa yeẓran wayen nnan
wway-gar-asen, yenna-yasen : Acuɣeṛ i tesḥeznem tameṭṭut agi ? D ayen
yelhan i yi-texdem !

<span id="an_26:11">26:11</span> Axaṭer aț-țesɛum daymen igellilen
yid-wen, meɛna nekk ur țțiliɣ ara daymen yid-wen.

<span id="an_26:12">26:12</span> Mi d-tesmar leɛṭeṛ-agi fell-i, d
lǧețța-w i thegga i temḍelt-iw.

<span id="an_26:13">26:13</span> A wen-iniɣ tideț : di yal amkan n
ddunit i deg ara ițțubecceṛ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, a d țmektayen tameṭṭut-agi d
wayen texdem.

<span id="an_26:14">26:14</span> Imiren Yudas n Qeṛyut, yiwen si
tnac-nni inelmaden n Sidna Ɛisa, iṛuḥ ɣer lmuqedmin imeqqranen,

<span id="an_26:15">26:15</span> yenna yasen : Ma wwiɣ-kkun ɣuṛ-es a
t-id teṭṭfem, d acu ara yi-tefkem ? FFkan-as tlatin iṣurdiyen n lfeṭṭa.

<span id="an_26:16">26:16</span> Seg imiren, Yudas yețɛassa tagniț i deg
ara yizmir ad izzenz Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_26:17">26:17</span> Ass amezwaru n lɛid n weɣṛum mbla iɣes
n temtunt , inelmaden usan-d ɣer Sidna Ɛisa nnan-as : A Sidi, anda
tebɣiḍ a k-nheggi imensi n lɛid n Izimer n leslak ?

<span id="an_26:18">26:18</span> Yerra-yasen : Ṛuḥet ɣer temdint, ɣer
leflani, init-as : yenna-yak Ssid-nneɣ, lweqt-iw yewweḍ-ed, deg uxxam-ik
ara sɛeddiɣ lɛid n Izimer n leslak nekk d inelmaden-iw.

<span id="an_26:19">26:19</span> Inelmaden-nni xedmen ayen i sen-yenna
Sidna Ɛisa, heggan imensi n lɛid n Izimer n leslak.

<span id="an_26:20">26:20</span> Mi d-teɣli tmeddit, Sidna Ɛisa yeqqim
ad yečč nețța d inelmaden-is.

<span id="an_26:21">26:21</span> Mi llan tețțen yenna-yasen : A wen-iniɣ
tideț : yiwen seg-wen ad iyi-izzenz.

<span id="an_26:22">26:22</span> Mi d-yenna ayagi, ikcem-iten akk leḥzen
d ameqqran, bdan qqaṛen as yiwen yiwen : Neɣ mačči d nekk a Sidi ?

<span id="an_26:23">26:23</span> Yerra-yasen : Win igren afus-is yid-i
deg uḍebsi, d nețța ara yi-izzenzen.

<span id="an_26:24">26:24</span> Ad yedṛu d Mmi-s n bunadem akken yura
fell-as ; mmeɛna a nnger n win ara t-izzenzen, lemmer ur d-ilul ara
axiṛ-is.

<span id="an_26:25">26:25</span> Yudas ara t-ixedɛen yenṭeq yenna-yas :
Eɛni d nekk a Sidi ? SSidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Atan tenniḍ-t-id !

<span id="an_26:26">26:26</span> Mi llan tețțen, Sidna Ɛisa yeddem-d
aɣṛum, iḥmed Ṛebbi, icekkeṛ-it, dɣa yebḍa-t, ifṛeq-it i inelmaden-is,
yenna-yasen : Eččet aɣṛum-agi : d lǧețța-w.

<span id="an_26:27">26:27</span> Iddem-ed daɣen taqbuct, iḥmed Ṛebbi,
icekkeṛ-it, yefka-yasen-ț, yenna-yasen : Swet akk si teqbuct-agi,

<span id="an_26:28">26:28</span> axaṭer ayagi d idammen-iw, d idammen n
lemɛahda ara yazzlen ɣef yizumal n lɣaci ɣef ddemma n leɛfu n
ddnubat-nsen.

<span id="an_26:29">26:29</span> A wen-d-iniɣ : ur țțuɣaleɣ ara ad sweɣ
seg waman-agi n tẓurin alamma d ass i deg ara ten-sweɣ d ijdiden
yid-wen, di tgelda n Baba Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_26:30">26:30</span> Mi ḥemden Sidi Ṛebbi s ccnawi d isefra,
ṛuḥen ulin ɣer yiɣil n uzemmur,

<span id="an_26:31">26:31</span> dinna Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasen : Iḍ-agi
ad a wen-iliɣ akk d sebba n tuccḍa, axaṭer yura di tira iqedsen ad wwteɣ
ameksa, ulli n tqeḍɛit-is ad rewlent ɣer yal tama .

<span id="an_26:32">26:32</span> Meɛna m'ara d-ḥyuɣ si ger lmegtin, ad
iyi-tafem zwareɣ ɣer tmurt n Jlili.

<span id="an_26:33">26:33</span> Buṭrus yenṭeq, yenna : Ɣas a sen-tiliḍ
d sebba n tuccḍa i wiyaḍ akk, nekk d lmuḥal ad ccḍeɣ.

<span id="an_26:34">26:34</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : A k-iniɣ tideț :
deg iḍ-agi uqbel ad iskkuɛ uyaziḍ, ad iyi-tnekṛeḍ tlata iberdan.

<span id="an_26:35">26:35</span> Buṭrus yerra-yas : Ɣas lukan d lmut ara
mmteɣ yid-ek, d lmuḥal a k-nekkṛeɣ ! UUla d inelmaden nniḍen, nnan-as am
nețța.

<span id="an_26:36">26:36</span> Imiren Sidna Ɛisa iṛuḥ yid-sen ɣer
yiwen wemkan ițțusemman Jitsimani, yenna i inelmaden-is : Qqimet dagi,
nekk ad ṛuḥeɣ ad dɛuɣ ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_26:37">26:37</span> Yewwi yid-es Buṭrus akk-d sin
warraw-nni n Zabadi ; yebda ikcem-it leḥzen d leɣben d ameqqran.

<span id="an_26:38">26:38</span> Dɣa yenna-yasen : Ḥusseɣ s leḥzen n
lmut, qqimet dagi, ɛiwzet yid-i !

<span id="an_26:39">26:39</span> Iṛuḥ yeɣli ɣef wudem, ibda yețẓalla
yeqqaṛ : A Baba Ṛebbi, ma yella wamek , ssebɛed fell-i leɛtab-agi !
Meɛna akken tebɣiḍ keččini, mačči akken bɣiɣ nekkini.

<span id="an_26:40">26:40</span> Yuɣal-ed ɣer inelmaden-is, yufa-ten-id
ṭṭsen, yenna i Buṭrus : Ur tezmirem ara aț-țɛiwzem yid-i ula d yiwet n
ssaɛa ?

<span id="an_26:41">26:41</span> Ɛiwzet, ẓallet, iwakken ur tɣellim ara
deg ujeṛṛeb ! Axaṭer ṛṛuḥ n wemdan yeǧhed ma d lǧețța ur tezmir ara !

<span id="an_26:42">26:42</span> Ibɛed akkin tikkelt tis snat iwakken ad
iẓẓal, yenna : A Baba, ma yella ulamek ara tesbeɛdeḍ fell-i leɛtab-agi ,
ma ilaq ad iyi-d-yaweḍ ! Ad yedṛu lebɣi-k !

<span id="an_26:43">26:43</span> Mi d-yuɣal, yufa-ten-id daɣen ṭṭsen,
iɣleb-iten nuddam.

<span id="an_26:44">26:44</span> Yeǧǧa-ten, issebɛed iman-is daɣen
fell-asen, yedɛa tikkelt tis tlata am tikkelt-nni tamezwarut.

<span id="an_26:45">26:45</span> Mi d-yuɣal ɣer inelmaden-is,
yufa-ten-id mazal-iten ṭṭsen ; yenna yasen : Lweqt i deg ara yețwasellem
Mmi-s n bunadem ɣer ifassen n yemcumen iwweḍ-ed, kunwi mazal ikkun
teṭṭsem ?

<span id="an_26:46">26:46</span> Dɣa yenna-yasen : Ekkret fell-awen,
ataya iteddu-d win i yi-izzenzen !

<span id="an_26:47">26:47</span> Mazal-it ițmeslay mi d-iwweḍ Yudas
yellan d yiwen si tnac-nni inelmaden. Ddan-d yid-es aṭas n lɣaci s
iɛekkzan d ijenwiyen, ceggɛen ten-id imeqqranen n lmuqedmin akk-d
imeqqranen n wegdud.

<span id="an_26:48">26:48</span> Win akken i t-izzenzen, imsefham
yid-sen, yenna-yasen : Win i ɣef ara selmeɣ, d win ara teṭṭfem !

<span id="an_26:49">26:49</span> Imiren, iqeṛṛeb ɣer Sidna Ɛisa
yenna-yas : Sslam fell-ak a Sidi ! DDɣa isellem fell-as.

<span id="an_26:50">26:50</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Ay amdakkel ,
ayen ɣef i d-tusiḍ a t-txedmeḍ, xdem-it ! DDɣa lɣaci-nni qeṛṛben ɣer
Sidna Ɛisa ṭṭfen-t.

<span id="an_26:51">26:51</span> Yiwen seg wid yeddan d Sidna Ɛisa
ijbed-ed ajenwi-ines, yewwet aqeddac n lmuqeddem ameqqran, igzem-as-d
ameẓẓuɣ-is.

<span id="an_26:52">26:52</span> Sidna Ɛisa yenṭeq yenna-yas : Err
ajenwi-inek ɣer wemkan-is, axaṭer kra win ara irefden ajenwi, ad immet s
ujenwi !

<span id="an_26:53">26:53</span> Eɛni tɣileḍ ur zmireɣ ara ad ssutreɣ i
Baba ad iyi-d-iceggeɛ luluf n lmalayekkat ?

<span id="an_26:54">26:54</span> Amek ihi ara țwakemlent tira iqedsen i
d-ixebbṛen belli ilaq a d-yedṛu wayagi meṛṛa ?

<span id="an_26:55">26:55</span> Imiren Sidna Ɛisa yenna i lɣaci : Kull
ass țțiliɣ yid-wen di lǧameɛ sselmadeɣ, ur iyi-teṭṭifem ara, ass-agi
tusam-d ɣuṛ-i s iɛekkzan d ijenwiyen am akken d bu tmegṛaḍ i lliɣ !

<span id="an_26:56">26:56</span> Meɛna annect-agi meṛṛa yedṛa-d iwakken
ad țwakemlent tira n lenbiya. IImiren, inelmaden meṛṛa ǧǧan-t, yal yiwen
ɣer wanda yerwel.

<span id="an_26:57">26:57</span> Wid yeṭṭfen Sidna Ɛisa wwin-t ɣer
Kayef, ameqqran n lmuqedmin, anda i nnejmaɛen lɛulama n ccariɛa d
imeqqranen n wegdud.

<span id="an_26:58">26:58</span> Buṭrus iḍfeṛ-it, ikcem ɣer wefrag n
lmuqeddem ameqqran, yeqqim akk-d iɛessasen n lǧameɛ iwakken ad iẓer amek
ara tefru temsalt.

<span id="an_26:59">26:59</span> Imiren lmuqedmin imeqqranen akk-d
usqamu n imeqqranen n ccariɛa, țnadin inigan ara icehden fell-as s ẓẓuṛ,
iwakken ad ḥekmen fell-as s lmut,

<span id="an_26:60">26:60</span> meɛna ur s-d-ufin ara sebba, ɣas akken
aṭas i d-icehden fell-as.

<span id="an_26:61">26:61</span> A ten-aya sin yergazen qeṛṛben d nnan :
D wagi i d-yennan : « zemreɣ ad huddeɣ lǧameɛ iqedsen n Sidi Ṛebbi, a
s-ɛiwdeɣ lebni di tlata wussan.»

<span id="an_26:62">26:62</span> Ameqqran n lmuqedmin ikker, yenna-yas :
Ulac ayen ara d-terreḍ ɣef wayen akka i d-ccetkan fell-ak ?

<span id="an_26:63">26:63</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessusem. Dɣa ameqqran n
lmuqedmin yenna-yas : Wekkleɣ-ak Sidi Ṛebbi yeddren, m'ur aɣ-d-tenniḍ ma
d kečč i d Lmasiḥ, Mmi-s n Sidi Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_26:64">26:64</span> Sidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Tenniḍ-t-id !
Yerna a wen-iniɣ, ssya d asawen : Mmi-s n bunadem aa d iḥkem ɣɣ er
uyeffus n Bab n tezmert, a t-twalim iteddu-d ɣef wusigna seg yigenni.

<span id="an_26:65">26:65</span> Imiren ameqqran n lmuqedmin icerreg
aqenduṛ-is yenna : Ikfeṛ ! Iwumi neḥwaǧ inigan tura ? Teslam akk d acu i
d-yenna ! D acu tennam ?

<span id="an_26:66">26:66</span> Rran-as-d : Yuklal lmut !

<span id="an_26:67">26:67</span> Dɣa bdan ssusufen-t, țțaken-as
tiyitiwin d ibeqqayen,

<span id="an_26:68">26:68</span> qqaṛen-as : Eɛqel a Lmasiḥ, ini-yaɣ-d
anwa i k-iwwten !

<span id="an_26:69">26:69</span> Buṭrus yella yeqqim deg ufrag,
tqeṛṛeb-ed ɣuṛ-es yiwet n tqeddact tenna-yas : Ula d kečč telliḍ d Ɛisa
ajlili !

<span id="an_26:70">26:70</span> Meɛna yenkeṛ zdat-sen meṛṛa yenna-yas :
Ur ẓriɣ ara d acu tebɣiḍ a d tiniḍ !

<span id="an_26:71">26:71</span> Akken ițeddu ɣer tewwurt, twala-t
tqeddact nniḍen, tenna i wid akk yellan dinna : Wagi yella akk-d Ɛisa
anaṣari !

<span id="an_26:72">26:72</span> Inkeṛ daɣen s limin : Qqaṛeɣ-awen ur
ssineɣ ara argaz-agi !

<span id="an_26:73">26:73</span> Taswiɛt kan, wid yellan dinna qeṛṛben
daɣen ɣer Buṭrus nnan-as : Mbla ccekk, kečč telliḍ seg-sen, tameslayt-ik
tbeggen-ed belli d ajlili i telliḍ !

<span id="an_26:74">26:74</span> Ibda yețgalla irennu : Di leɛmeṛ ur
ssineɣ argaz-agi ! IImiren kan yeskkuɛ uyaziḍ.

<span id="an_26:75">26:75</span> Dɣa Buṭrus immekta-d imeslayen-nni i
s-d-yenna Sidna Ɛisa : uqbel ad iskkuɛ uyaziḍ, ad iyi-tnekṛeḍ tlata n
tikkal . Yeffeɣ ɣer beṛṛa s nndama tameqqrant, iṭṭerḍeq d imeṭṭawen.

<span id="an_27:1">27:1</span> Taṣebḥit, nnejmaɛen-d akk imeqqranen n
lmuqedmin akk-d imeqqranen n wegdud, mcawaṛen iwakken ad nɣen Sidna
Ɛisa.

<span id="an_27:2">27:2</span> Dɣa urzen-t, wwin-t i Bilaṭus, yellan d
lḥakem n Ṛuman yesteɛemṛen tamurt.

<span id="an_27:3">27:3</span> Mi gwala ḥekmen ɣef Sidna Ɛisa, Yudas-nni
i t-ixedɛen yendem. DDi nndama-nni-ines tameqqrant, iṛuḥ ɣer imeqqranen
n lmuqedmin d imeqqranen n wegdud, yerra-yasen tlatin-nni twiztin n
lfeṭṭa, dɣa

<span id="an_27:4">27:4</span> yenna yasen : Denbeɣ, nekk i
wen-d-izzenzen amdan aḥeqqi. RRran-as-d : Ur aɣ-d-tewqiɛ ara lmeɛna,
wagi d ccɣel-ik.

<span id="an_27:5">27:5</span> Yudas iḍeggeṛ tiwiztin-nni di lǧameɛ
iqedsen, imiren iṛuḥ iɛelleq iman-is.

<span id="an_27:6">27:6</span> Imeqqranen n lmuqedmin leqḍen-d
tiwiztin-nni n lfeṭṭa, nnan : Ur yeḥlil ara a tent-nerr ɣer usenduq n
lǧameɛ iqedsen, imi d lexlaṣ n temgeṛt.

<span id="an_27:7">27:7</span> Mi mcawaṛen d acu ara xedmen s
twiztin-nni, msefhamen iwakken ad aɣen iger n yiwen wergaz ixeddmen
afexxaṛ, iwakken a t-erren ț-țimeqbeṛt i ibeṛṛaniyen.

<span id="an_27:8">27:8</span> Daymi iger-agi ițțusemma ar ass-a : «
Iger n idammen ».

<span id="an_27:9">27:9</span> S wakka i gedṛa wayen i d-yenna nnbi
Irmiya : Ddmen-d tlatin n twiztin n lfeṭṭa, d wagi i d azal i s-fkan
warraw n wat Isṛail ;

<span id="an_27:10">27:10</span> uɣen-d yis iger ɣer win ixeddmen
afexxaṛ, akken i yi-d-yumeṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.

<span id="an_27:11">27:11</span> Sidna Ɛisa ibedd zdat lḥakem Bilaṭus.
Yesteqsa-t lḥakem-nni yenna-yas : D kečč i d agellid n wat Isṛail ?
SSidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Tenniḍ-t-id !

<span id="an_27:12">27:12</span> Lmuqedmin imeqqranen akk-d imeqqranen n
wegdud sseḍlamen deg-s, ma d nețța ur sen-d-yerri ula d acemma.

<span id="an_27:13">27:13</span> Bilaṭus yenna i Sidna Ɛisa : Eɛni ur
tesliḍ ara ayen akk ɣef i d-țcetkin fell-ak ?

<span id="an_27:14">27:14</span> Sidna Ɛisa yessusem, ur as-d yerri ula
d yiwen wawal, ayagi d ayen iswehmen lḥakem.

<span id="an_27:15">27:15</span> Lḥakem yennum di mkul lɛid n Tuffɣa
ițserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus i gextaṛ lɣaci.

<span id="an_27:16">27:16</span> Yella yakan yiwen umeḥbus mechuṛen,
ițțusemman Barabas.

<span id="an_27:17">27:17</span> Mi d-nnejmaɛen akk lɣaci, Bilaṭus
isteqsa-ten : Anwa i tebɣam a s-d-serrḥeɣ : i Barabas neɣ i Ɛisa
ițțusemman Lmasiḥ ?

<span id="an_27:18">27:18</span> Axaṭer yeẓra s tismin i s-d-wwin Ɛisa.

<span id="an_27:19">27:19</span> Mi gella Bilaṭus ițcaṛaɛ, tceggeɛ-as-d
tmeṭṭut-is, tenna-yas-d : Ur ssekcam ara iman-ik di temsalt n
uḥeqqi-agi, axaṭer ass-agi targit urgaɣ fell-as terwi-yi.

<span id="an_27:20">27:20</span> Imeqqranen n lmuqedmin akk-d imeqqranen
n wegdud sḥeṛcen-d lɣaci iwakken ad ssutren a d-serrḥen i Barabas, ad
nɣen Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_27:21">27:21</span> Lḥakem yenna-yasen : Anwa ger sin-agi
iwumi tebɣam ad serrḥeɣ ? RRran-as : I Barabas ! Serreḥ-ed i Barabas !

<span id="an_27:22">27:22</span> Bilaṭus yenna-yasen : D acu ara xedmeɣ
ihi i Ɛisa ițțusemman Lmasiḥ ? RRran-as-d akk : Ad ițțusemmeṛ ɣef
wumidag !

<span id="an_27:23">27:23</span> Lḥakem yenna : D acu i gexdem n diri ?
RRnan țɛeggiḍen : Semmeṛ-it ɣef wumidag !

<span id="an_27:24">27:24</span> Mi gwala lɣaci ugin a s-d ḥessen, yerna
ccwal simmal yețțimɣuṛ, Bilaṭus yeddem-ed aman, issared ifassen-is zdat
lɣaci, yenna : Nekk ur țekkiɣ ara di tazzla n idammen n uḥeqqi-agi, wagi
d ccɣel-nwen.

<span id="an_27:25">27:25</span> Lɣaci meṛṛa nnan-as : Tazzla n
idammen-is a d-tuɣal ɣef yirawen-nneɣ d yirawen n warraw-nneɣ.

<span id="an_27:26">27:26</span> Imiren Bilaṭus iserreḥ-ed i Barabas,
jelkḍen Sidna Ɛisa, dɣa yefka lameṛ a t-semmṛen ɣef wumidag.

<span id="an_27:27">27:27</span> Iɛsekṛiyen n lḥakem ssufɣen Sidna Ɛisa
ɣer ufrag, snejmaɛen-d akk iɛsekṛiyen nniḍen, zzin-as.

<span id="an_27:28">27:28</span> Imiren kksen-as llebsa-s, sselsen as
abeṛnus azeggaɣ.

<span id="an_27:29">27:29</span> Zḍan taɛeṣṣabt s isennanen,
ssersen-as-ț ɣef wuqeṛṛuy is, fkan-as aɣanim ɣer ufus-is ayeffus. Bdan
kennun zdat-es, stehzayen fell-as, qqaṛen-as : Sslam fell-ak ay agellid
n wat Isṛail !

<span id="an_27:30">27:30</span> Ssusufen-t, kkaten-t s uɣanim ɣer
uqeṛṛuy.

<span id="an_27:31">27:31</span> Mi ɛyan deg ustehzi fell-as, kksen-as
abeṛnus-nni, rran-as llebsa-s, wwin-t a t-semmṛen ɣef wumidag.

<span id="an_27:32">27:32</span> Mi d-ffɣen, mlalen-d yiwen wergaz n
tmurt n Qiṛwan, isem-is semɛun, ḥettmen fell-as ad ibbib amidag n Sidna
Ɛisa.

<span id="an_27:33">27:33</span> Mi wwḍen ɣer yiwen wemkan ițțusemman
Gulguṭa, yeɛni « amkan n uxecxuc »,

<span id="an_27:34">27:34</span> fkan-as ad isew ccṛab i deg yexleḍ
yiwen uɛeqqaṛ aṛzagan. Iɛreḍ-it, yugi a t-isew.

<span id="an_27:35">27:35</span> Mi t-semmṛen ɣef wumidag, gren tasɣaṛt
iwakken ad feṛqen llebsa-ines, s wakka, yedṛa-d wayen yuran di tira
iqedsen : feṛqen llebsa-w, gren tasɣart ɣef wuqenduṛ-iw.

<span id="an_27:36">27:36</span> Imiren qqimen a t-ɛassen,

<span id="an_27:37">27:37</span> ɛelqen sennig uqeṛṛuy-is talwiḥt i ɣef
uran sebba n lmut-is : Wagi d Ɛisa, agellid n wat Isṛail

<span id="an_27:38">27:38</span> Țwasemmṛen yid-es sin imcumen, yiwen
ɣer uyeffus-is wayeḍ ɣer uẓelmaḍ-is.

<span id="an_27:39">27:39</span> Imsebriden țhuzzun iqeṛṛay-nsen
reggmen-t,

<span id="an_27:40">27:40</span> qqaṛen-as : A win ițhuddun lǧameɛ
iqedsen ibennu-t di tlata wussan, sellek iman-ik ma d Mmi-s n Ṛebbi i
telliḍ, ers-ed seg umidag-nni.

<span id="an_27:41">27:41</span> Imeqqranen n lmuqedmin, lɛulama n
ccariɛa akk-d imeqqranen n wegdud, stehzayen fell-as ula d nutni, qqaṛen
:

<span id="an_27:42">27:42</span> Isellek wiyaḍ ur yezmir ad isellek
iman-is ! Ma d agellid n wat Isṛail i gella, a d-yers ihi seg umidag
iwakken a namen yis.

<span id="an_27:43">27:43</span> Yețkel ɣef Ṛebbi, a t-isellek ihi Ṛebbi
ma iḥemmel-it aaxaṭer yenna-d : « Nekk d Mmi-s n Ṛebbi.»

<span id="an_27:44">27:44</span> Ula d imcumen-nni ițțusemmṛen yid-es,
regmen-t am wiyaḍ.

<span id="an_27:45">27:45</span> Deg uzzal si tnac armi d țlata n
tmeddit, yeɣli-d ṭṭlam ɣef ddunit meṛṛa.

<span id="an_27:46">27:46</span> Ɣef leǧwahi n țlata, Sidna Ɛisa iɛeggeḍ
s tɛibṛanit, yenna : Ilya, Ilya, lama sabaqtani ? Yeɛni : Illu-iw,
Illu-iw, acuɣeṛ i yi-teǧǧiḍ ?

<span id="an_27:47">27:47</span> Kra seg wid iḥedṛen dinna slan d acu i
genna, qqaṛen : Issawal i nnbi Ilyas !

<span id="an_27:48">27:48</span> Imiren kan yiwen seg-sen yuzzel
yeddem-ed ameččim n taḍuṭ isselxes-it di lxell, icudd-it ɣef wuɣanim
yefka-yas ad isew.

<span id="an_27:49">27:49</span> Wiyaḍ qqaṛen : Anfet-as, a nwali ma
yella a d-yas nnbi Ilyas a t-isellek.

<span id="an_27:50">27:50</span> Sidna Ɛisa iɛeggeḍ tikkelt nniḍen, dɣa
iffeɣ-it Ṛṛuḥ.

<span id="an_27:51">27:51</span> Imiren kan abeḥnuq n leḥjab yellan di
lǧameɛ iqedsen icerreg ɣef sin, seg ixef ufella armi d akessar. Lqaɛa
tergagi, idurar ceqqeqen,

<span id="an_27:52">27:52</span> iẓekwan ldin, aṭas seg iḥeqqiyen
yemmuten, ḥyan-d

<span id="an_27:53">27:53</span> ffɣen-d seg iẓekwan-nsen. Mi d-iḥya
Sidna Ɛisa, kecmen ɣer temdint iqedsen, aṭas n lɣaci iwumi i d-ḍehṛen.

<span id="an_27:54">27:54</span> Lḥakem yellan d aqeṛṛuy ɣef meyya
iɛsekṛiyen akk-d iɛsekṛiyen iɛussen Sidna Ɛisa, tekcem-iten tugdi mi
walan tergagi lqaɛa d wayen akk yedṛan, nnan : Ț-țideț, argaz-agi d
Mmi-s n Ṛebbi !

<span id="an_27:55">27:55</span> Aṭas n tilawin i gellan dinna,
țmuqulent-ed si lebɛid. Ț-țiggad-nni i d-yeddan d Sidna Ɛisa si tmurt n
Jlili iwakken a s-qedcent.

<span id="an_27:56">27:56</span> Tella gar-asent Meryem tamagdalit,
Meryem yemma-s n Yeɛqub d Yusef akk-d d yemma-s n warraw n Zabadi.

<span id="an_27:57">27:57</span> Mi d-tewweḍ tmeddit, yusa-d yiwen
umeṛkanti n temdint n Arimati isem-is Yusef, ula d nețța d anelmad n
Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_27:58">27:58</span> Iṛuḥ ɣer Bilaṭus yessuter-as lǧețța n
Sidna Ɛisa. Bilaṭus yumeṛ ad a s-ț-id-fken.

<span id="an_27:59">27:59</span> Yusef yeddem-ed lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa,
ițțel-iț di lekfen zeddigen,

<span id="an_27:60">27:60</span> issers-iț deg yiwen uẓekka ajdid, i
geɣza deg uzṛu. Yeɣleq tawwurt n uẓekka-nni s weblaḍ ameqqran, dɣa iṛuḥ.

<span id="an_27:61">27:61</span> Meryem tamagdalit akk-d Meryem-nni
nniḍen, llant dinna qqiment, qublent-ed aẓekka.

<span id="an_27:62">27:62</span> Azekka nni yellan d ass n uheggi n wass
n westeɛfu, imeqqranen n lmuqedmin d ifariziyen ṛuḥen ɣer Bilaṭus

<span id="an_27:63">27:63</span> nnan-as : A Sidi, necfa ɣef wayen i
d-yenna ukeddab-agi asmi yedder, yenna-d : Ad ɛeddin tlata wussan, a
d-ḥyuɣ si ger lmegtin .

<span id="an_27:64">27:64</span> Ceggeɛ iɛessasen ad ɛassen aẓekka-s
alamma d ass wis tlata, iwakken inelmaden-is ur d-țasen ara ad akren
lǧețța-s, ad inin i wegdud : « iḥya-d si ger lmegtin. » Neɣ m'ulac
lekdeb-agi aneggaru ad yaggar amezwaru.

<span id="an_27:65">27:65</span> Bilaṭus yenna-yasen-d : Awit iɛessasen,
ṛuḥet ɛasset-ț akken tebɣam.

<span id="an_27:66">27:66</span> Ṛuḥen, zemmemen aken ilaq tawwurt n
uẓekka-nni s weblaḍ, imiren sbedden taɛessast zdat-es.

<span id="an_28:1">28:1</span> Mi gɛedda wass n westeɛfu, taṣebḥit n
wass amezwaru n dduṛt, Meryem tamagdalit akk-d meryem-nni nniḍen, ṛuḥent
a d-ẓuṛent aẓekka n Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_28:2">28:2</span> Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, tergagi lqaɛa ;
ataya yiwen n lmelk n Sidi Ṛebbi, iṣubb-ed seg igenni, iqeṛṛeb ɣer
uẓekka, iswexxeṛ ablaḍ-nni, yeqqim fell-as.

<span id="an_28:3">28:3</span> Ițfeǧǧiǧ am lebṛaq, llebsa-s ț-țamellalt
am udfel.

<span id="an_28:4">28:4</span> Iɛessasen yellan dinna, ikcem-iten lxuf d
ameqqran, qquṛen amzun mmuten.

<span id="an_28:5">28:5</span> Yenṭeq lmelk ɣer tilawin-nni,
yenna-yasent : Kunemti ur țțaggademt ara, axaṭer ẓriɣ ɣef Ɛisa i
yețțusemmṛen ɣef wumidag i tețnadimt.

<span id="an_28:6">28:6</span> Ulac-it dagi, iḥya-d si ger lmegtin akken
i t-id-yenna. Asemt-ed aț-țwalimt amkan anda akken yeḍleq !

<span id="an_28:7">28:7</span> Azlemt aț-ținimt i inelmaden-is belli
yeḥya-d si ger lmegtin. Atan a kkun-yezwir ɣer tmurt n Jlili ; dinna ara
t-teẓrem. AAtan nniɣ-akunt-ț-id !

<span id="an_28:8">28:8</span> Imiren kan, ṛuḥent seg uẓekka-nni s lfeṛḥ
d ameqqran ɣas akken uggadent. Uzzlent ad awint lexbaṛ i inelmaden n
Sidna Ɛisa.

<span id="an_28:9">28:9</span> Ataya Sidna Ɛisa imuger-itent-id,
yenna-yasent : Sslam fell-akunt ! QQeṛṛbent, seǧǧdent zdat-es, ssudnent
iḍaṛṛen-is.

<span id="an_28:10">28:10</span> Imiren Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yasent : Ur
țțaggademt ! Ṛuḥemt inimt i watmaten-iw ad ṛuḥen ɣer tmurt n Jlili,
dinna ara yi-ẓren.

<span id="an_28:11">28:11</span> Mi țeddunt deg ubrid, kra seg
iɛessasen-nni n uẓekka kecmen ɣer temdint, xebbṛen imeqqranen n
lmuqedmin ɣef wayen akk yedṛan.

<span id="an_28:12">28:12</span> Mi nnejmaɛen imeqqranen n wegdud akk-d
imeqqranen n lmuqedmin, msefhamen ad fken i iɛessasen-nni ssuma
tameqqrant n yedrimen,

<span id="an_28:13">28:13</span> nnan-asen : Init belli d inelmaden-is i
d-yusan deg yiḍ, ukren lǧețța-s mi nella neṭṭes.

<span id="an_28:14">28:14</span> Ma yella yewweḍ lexbaṛ-agi ɣer lḥakem,
d nukkni ara t-iqablen iwakken ur awen-ixeddem ula d acemma.

<span id="an_28:15">28:15</span> Iɛsekṛiyen-nni ṭṭfen idrimen-nni,
xedmen ayen akk i sen-d-nnan lmuqedmin. Tamsalt-agi țɛawaden-ț-id wat
Isṛail ar ass-a.

<span id="an_28:16">28:16</span> Ḥdac inelmaden-nni ṛuḥen ɣer tmurt n
Jlili, ɣer wedrar-nni anda i sen-yenna Sidna Ɛisa ad mlilen.

<span id="an_28:17">28:17</span> Mi t-walan seǧǧden zdat-es, meɛna kra
seg-sen mazal țcukkuten.

<span id="an_28:18">28:18</span> Sidna Ɛisa iqeṛṛeb-ed ɣuṛ-sen,
yenna-yasen : Tețțunefk-iyi-d tezmert ama di lqaɛa ama deg igenwan.

<span id="an_28:19">28:19</span> Ṛuḥet ɣer tmura meṛṛa n ddunit, slemdet
imdanen iwakken ad uɣalen d inelmaden-iw, ad țwaɣedṣen s yisem n Baba
Ṛebbi, s yisem n Mmi-s akk-d yisem n Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen.

<span id="an_28:20">28:20</span> Slemdet-asen ad tebɛen ayen akk i
wen-slemdeɣ. MMa d nekk ad iliɣ yid-wen yal ass alamma ț-țaggara n
ddunit.

